\id LUK ; Baga Sitem, Pioneer Bible Translators; 1st edition, June, 2006; 2nd edition Oct. 2012 with up-to-date key-term and spelling changes; spelling update (tch -->c) 08/2015; spelling update (changed all apostrophes to Unicode 2018: ', removed spaces before and after apostrophes) Aug 2016 CU; spelling update (/k…Ē-/ -->/k…Ē/) & (/c-/ --> /c/) Aug 2016 KWV 
\h Luk 
\toc3 LUK 
\toc2 Luk 
\toc1 K…ôbaru K…ôt…Ēt ka Luk 
\mt1 Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt ka Luk 
\c 1  
\s1 K…ôb…õr…õ ka k…ôcop moloku ma Luk 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ afum alar…ôm Ňčancop k…ôlomp…ôs ka mes mm…õ m…õnacep…ôr su dac…Ē m…Ē,  
\v 2 p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk mi d…ôk…ôcop, ak…Ē Ňčanasom k…ôloku ka afum toloku ta Kanu m…Ē.  
\v 3 K…ôlel…ôs kam, Teyofil, it…Ē p…ôwur…õn'em f…Ē p…ôntes…õ ina s…Ē, nt…õ int…õn mi belbel k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ôcop m…Ē. Awa, is…ĒŇč'am mi k…ôc…ôr…õ d…ômecic…ôs p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē inat…ôk…ôs mi m…Ē,  
\v 4 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôc…ôr…õ kance ka mes mm…õ ant…ôks'am m…Ē. 
\s1 M…õl…õk…õ moloku k…ôdekom ka AŇčnabi SaŇč\f + \fr 1:4 \fqa SaŇč Batis\ft  = ¬ęYaya¬Ľ, it…Ē ¬ęSaŇč, w…ôgb…ôt afum d…ôromun teta k…ôs…Ēk…ôs b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan.¬Ľ.\f* 
\p  
\v 5 T…õm nt…õ Herodu …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka at…Ēf Ňča Yude m…Ē, w…ôloŇčn…õ ka Kanu w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi pacwe k…Ē Sakary, w…ôka k…ôgba ka aloŇčn…õ nk…õ ancwen…õ w…ôtem Abiya m…Ē …õnay…Ēn…õ. W…ôran k…Ēn p…ôwur dokom da Aruna, pacwe k…Ē Elisab…õt.  
\v 6 M…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp Ňčanalomp f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč, Ňčac…ôm…õ s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē k…Ē mosom ma Mariki f…ôp dar…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar m…Ē.  
\v 7 Mba Ňčanay…Ē f…õ wan, bawo Elisab…õt …õnay…Ēn…õ f…õ w…ôran w…ôkomb…ôra, m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp Ňčanasik…ôr. 
\p  
\v 8 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma Sakary p…ôcb…ôc y…õb…ôc y…Ēn ya k…ôloŇčn…õ ka Kanu, bawo k…ôgba k…ôŇčan k…ônak…Ē k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôloŇčn…õ kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 9 P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aloŇčn…õ a Kanu ŇčaŇčy…Ē ti m…Ē, k'aŇčgbal k…Ēla\f + \fr 1:9 \fq K'aŇčgbal k…Ēla\ft  = tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē ancy…õk-y…õk w…ôloŇčn…õ aloŇčn…õ dac…Ē nw…õ p…ôcmar k…ôb…õr…õ k…ôfo k…ôcempi k…ôk…Ēmot…õ Kanu curay nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē. K…Ē k…Ēla k…ôment…ôr nw…õ Kanu k…ôfaŇč m…Ē.\f*, k…Ē k…Ēla k…ôment…ôr Sakary d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē k…ôb…õr…õ ka d…ôk…ôfo k…ôcempi ka k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôk…Ēmot…õ Mariki curay.  
\v 10 Afum alar…ôm Ňčanayi nde dabaŇčka \k Ňčaclok-lok…ôr Kanu\k* t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ancmot curay m…Ē.  
\v 11 Awa, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma Mariki mowur…ôr Sakary, m…õc…ôm…õ nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka tetek nt…õ aŇčmot…õ Mariki suray m…Ē.  
\v 12 Nt…õ Sakary …õn…ôŇčk m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē yamayama, k…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôsump…ôr k…Ē.  
\v 13 Mba k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ moloku k…Ē: 
\q1 ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ Sakary, 
\q1 bawo Kanu k…ôl…õk k…ôtola kam: 
\q1 Elisab…õt, w…ôran kam, endekom'am wan w…ôrkun 
\q1 m…ôde m…ôwe k…Ē tewe ta SaŇč\f + \fr 1:13 \fq SaŇč\ft  = ¬ęYaya¬Ľ\f*. 
\q1  
\v 14 Wan w…ôkak…Ē endes…ĒŇč'am k…ôyekti domp p…ôb…Ēt …ôm s…Ē mes, 
\q1 k…ôkom k…Ēn k…ôndes…ĒŇč…õ afum alar…ôm k…ôsels…ôr. 
\q1  
\v 15 Bawo fum w…ôp…ĒŇč endeyi f…Ēr ya Mariki kiriŇč, 
\q1 …Ēf…Ēde p…ôcmun member, …Ēf…Ēde p…ôcmun yomun…ôs ny…õ yencis…ôs m…Ē, 
\q1 endelar…õ \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* p…ôs…Ēr…Ēyi k…õr…õ d…ôkor. 
\q1  
\v 16 Endeluks…õ awut a Yisrayel alar…ôm nn…Ē Mariki, Kanu k…ôŇčan k…ôyi m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 17 Kanu k…ôndesak SaŇč p…ôyi W…ôb…õ kiriŇč k…ôder…õn…õ amera k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr ya w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu Eli. 
\q1 Endekaf…ôli b…ôk…ôc ya cas nn…Ē awut Ňčayi m…Ē, 
\q1 b…ôk…ôc ya ataŇči l…ôŇč…ôs nn…Ē k…ôs…Ēk domp ka alompu k…ôyi m…Ē, 
\q1 p…ôlomp…ôs afum aŇč…õ Ňčandeyi kiyi ka Mariki t…õm f…ôp m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\b  
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē Sakary eyif m…õl…õk…õ: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē indec…ôr…õn…õ, a kance k…Ē-…õ? Bawo w…ôtem iy…Ēn…õ k…Ē w…ôran kem s…Ē …õmb…õk.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ m…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ, mocloku k…Ē : ¬ęIna …Ēy…Ēn…õ Yibirila nw…õ …õnc…ôm…õ Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē! Asom im k…ôsom d…ôm k…ôdelok-lok…ôr …ôm, ilok'…ôm toloku t…Ēt…Ēt tant…õ.  
\v 20 Mba nt…õ m…ônt…ĒlaŇč moloku mem m…Ē, m…ôf…Ēdes…Ētam k…ôlok-loku haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ tendeyi m…Ē, t…õm nt…õ Kanu k…ôndefaŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 21 Nt…õ afum f…ôp Ňčackar Sakary nde dabaŇčka m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônde p…ôciyan…õ Ňča, bawo oncwon d…ôndo k…ôfo k…ôcempi.  
\v 22 Sakary endewur, …õntam f…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr Ňča, k…Ē afum Ňčanc…ôr…õ a Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Sakary k…ôn…ôŇčk tes t…Ēl…Ēma d…ôndo k…ôfo k…ôcempi disr…õ. K…Ē Sakary …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôt…Ētam k…ôlok-loku, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr…õ Ňča waca. 
\p  
\v 23 Nt…õ mataka m…Ēn ma y…õb…ôc mencep…ôr m…Ē, k'olukus nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn.  
\v 24 P…ôwon f…õ, k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Elisab…õt …õmb…õk…ôs. K'…ĒŇčgb…Ēpn…õ yof k…ôcam…ôt, p…ôcloku:  
\v 25 ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē Mariki …Ēy…Ēn'em, …õnt…õp oŇč k…ôdewos…õ k…ôwur'em malap nn…Ē afum Ňčayi m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 M…õl…õk…õ moloku k…ôdekom k'AŇčnabi Yesu 
\p  
\v 26 Nt…õ K…ôb…õk…ôs ka Elisab…õt k…ôs…Ēt…Ē yof cam…ôt-tin m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôsom m…õl…õk…õ m…Ēn Yibirila nde dare d…Ēk…Ē aŇčwe Nasar…õt m…Ē, at…Ēf Ňča Kalile,  
\v 27 ndena wan w…ôran w…ôt…Ēc…ôr…õ w…ôrkun, nw…õ ancwe Mari m…Ē. Isifu w…ôka dokom da Dawuda …õncfac k…Ē.  
\v 28 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ m…õmb…õr…õ ndena Mari, k…Ē moloku: ¬ęP…ôb…Ēt …ôm, m…ôna nw…õ Kanu k…ômar kif…ôli m…Ē! Mariki osol'am!¬Ľ  
\v 29 K…Ē toloku tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē p…ôyi Mari yamayama. K'eyifn…õ nt…õ k…ôyif kaŇčk…Ē k…ôloku m…Ē.  
\v 30 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku k…Ē: 
\q1 ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ Mari, bawo m…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ômar kif…ôli nk…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ndena Kanu m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 31 M…ôn…ôŇčk f…õ! K…ôb…õk…ôs k…Ē m…ônder, m…ôkom wan w…ôrkun, 
\q1 m…ôde m…ôwe k…Ē tewe ta Yesu.  
\v 32 Fum w…ôp…ĒŇč endeyi, pacwe k…Ē wan ka W…ôb…õ w…ôka darenc, 
\q1 Mariki Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôndes…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôŇčgbasar \f + \fr 1:32 \fq K…ôŇčgbasar\ft  = ¬ęd…Ēc…Ēm da d…õb…õ¬Ľ, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta d…õb…õ.\f* ka d…õb…õ da Dawuda, w…ôtem k…Ēn. 
\q1  
\v 33 Nk…Ēn endekek…ôr…õ d…õb…õ da doru o doru nn…Ē aka dolom da Yakuba \f + \fr 1:33 \fq Aka dolom da Yakuba\ft  = ¬ęafum aka Yisrayel¬Ľ\f* Ňčayi m…Ē, 
\q1 d…õb…õ d…Ēn d…Ēf…Ēdelip.¬Ľ 
\b  
\p  
\v 34 K…Ē Mari eyif m…õl…õk…õ: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē t…õntam k…ôyi-…õ, bawo inc…ôr…õ f…õ w…ôrkun?¬Ľ  
\v 35 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku k…Ē: 
\q1 ¬ę\k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňčendeder …ôm, f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa W…ôb…õ w…ôka darenc f…ôkump …ôm kat…ôk…ôp k…Ēn. 
\q1 It…Ē endes…ĒŇč…õ wan nw…õ andekom m…Ē k…ôcemp, packul…õ k…Ē ¬ęWan ka Kanu.¬Ľ 
\m  
\v 36 M…ôn…ôŇčk f…õ! Elisab…õt w…ôkom…õn…õ kam, nk…Ēn s…Ē …õmb…õk…ôs wan w…ôrkun detemb…ôra d…Ēn disr…õ. Nk…Ēn nw…õ anckul…õ k…ôt…Ēkom m…Ē, Ňčof Ňč…Ēn Ňča cam…ôt-tin Ňča k…ôb…õk…ôs Ňčeyi ŇčaŇč…õ,  
\v 37 bawo Kanu k…ôf…Ētarp…õn…õ tes o tes.¬Ľ  
\v 38 K…Ē Mari oloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôy…Ēn'em tat…Ēk…Ē m…ônt…õp k…ôcloku m…Ē. W…ôcar ka Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč iy…Ēn…õ. Intola teyi p…ôm…Ē tant…õ m…ôlok'im ti m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ m…õy…õf…õ k…Ē day k…Ē m…ĒŇčk…Ē. 
\s1 Mari k…ôk…Ēt…ôs ndena Elisab…õt p…ôk…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē 
\p  
\v 39 Mata mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Mari …õy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē kat…ôna kat…ôna dare da Yuda d…Ēl…Ēma, nde at…Ēf Ňča d…ôm…Ēr…Ē.  
\v 40 K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē ka Sakary, k'eyif Elisab…õt.  
\v 41 Elisab…õt endene k…ône d…ôm k…ôyif ka Mari, k…Ē wan …õs…õp k…Ē d…ôkor. K…Ē \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňč…õlar…õ katin Elisab…õt,  
\v 42 k…Ē Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Elisab…õt k…ôgb…ôŇč…õ k…ôloku: 
\q1 ¬ęKanu k…ômpoc'am p…ôt…Ēt aran f…ôp dac…Ē, 
\q1  
\v 43 Ak'iy…Ēn…õ nt…õ iya w…ôka W…ôb…õ kem endeder k…ôyif im m…Ē?  
\v 44 Nt…õ ine k…ôyif kam m…Ē, k…Ē wan …õs…õp im d…ôkor p…ôbotu disr…õ.  
\v 45 P…ôb…Ēt nw…õ …õnalaŇč m…Ē, bawo nt…õ Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč k…ônaloku k…Ē m…Ē tendeyi.¬Ľ 
\s1 TeleŇč ta Mari tokor-kor…õ Kanu 
\p  
\v 46 K…Ē Mari oloku oŇč: 
\q1 ¬ęIŇčkor-koru Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôtam kem f…ôp, 
\q1 Kanu k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt pokom pa kor kam! 
\q1  
\v 47 Amera Ňčem Ňč…õlar…õ p…ôbotu teta Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč W…ôyac kem, 
\q1  
\v 48 bawo owos…õ k…ôgbal f…Ēr nn…Ē ina, w…ôcar k…Ēn w…ôf…ôf…ôr iyi m…Ē. 
\q1 ∆źy, k…ôy…õf…õ nd…õk…ôl haŇč t…õm f…ôp, afum Ňčande Ňčaclok'im a p…ômb…Ēt im, 
\q1  
\v 49 bawo W…ôka f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn'em mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč m…Ē, 
\q1 tewe t…Ēn tencemp! 
\q1  
\v 50 K…ôb…Ēt ka Kanu amera k…ôŇčy…õf…õ d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp 
\q1 ak…Ē Ňčalel…ôs ki m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 51 K…ôment…ôr f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa k…ôca k…Ēn: 
\q1 k…Ē k…ôsams…ôr afum ak…Ē Ňčanab…õk b…ôk…ôc m…Ē, 
\q1  
\v 52 k…Ē k…ôŇčgbal ab…õ ap…ĒŇč d…õb…õ daŇčan 
\q1 k…Ē k…ônc…ômb…ôr af…ôf…ôr kiriŇč. 
\q1  
\v 53 K…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ p…ôt…Ēt aŇč…õ dor d…õnay…Ē m…Ē, 
\q1 k…Ē k…ômb…õl…ôs ak…Ē Ňčanay…Ē daka m…Ē waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr. 
\q1  
\v 54 K…Ē k…ônder k…ôdemar aka Yisrayel, amar…ôs …Ēn: 
\q1 k…ômp…ôl…ôrn…õ f…õ k…ôment…ôr dobotu amera d…Ēn 
\q1  
\v 55 a Abraham k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn ta doru o doru 
\q1 ‚ÄĒp…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku ti atem asu m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\b  
\p  
\v 56 K…Ē Mari Ňčayi k…Ē Elisab…õt haŇč yof maas, k'olukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn. 
\s1 K…ôkom ka AŇčnabi SaŇč Batis\f + \fr 1:56 \fqa SaŇč Batis\ft , m…ôm…Ēm…ôn 1.6\f* 
\p  
\v 57 K…Ē t…õm t…õmb…ôp nt…õ p…ônamar Elisab…õt p…ôkom m…Ē, k'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun.  
\v 58 And…õ …Ēn k…Ē akom…õn…õ …Ēn Ňčane, a Kanu k…ôntor…õ k…Ē p…ôforu disr…õ, k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt Ňča f…ôp faŇčan.  
\v 59 Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas ta k…ôkom k…Ēn, k…Ē Ňčander k…ôdek…ônc ka wan, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč…õn…õ k…Ē tewe ta kas Sakary.  
\v 60 Mba k…Ē k…õr…õ …õl…õk moloku, k'oloku: ¬ęAla, SaŇč s…Ē andewe k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 61 Mba afum Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęAli fum eyi f…õ dokom dam nw…õ aŇčwe tewe tant…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 62 K…Ē afum Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt…õ kas waca, tewe ta wan nt…õ …õfaŇč pawe k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 63 K…Ē Sakary ewe tabam, k'encic: ¬ęSaŇč s…Ē andewe k…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē p…ônciyan…õ afum f…ôp.  
\v 64 K…Ē kusu k…Ēn k…ômep…õ katina, k…Ē temer t…Ēn t…õy…õf…õ, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôkor-koru Kanu.  
\v 65 K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôyi and…õ …Ēn f…ôp, k…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmbaŇč at…Ēf Ňča Yude f…ôp, pacyif…ôt…õn…õ mi.  
\v 66 Nw…õ o nw…õ ene pacloku mi, teŇčyi k…Ē d…õb…ôk…ôc, Ňčacyifn…õ: ¬ęAke wan w…ôkak…Ē endey…Ēn…õ oŇč-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč f…ônc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč. 
\s1 TeleŇč ta Sakary tokor-kor…õ Kanu 
\p  
\v 67 K'\k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňč…õlar…õ Sakary papa ka SaŇč, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôd…ôŇčk moloku mm…õ Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôloku m…Ē, p…ôcloku: 
\q1  
\v 68 ¬ęIŇčkor-kor'…ôm m…ôna Mariki, Kanu ka aka Yisrayel, 
\q1 bawo k…ônder k…ômar afum …Ēn, k…Ē k…ômbaŇč Ňča. 
\q1  
\v 69 K…ôwur…õ su w…ôyac w…ôp…ĒŇč, 
\q1 dokom da Dawuda, w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn. 
\q1  
\v 70 ‚ÄĒIt…Ē Kanu k…ônalok-lok…õ cusu ca ad…ôŇčk …Ēn acempi k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ p…ônawon m…Ē‚ÄĒ 
\q1  
\v 71 k…ônas…ĒŇč su temer k…ôdebaŇč su ater…õn…õ asu d…ôwaca 
\q1 k…Ē k…ôtam ka ak…Ē Ňčant…ĒfaŇč…õ su p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 72 It…Ē k…ônament…ôr…õ amera Ňčobotu Ňča ki atem asu, 
\q1 k…Ē k…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ \k k…ôcaŇč…ôs k…ôcempi k…ôŇčan k…ôyi tes tin\k*. 
\q1  
\v 73 P…ôm…Ē \k k…ôd…õr…ôm\k* kaŇčk…Ē Kanu k…ônad…õrm…õ Abraham w…ôtem kosu, it…Ē …õlas…õ su ki, 
\q1  
\v 74 a k…Ē k…ôndebaŇč su ater…õn…õ asu d…ôwaca-…õ, 
\q1 k…ôndes…ĒŇč…õ su t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē packor-koru k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yoforu disr…õ, 
\q1  
\v 75 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pakor-koru k…Ē decempi k…Ē dolompu disr…õ f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč 
\q1 kiyi kosu doru f…ôp m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 76 K…Ē m…ôna wan kem, w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka W…ôb…õ w…ôka darenc …Ē andew'am. 
\q1 M…ôna endeyi Mariki kiriŇč, m…ôclomp…ôs s…ôp…Ē s…Ēn. 
\q1  
\v 77 M…ôk…Ē m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum …Ēn k…ôc…ôr…õ a Kanu k…ônder k…ôdeyac Ňča, 
\q1 k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan.  
\v 78 ∆źy! Teta d…õr…õnc k…Ē dobotu amera da Kanu kosu, 
\q1 k…ômot su p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pa darenc, mp…õ powur…õn…õ k…Ē p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pa dec d…õp…õnc…õ m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 79 Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ak…Ē Ňčayi kubump k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčayi kat…ôk…ôp ka defi d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, Ňčas…Ēt…Ē p…ôwaŇčk…ôra, 
\q1 k…ôsol…õ su s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē da p…ôforu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 80 K…Ē wan …õmb…õk, p…ôcs…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa amera. K'eyi d…ôndo d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ …õnament…ôrn…õ nn…Ē afum aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē. 
\c 2  
\s1 K…ôkom ka AŇčnabi Yesu (Isa) 
\r Mat 1.18-25 
\p  
\v 1 Mata mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, Okustu w…ôb…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp, osom k…ôl…Ēm ka afum aŇč…õ Ňčanayi d…õb…õ d…Ēn d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 2 K…ôl…Ēm k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē kaŇčk…Ē k…ônayi t…õm nt…õ Okustu …õnac…ômb…ôr Kureniyo, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka at…Ēf Ňča Siri m…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē afum f…ôp ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ mewe nw…õ o nw…õ nde dare d…Ēn d…Ēp…ĒŇč nd…õ aŇčkom k…Ē m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 4 K…Ē Isifu nk…Ēn s…Ē …õmp…õ k…ôy…õf…õ dare da Nasar…õt at…Ēf Ňča Kalile k…ôk…Ē dare da Dawuda nd…õ aŇčwe Betl…õh…õm m…Ē, bawo Isifu w…ôka k…ôl…Ē k…Ē dokom da Dawuda d…Ē …õnay…Ēn…õ.  
\v 5 Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ tewe k…Ē Mari, w…ôran nw…õ …õncfac m…Ē, w…ôkak…Ē p…ôb…õk…ôs. 
\p  
\v 6 Ňäanas…Ēr…Ēyi di, k…Ē t…õm ta Mari tokom t…õmb…ôp,  
\v 7 k'oŇčkom wan k…Ēn w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôrkun. K'…Ēf…Ēkt…ôr k…Ē d…ôk…ôloto, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôboc k…Ē d…ôtaŇčku nt…õ ancb…õr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yeri m…Ē, bawo Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē f…õ k…ôfo d…ôndo d…ôkarwaŇčse. 
\s1 M…õl…õk…õ ma Kanu mowur…ôr ak…õk y…Ēc…Ēl 
\p  
\v 8 At…Ēf Ňčin ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnay…Ē ak…õk aŇč…õ Ňčanccep…ôr…õn…õ pibi d…ôkulum k…ôbum ka y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan m…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč mowur…ôr Ňča, k…Ē \k p…ômot pa debeki da Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč\k* p…õŇčk…õl Ňča. K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôyi Ňča.  
\v 10 Mba k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ! Bawo toloku t…Ēt…Ēt t…Ē inder k…ôdeloku nu, nt…õ tendeb…Ēt…ôs afum f…ôp b…ôk…ôc m…Ē:  
\v 11 M…Ēk…Ē, nde dare da Dawuda disr…õ, aŇčkom…õ nu w…ôyac, nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ W…ôb…õ, nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē. \f + \fr 2:11 \fq W…ôsom ka Kanu\ft  = ¬ęKrist¬Ľ tokul…õ t…Ē = ¬ęNw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk k…ôsom m…Ē¬Ľ.\f* 
\v 12 Nt…õ tendey…Ēn…õ nu t…õn…õp…ôl…õ taka ti: N…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp k…ônaka paf…Ēkt…ôr ki d…ôk…ôloto, k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ d…ôtaŇčku nt…õ amb…õr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yeri m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 13 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē k…ônay ka m…õl…õk…õ ma darenc k…ôm…õpn…õ katina m…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôkor-koru ka Kanu, mocloku:  
\v 14 ¬ę\k Debeki da Kanu\k* deyi darenc, b…ôk…ôc y…Ēf…Ēr ak…Ē Ňčayi d…ônt…Ēf ak'…Ēmb…Ēt…ôr Ňča m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 Ak…õk k…ôk…Ē k…ôŇčan Bet L…õh…õm 
\p  
\v 15 Nt…õ m…õl…õk…õ m…õsak Ňča k…Ē m…õmp…õ darenc m…Ē, k…Ē ak…õk Ňčalok…õn…õ: ¬ęAwa, paŇčk…Ēn haŇč Betl…õh…õm, pak…Ē pan…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē teyi m…Ē, nt…õ Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôc…ôr…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē ak…õk Ňčamb…õlk…ôr k…ôk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp Mari k…Ē Isifu, k…ônaka k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ taŇčku p…õb…õr…õ pa y…Ēc…Ēl yeri.  
\v 17 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôn…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčal…Ēm t…Ēk…Ē analoku Ňča teta wan kak…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 18 Ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôŇčk…ôl moloku m…Ēk…Ē ak…õk Ňčancl…Ēm…ôr Ňča m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē menciyan…õ Ňča.  
\v 19 K…Ē Mari …õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ moloku mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, p…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ mi d…õb…ôk…ôc.  
\v 20 K…Ē ak…õk Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē nde Ňčanay…õf…õ m…Ē, \k Ňčaccam debeki\k* da Kanu, Ňčanckor-koru Ki teta moloku m…Ēk…Ē m…õl…õk…õ m…õnaloku Ňča, a k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk s…Ē mi m…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôwur…õ ka AŇčnabi Yesu doru 
\p  
\v 21 Nt…õ k…ôkom ka wan k…ôs…Ēt…Ē mata cam…ôt-maas m…Ē, k'aŇčk…ônc k…Ē, k'awe k…Ē Yesu, tewe nt…õ m…õl…õk…õ m…õnabonc…ôr Ňča, ta antab…õk…ôs k…Ē m…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôment…ôr ka AŇčnabi Yesu nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* 
\p  
\v 22 Nt…õ mataka maŇčan ma k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ melip p…ôm…Ē nt…õ sariy…õ sa Musa s…ôloku ti m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē Yerusal…õm k…ôk…Ēment…ôr k…Ē W…ôb…õ Kanu.  
\v 23 Ňäanay…Ē m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēk…Ē ancic buk ba sariy…õ sa W…ôb…õ disr…õ m…Ē: ¬ęAwut arkun ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē aŇč…õ aran ŇčaŇčkom m…Ē f…ôp, p…ômar pas…ĒŇč Ňča W…ôb…õ Kanu Ňčay…Ēn…õ acempi.¬Ľ  
\v 24 P…ômar s…Ē akomb…ôra a wan w…ôkak…Ē ŇčaloŇčn…õ Kanu ¬ęm…Ēpay m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ntantoriya yowut m…õr…ôŇč,¬Ľ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aloku ti sariy…õ sa W…ôb…õ disr…õ m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 25 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi Yerusal…õm pacwe k…Ē Simey…ĒŇč. Fum w…ôlompu …õnayi p…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu dar…ôŇč, p…ôckar nw…õ endeyac Yisrayel m…Ē, \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňč…õnayi k…Ē k…ôroŇč.  
\v 26 Amera Ňäecempi ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ, a …Ēf…Ēfi ta …õn…ôŇčk Krist, w…ôb…õ nw…õ Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē.  
\v 27 K…Ē \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňč…Ēnc…ĒŇč…ôs k…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k*. Nt…õ akomb…ôra a Yesu ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē k…ôk…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku m…Ē,  
\v 28 k…Ē Sim…ĒŇč …õl…õk wan d…ôwaca k'eyif Kanu barka p…ôcloku:  
\v 29 ¬ęW…ôb…õ, m…ôntam oŇč k…ôsak w…ôcar kam p…ôfin…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčoforu p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ônaloku ti m…Ē,  
\v 30 bawo f…Ēr yem yati y…Ē in…ôŇčk…õ nt…õ m…ôy…Ē k…ôyac ka afum am m…Ē‚ÄĒ  
\v 31 Nw…õ m…ôlomp…ôs afum f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē‚ÄĒ  
\v 32 endey…Ēn…õ p…ôm…Ē p…ômot mp…õ pendes…ĒŇč afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp p…ôwaŇčk…ôra it'…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôr…õ Kanu. Nw…õ endey…Ēn…õ p…ôlel pa afum am, aka Yisrayel.¬Ľ 
\s1 Sim…ĒŇč k…ôloku ka t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ôndey…Ē m…Ē 
\p  
\v 33 K…Ē p…ônciyan…õ akomb…ôra a Yesu nt…õ Sim…ĒŇč oncloku teta Yesu m…Ē.  
\v 34 K…Ē Simey…ĒŇč ontolan…õ Ňča, k'oloku Mari iya w…ôka Yesu: ¬ęKanu k…ôŇčk…õr…õ wan w…ôkaw…õ k…ôdes…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel alar…ôm k…ôt…õmp…õn…õ, p…ôyekti s…Ē alar…ôm. Paka pa Kanu p…Ē mp…õ pendes…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 35 Endeb…õr p…ôwaŇčk…ôra b…ôk…ôc ya ak…Ē Ňčay…Ē m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…Ēgb…Ēpn…õ m…Ē. K…Ē m…ôna Mari, p…ôcuy pendefut'…ôm ab…ôk…ôc p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…ôŇčgbasar k…ôŇčfutu m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 W…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu w…ôran Hana 
\p  
\v 36 W…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi pacwe k…Ē Hana, wan ka Panuy…õl, w…ôka kusuŇčka ka As…õr. W…ôran w…ôsik…ôr …õnayi. ∆źnal…Ē nda w…ôrkun meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ anagbaŇčn…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 37 K…Ē wos ende p…ôfi, k'eyi oŇč ta …Ēy…Ē w…ôrkun-…õ. Hana p…ôs…Ēt…Ē meren 84 k'eyi, ta …Ēmb…Ēl…õ \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k*-…õ p…ôcb…ôc m…õfaŇč ma Kanu daŇč k…Ē pibi \k k…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu\k* k…Ē k…ôsuŇč disr…õ.  
\v 38 K…Ē nk…Ēn …ĒŇčk…Ē s…Ē p…ôb…õr…õ di t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Sim…ĒŇč oncloku teta wan p…ôckor-koru s…Ē Kanu m…Ē, p…ôcyif Kanu n…ôwali, p…ôcloku teta wan ak…Ē Ňčanckar Kanu k…ôdeyac Yerusal…õm m…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôlukus ka Nasar…õt 
\p  
\v 39 Nt…õ akomb…ôra a Yesu Ňčalip k…ôy…Ē ka m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēk…Ē aloku sariy…õ sa Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalukus nde ndaraŇčan Kalile, nde dare da Nasar…õt.  
\v 40 Awa, wan p…ôcb…õk, p…ôcs…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. P…ôlar…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes, k…ômar kif…ôli ka Kanu k…ôyi k…Ē k…ôroŇč. 
\s1 AŇčnabi Yesu k…ôk…Ē ka nde K…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč teren t…Ēn ta w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč 
\p  
\v 41 K…ôren o k…ôren, akomb…ôra a Yesu Ňčanck…Ē Yerusal…õm k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôsata ka aSuyif ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif.\f + \fr 2:41 \fqa K…ôsata ka k…ôcep…ôr\ft  = K…ôsata k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Yisrayel k…Ē, nk…õ k…ônc…õm-c…õm…ôs Ňča t…Ēk…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mencdif…ôt awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Misira a m…õcsak ak…ôŇčan m…Ē.\f* 
\p  
\v 42 Nt…õ Yesu …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, k…Ē akomb…ôra …Ēn Ňčasol…õ k…Ē k…ôk…Ēt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif d…ôndo Yerusal…õm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčancy…Ē ti k…ôren o k…ôren m…Ē.  
\v 43 Nt…õ mataka ma k…ôsata melip m…Ē, k…Ē akomb…ôra a Yesu Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…ôlukus ndaraŇčan, mba k…Ē wan Yesu nk…Ēn eyi Yerusal…õm, ta akomb…ôra …Ēn Ňčanc…ôr…õ ti-…õ.  
\v 44 Akomb…ôra …Ēn Ňčanac…õm-c…õmn…õ a Yesu Ňčasol k…Ē alukus, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēt tataka tin. K…Ē Ňčant…õn Yesu akom…õn…õ k…Ē ac…ôr…õn…õ aŇčan dac…Ē.  
\v 45 Mba Ňčanan…ôŇčk f…õ k…Ē. K…Ē Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē Yerusal…õm Ňčact…õn k…Ē.  
\v 46 Mata maas disr…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk k…Ē nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* disr…õ, p…ônd…õ at…ôks…õ dac…Ē p…ôcc…ôŇčk…ôl Ňča, p…ôcyif…ôt Ňča moloku.  
\v 47 AŇč…õ Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, cusu c…ônawos Ňča dosoku domp d…Ēn, k…Ē moloku mm…õ oncluks…õ Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 48 Nt…õ akomb…ôra …Ēn Ňčan…ôŇčk k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônciyan…õ Ňča. K…Ē k…õr…õ eyif k…Ē: ¬ęWan kem, ta ake t…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ su tant…õ-…õ? Papa kam k…Ē ina, b…ôk…ôc y…õl…õc…õ-l…õc…õ su k…ôt…õn kam!¬Ľ  
\v 49 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônt…õn'em-…õ? N…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ a m…õn…õ isump…ôr y…õb…ôc ya Papa kem?¬Ľ  
\v 50 Mba akomb…ôra …Ēn Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ tedisr…õ ta toloku tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 51 K…Ē Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…Ē Ňčasol k…Ē akomb…ôra …Ēn k…ôk…Ē ka Nasar…õt, bawo Yesu …õnalel…ôs Ňča. K…Ē iya k…Ēn …õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp. 
\p  
\v 52 Yesu p…ôcb…õr…õn…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes k…ôt…Ēt, p…ôcnaŇčkan…õ k…ôb…õk, p…ôcs…Ēt…Ē k…ômar kif…ôli ka Kanu k…Ē afum. 
\c 3  
\s1 Kawandi ka AŇčnabi SaŇč 
\r Mat 3.1-12; Mark 1.1-8; IsaŇč 1.19-28 
\p  
\v 1 Teren ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt ta w…ôb…õ w…ôka at…Ēf Ňča Tib…õr, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē s…Ē P…ĒŇčse Pilat p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka at…Ēf Ňča Yude, Herodu nk…Ēn p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka at…Ēf Ňča Kalile, w…õnc Filip p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka t…Ēf m…õr…ôŇč: nde Iture k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Tirakoniti. Lisaniyas p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ nde at…Ēf Ňča Abil…õn.  
\v 2 T…õm ta aloŇčn…õ a Kanu ap…ĒŇč Hana k…Ē Kayifa t…õnayi s…Ē. K…Ē toloku ta Kanu tender SaŇč, wan ka Sakary, nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.  
\v 3 K…Ē SaŇč …ĒŇčk…Ēt s…ôdare f…ôp ns…õ s…ôyi k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, p…ôckawandi k…ôgb…ôt afum d…ôromun teta k…ôs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc Ňčac…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Kanu k…ôdeŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan m…Ē.  
\v 4 P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic mi nde buk ba moloku ma sayib…õ Esayi m…Ē: 
\q1 ¬ęFum w…ôk…Ē dim d…Ēn deyi k…ôwur nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē …Ēf…Ē: 
\q1 N…ôlomp…ôs d…Ēp…Ē da Mariki. 
\q1 N…ôlomp…õ s…ôp…Ē s…Ēn sa w…õc…ôk! 
\q1  
\v 5 Andelas m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē f…ôp, 
\q1 m…Ēr…Ē k…Ē p…ôŇčeci f…ôp yendetor, 
\q1 S…ôp…Ē s…ônut…ôsn…õ f…ôp s…ôndelomp, 
\q1 S…ôp…Ē s…ôcumbul-cumbul f…ôp, andeyukur si, 
\q1  
\v 6 Afum f…ôp Ňčanden…ôŇčk k…ôyac ka Kanu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 7 Afum alar…ôm ak…Ē Ňčancder nk…Ēn SaŇč p…ôdegb…ôt Ňča d…ôromun teta Kanu m…Ē, Ňč…Ē oncloku ti: ¬ęN…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôyi p…ôm…Ē Ňčkisin m…Ē! An'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôc…ôr…õ nt…õ aŇčy…õks…ôr kiti ka Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi k…ôder m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 8 Awa n…ôde n…ôcy…Ē m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ meŇčment…ôr a n…ôs…ôkp…ôr mera k…Ē n…ônc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč m…Ē. Ta p…ôb…Ēt nu k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ: ‚ÄĻAbraham …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem kosu.‚Äļ ∆źy, icloku nu, n…ôn…ôŇčk masar mam…õ ba? Kanu k…ôntam k…ôkaf…ôli mi m…Ēy…Ēn…õ awut a Abraham.  
\v 9 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč tomunt pelip k…ôc…ôm…õ k…ôc…õp ka t…Ēk haŇč nde nt…õnt…ôl ya yi: K…ôt…Ēk nk…õ o nk…õ k…ônt…Ēkom yokom y…Ēt…Ēt m…Ē, anc…õp ki, pal…ôm d…ôn…õnc.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē c…ôgba ca afum c…ôy…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē s…ôndey…Ē oŇč-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 11 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęM…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē suma m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, m…ôpoc…õ w…ôk…Ē …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē m…Ē, m…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē yeri m…Ē, m…ôpoc…õ w…ôk…Ē …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē abaŇč…ôs dut Ňčander a SaŇč p…ôgb…ôt Ňča d…ôromun teta Kanu, Ňčacyif…ôt k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, c…ôke c…Ē p…ômar s…ôdey…Ē oŇč-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 13 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ôdeŇč…ôr mp…õ o mp…õ ant…Ēloku nu k…ôbaŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē as…Ēdar Ňčayif k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęA s…ôna-a, c…ôke c…Ē p…ômar s…ôy…Ē oŇč-…õ?¬Ľ K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ôment…ôr nw…õ o nw…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr, ta n…ôdeŇč…õ s…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ yem, k…ôway konu k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ nu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 15 Nt…õ afum f…ôp Ňčanayi k…ôkar m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčyifn…õ d…ôb…ôk…ôc k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ baf…Ē SaŇč …Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist, nw…õ Kanu k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē SaŇč oluks…õ Ňča: ¬ęIna d…ôromun iŇčgb…ôt nu teta Kanu de, mba w…ôl…Ēma eyi k…ôder nw…õ …Ēy…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr p…ôtas im m…Ē, ali b…ônda ya c…Ēfta c…Ēn is…Ēt…Ē f…õ yati dofum isik…ôli ci. W…ôkak…Ē, \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* disr…õ k…Ē n…õnc y…Ē ende p…ôcgb…ôt nu.  
\v 17 P…ôc…ôm…õ d…ôkur p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôr…õb…õ d…ôwaca p…ôcgbap, p…ôgb…õy m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ endem…õŇčk…ôrn…õ d…ôk…õl…õ m…Ē, mba p…ôc…Ēf fonta d…ôn…õnc nd…õ d…Ēnt…Ēnim…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 18 SaŇč oncloku s…Ē afum moloku m…Ēt…Ēt p…ôcyeŇčk…ôs Ňča s…Ē b…ôk…ôc belbel.  
\v 19 Mba k…Ē SaŇč …õnal w…ôb…õ Herodu teta Herodiyad, w…ôran nw…õ …õnabaŇč…ôr w…õnc k'…õn…õnc…õ m…Ē, k…Ē teta mes m…õl…õc m…Ēk…Ē Herodu …õnay…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 20 K…Ē Herodu ende p…ônaŇčkan…õ k…ôl…ôs…ôr: k'osump…ôr SaŇč, k'…õmb…õr k…Ē d…ôbili. 
\s1 K…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka AŇčnabi Yesu 
\r Mat 3.13-17; Mark 1.9-11 
\p  
\v 21 Nt…õ afum Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun teta Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu nk…Ēn s…Ē …Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun. Eyi \k k…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu\k*, k…Ē k…Ēm k…ôŇčgbit…õ,  
\v 22 k…Ē \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňčontor…ôr k…Ē p…ôm…Ē antantoriya. K…Ē dim dontor k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm: ¬ęWan kem m…ôy…Ēn…õ nw…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē, m…ôn'…Ēb…Ēt im mes belbel.¬Ľ 
\s1 Akomb…ôra a AŇčnabi Yesu 
\r Mat 1.1-17 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren 30, a p…ôdecop y…õb…ôc y…Ēn. Wan ka Isifu …õnayi p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē anac…õm-c…õmn…õ ti m…Ē, w…ôka Heli, 
\q1  
\v 24 w…ôka Matat, w…ôka Lewy, 
\q1 w…ôka Melki, w…ôka Yannay, w…ôka Isifu, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 25 w…ôka Matatiyas, w…ôka Am…Ēs, 
\q1 w…ôka Nahum, w…ôka Hes…ôli, w…ôka Nakay, 
\q1  
\v 26 w…ôka Mahat, w…ôka Matatiyas, 
\b  
\q1 w…ôka Semeyin, w…ôka Yos…õk, w…ôka Yoda, 
\q1  
\v 27 w…ôka YohanaŇč, w…ôka Resa, w…ôka Sorobab…õl, 
\b  
\q1 w…ôka Salatiyel, w…ôka Neri, 
\q1  
\v 28 w…ôka Melki, w…ôka Adi, w…ôka Kosam, 
\q1 w…ôka ∆źlmadam, w…ôka Er, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 29 w…ôka Yesu,\f + \fr 3:29 \fq Yesu\ft  = ceHeb…ôre ¬ęYosuwe¬Ľ\f* w…ôka Eliy…õs…õr, w…ôka Yorim, 
\q1 w…ôka Matat, w…ôka Lewy, 
\q1  
\v 30 w…ôka Simey…ĒŇč, w…ôka Yuda, w…ôka Isifu, 
\b  
\q1 w…ôka Yonam, w…ôka Eliyakim, 
\q1  
\v 31 w…ôka Meleya, w…ôka M…õnna, w…ôka Matata, 
\q1 w…ôka Natan, w…ôka Dawuda, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 32 w…ôka Yisay, w…ôka Yobed, w…ôka B…Ēs, 
\q1 w…ôka Sala, w…ôka Nas…ĒŇč, 
\q1  
\v 33 w…ôka Aminadab, w…ôka Admin, 
\b  
\q1 w…ôka Arni, w…ôka Hec…ôr…ĒŇč, 
\q1 w…ôka Per…õc, w…ôka Yuda, 
\q1  
\v 34 w…ôka Yakuba, w…ôka Siyaka, w…ôka Abraham, 
\b  
\q1 w…ôka Terah, w…ôka Nahor, 
\q1  
\v 35 w…ôka Seruk, w…ôka Rehu, w…ôka P…õl…õk, 
\q1 w…ôka Heber, w…ôka Sala, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 36 w…ôka Kayinan, w…ôka Arpaksad, 
\q1 w…ôka Semy, w…ôka Nuha, w…ôka L…õm…õk, 
\q1  
\v 37 w…ôka Metusela, w…ôka Henok, 
\b  
\q1 w…ôka Y…õr…õdu, w…ôka Mahalalel, w…ôka Kenan,\f + \fr 3:37 \fq Kenan\ft  = ceKresi ¬ęKayinam¬Ľ \f* 
\q1  
\v 38 w…ôka En…Ēs, w…ôka S…õt, 
\q1 w…ôka Adama, w…ôka Kanu. 
\c 4  
\s1 Sentani\f + \fr 4:0 \fq Sentani\ft  = ceKresi ¬ędiyabolos¬Ľ = ¬ęw…ôfor¬Ľ, it…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc, Ňči Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôciya, w…ôter ka Kanu w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ.\f* k…ôfaŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ AŇčnabi Yesu k…ôciya 
\r Mat 4.1-11; Mark 1.12-13 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu ender k…ôy…õf…õ Yurd…õn, p…ôlar…õ \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k*. K…Ē Amera ŇčeŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ,  
\v 2 nde Ňä…ĒŇčk Ňä…õl…õc Ňč…õnawak…ôs k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôciya mata w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) disr…õ m…Ē. Ali paka …õnadi f…õ mataka mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, nt…õ mataka mam…Ēk…Ē melip m…Ē, k…Ē dor d…Ēy…Ē k…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē Ňä…ĒŇčk Ňä…õl…õc Ňčoloku k…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a Wan ka Kanu m…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ, m…ôloku oŇč tasar tant…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôcom.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Yesu oloku sentani: ¬ęAncic ti d…ôbuk ba sariy…õ sa Kanu: ‚ÄĻBaf…Ē k…ôcom gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ fum k…ôyi ka doru.‚Äļ¬Ľ\x - \xo 4:4 \xt Sariy…õ 8.3\x* 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē sentani s…ômp…õn…õ k…Ē s…Ē tofo teŇčeci k…ôroŇč, t…õm tepic k…Ē s…ôment…ôr Yesu t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp.  
\v 6 K…Ē s…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęIndes…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôtam f…ôp k…Ē da t…Ēf yay…õ f…ôp, bawo anas…ĒŇč im yi, ina s…Ē ictam k…ôs…ĒŇč yi nw…õ o nw…õ iŇčfaŇč m…Ē.  
\v 7 Awa, k…Ē m…ôna m…ôntontn…õn'em f…Ēr kiriŇč-…õ, yay…õ f…ôp yam y…Ē y…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Yesu oloku sentani: ¬ęAncic d…ôYecic…ôs yosoku: ‚ÄĻMariki Kanu kam p…ômar m…ôctontn…õn…õ f…Ēr kiriŇč, nk…Ēn gb…ôc…ôr…ôm p…ômar m…ôcsal…õn…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē sentani s…ôŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē s…Ē Yerusal…õm, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôc…ômb…ôr k…Ē nde d…ôtelempan pa \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* k…ôroŇč. K…Ē s…ôloku Yesu: ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a Wan ka Kanu m…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ, m…ôyok…õ oŇč ma nn…Ē d…ônt…Ēf. Bawo d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku ancic…ôs:  
\v 10 ‚ÄĻKanu k…ôndesom m…õl…õk…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ Ňčande k…ôcbum …ôm m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 11 K'ancic s…Ē: ‚ÄĻŇäandet…Ēmp…ôr …ôm d…ôwaca nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta m…ômp…ôt tasar m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 12 K…Ē Yesu oloku Sentani: ¬ęAncic…ôs d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku: ‚ÄĻTa m…ôc…ĒŇč…ôs Mariki Kanu kam k…ôy…Ē ka tes t…õw…õy-w…õy t…Ēn.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 13 Nt…õ Ňä…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňčelip k…ôwak…ôs Yesu k…ôciya m…Ē, k…Ē Ňč…Ēmb…Ēl…õ k…Ē haŇč t…õm t…Ēl…Ēma. 
\s1 AŇčnabi Yesu k…ôcop ka y…õb…ôc y…Ēn Kalile 
\r Mat 4.12-17; Mark 1.14-15 
\p  
\v 14 K…Ē Yesu olukus Kalile k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Amera Ňča Kanu disr…õ, k…Ē tewe t…Ēn t…õsam d…Ēt…Ēf f…ôp.  
\v 15 P…ôct…ôks…õ afum nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu daŇčan, k…Ē afum f…ôp ŇčaŇčlel…ôs k…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôb…õl…ôs ka AŇčnabi Yesu nde Nasar…õt 
\r Mat 13.53-58; Mark 6.1-6 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē Yesu ender Nasar…õt nde anadusum k…Ē m…Ē. K'…õmb…õr…õ d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēncy…Ē ti m…Ē. K'…õy…õf…õ k…ôk…ĒkaraŇč dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč,  
\v 17 k'as…ĒŇč k…Ē buk ba w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu Esayi. K'emperi buk, k'…õmb…ôp da ancic: 
\q1  
\v 18 ¬ęAmera Ňča Mariki Ňčey'im k…ôroŇč, 
\q1 bawo Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk im 
\q1 nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ iloku afum at…Ēy…Ē daka toloku t…Ēt…Ēt m…Ē. 
\q1 Kanu k…ôsom im k…ôded…ôŇčk k…ôyac ka acar aŇč…õ asump…ôr d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē.\f + \fr 4:18 \fq K…ôded…ôŇčk k…ôyac ka acar aŇč…õ asump…ôr d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē\ft  k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ¬ęK…ôdeloku acar k…ôsak k…ôŇčan Ňčayi t…õfaŇč taŇčan.¬Ľ \f* 
\q1 Ideloku at…Ēn…ôŇčk a Ňčanden…ôŇčk, 
\q1 k…ôdekek…ôr…õ aŇč…õ Ňčayi k…ôtam disr…õ m…Ē, b…ôk…ôc yoforu disr…õ 
\q1  
\v 19 k…ôded…ôŇčk k…ôren ka k…ômar nk…õ Kanu k…ôndeŇčaŇčn…õn…õ afum s…ôbe ns…õ Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē.¬Ľ\x - \xo 4:19 \xt Esayi 61.1-2\x* 
\b  
\p  
\v 20 Nt…õ Yesu elip k…ôkaraŇč m…Ē, k'…õn…õp buk, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč bi w…ômar…ôs nw…õ …õnat…Ēmp…ôr teta s…ôbuk m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ. Ak…Ē Ňčanayi d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôtn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr Ňča: ¬ęM…Ēk…Ē toloku tecic tat…Ēk…Ē n…ône m…Ē, t…õlar…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē f…ôp f…ôment…ôr k…Ē nt…õ p…ômb…Ēt k…Ē nn…Ē eyi m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ônciyan…õ Ňča moloku m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ moncwur k…Ē d…ôkusu m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčyift…õn…õ: ¬ęBaf…Ē wan ka Isifu …Ēf…Ē ba?¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ a n…ôndelok'im capaf…Ē nc…õ: ‚ÄĻW…ôt…õn c…Ēl, m…ôtam…ôsn…õ m…ônas…ôrka!‚Äļ N…ôndes…Ēlok'im: ‚ÄĻS…ône mes m…Ēk…Ē m…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ Kaparnam m…Ē f…ôp, m…ôy…Ē s…Ē mes min mayi nn…Ē aŇčkom …ôm m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 24 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęKance k'indeloku nu: Ali sayib…õ af…Ēsel…õn…õ belbel nde aŇčkom k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 25 Kance k…Ē kaŇčk…õ indes…Ēloku nu m…Ē: Aran aŇč…õ awos aŇča Ňčanafi Yisrayel m…Ē Ňčanala t…õm ta Eli, t…õm nt…õ k…Ēm k…ônagb…ôtn…õ meren maas yof cam…ôt-tin m…Ē, a k…Ē dor d…Ēp…ĒŇč dosump…ôr at…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 26 Mba k…ônasom f…õ Eli nda nw…õ o nw…õ, m…õn…õ nda w…ôran w…ôt…Ēl…Ē w…ôl…Ēma, nde Sarepta nde at…Ēf Ňča Sid…ĒŇč.  
\v 27 Acun…õ sen alar…ôm Ňčanayi s…Ē Yisrayel t…õm ta sayib…õ Elise. Mba ali w…ôkin Ňča dac…Ē anas…Ēk…ôs f…õ, m…õn…õ Naman w…ôka Siri.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 28 Nt…õ afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, Ňčanane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē m…õt…õl…õ meyi f…ôp faŇčan.  
\v 29 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôb…õl…ôs k…Ē k…ôwur…õn…õ dare, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē teŇčeci ta dare da Nasar…õt k…ôroŇč nde Ňčanac…ômb…ôr dare daŇčan m…Ē, k…ôk…Ēw…õn k…Ē p…ôt…õmp…õn…õ.  
\v 30 K…Ē Yesu …õmb…õr…õ-b…õr…õ Ňča dac…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē. 
\s1 Fum nw…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…õnakaf…ôli-kaf…ôli m…Ē 
\r Mark 1.21-28 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē Yesu ontor dare da Kaparnam at…Ēf Ňča Kalile. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôct…ôks…õ simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm.  
\v 32 Cusu c…ônawos Ňča k…ôt…ôks…õ k…Ēn, bawo moloku m…Ēn m…õnay…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr.  
\v 33 Fum w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi d…ôndo d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, nw…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…õnayi m…Ē, p…ôckul…õ-kul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč:  
\v 34 ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ômb…õr…õn…õ mes mosu-…õ, Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt? D…ôk…ôl…ôs…ôr su m…ônder ba? S…ônc…ôr…õ belbel nw…õ m…ôy…Ēn…õ m…Ē: W…ôcempi w…ôka Kanu!¬Ľ  
\v 35 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňči, p…ôcloku: ¬ęM…ôm…õp kusu! M…ôwur fum w…ôkaw…õ d…ôris!¬Ľ K…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…õŇčgbal fum w…ôkak…Ē d…ônt…Ēf afum dac…Ē, k…Ē Ňčowur k…Ē d…ôris, ali p…ôl…õc Ňč…õnay…Ē f…õ k…Ē.  
\v 36 K…Ē cusu c…ôwos afum f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt…õn…õ: ¬ęAke toloku t…Ē tant…õ-…õ? F…ôn…Ēnt…ôr k…Ē k…ôtam k…Ēn k'oŇčlok-lok…ôr…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc, y…Ēcb…Ēl…õ Ňča.¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē tet…Ēn t…õsam m…Ēmp…Ēmp…Ē ma d…Ēt…Ēf f…ôp. 
\s1 AŇčnabi Yesu k…ôtam…ôs k…Ēn acuy alar…ôm 
\r Mat 8.14-17; Mark 1.29-34 
\p  
\v 38 Nt…õ Yesu …õy…õf…õ d…ôndo d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē ndena Sim…ĒŇč. K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp iya w…ôka w…ôran ka Sim…ĒŇč p…ôcyikc…õn…õ fiba f…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē akak…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôl…õts…õn…õ Yesu a p…ômar k…Ē.  
\v 39 K…Ē Yesu entils…ôrn…õ w…ôran nw…õ k'…õŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr fiba faf…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē fiba f…ôsak k…Ē. Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õy…õf…õ k'eyer…ôs afum yeri. 
\p  
\v 40 Nt…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ē acuy aŇč…õ Ňčanccun…õ docu d…õyamayama m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčken…õ Ňča Yesu. K'endeŇč…ôs…ôr Ňča waca f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčantamn…õ.  
\v 41 K…Ē y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc yolukus afum alar…ôm dar…ôŇč, yockul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęM…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Wan ka Kanu!¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu …õŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr yi, ta oŇčwos…õ a yolok-loku-…õ, bawo y…õnac…ôr…õ a nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ W…ôb…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē. 
\s1 AŇčnabi Yesu k…ôkawandi k…Ēn d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif 
\r Mat 4.23; Mark 1.35-39 
\p  
\v 42 Dec dendes…Ēk, k…Ē Yesu owur k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde k…ôfo k…ôyer-yer k…ôl…Ēma. K…Ē afum alar…ôm Ňčawur k…ôt…õn k…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp k…Ē d…ôndo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē. ŇäanafaŇč f…õ k…ôsak Yesu p…ôk…Ē.  
\v 43 Mba k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôsak im ik…Ēd…ôŇčk s…Ē s…ôdare s…ôl…Ēma moloku m…Ēt…Ēt ma d…õb…õ da Kanu, bawo it…Ē anasom'em.¬Ľ  
\v 44 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčkawandi Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt d…ôndo d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif nde s…ôdare sa Yude. 
\c 5  
\s1 Yesu k…ôwe ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē 
\r Mat 4.18-22; Mark 1.16-20 
\p  
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, Yesu p…ôc…ôm…õ agb…õp Ňča k…ôba ka Kenesar…õt, afum Ňčam…õpn…õ k…Ē Ňčacc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta Kanu.  
\v 2 K'…õn…ôŇčk d…ôndo k…ôba k…ôs…ôk cibil m…õr…ôŇč, nc…õ aw…õnt Ňčanawur disr…õ, Ňčacyak manta maŇčan m…Ē.  
\v 3 K…Ē Yesu …õmb…õk…õ abil Ňčin disr…õ, nŇč…õ Ňč…õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča Sim…ĒŇč m…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē a p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ agb…õp pipic. K'…õnd…õ debil p…ôct…ôks…õ k…ônay k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ônac…ôm…õ d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 4 Nt…õ …õsak k…ôlok-loku m…Ē, k'oloku Sim…ĒŇč: ¬ęM…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ nde p…ôntukm…õ m…Ē, n…ôgbal manta monu n…ôsump…ôr lop.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Sim…ĒŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôkiriŇč, pibi pamp…õ f…ôp s…ôcgbal manta, mba ali paka s…ôs…Ēt…Ē f…õ. Mba nt…õ m…ôloku ti m…Ē, k…ôgbal k'inder manta.¬Ľ  
\v 6 Nt…õ …õŇčgbal manta m…Ē, k'osump…ôr lop y…õlar…ôm haŇč k…Ē manta moncop k…ôwal…õ.  
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčawe anapa aŇčan ak…Ē Ňčanayi abil Ňča m…õr…ôŇč Ňč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ m…Ē, k…ôdemar Ňča. K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčander, k…Ē Ňčalas cibil cac…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč haŇč c…ôcfaŇč k…ôkal…õ.  
\v 8 Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Sim…ĒŇč Piy…õr …õnt…õmp…õn…õ Yesu w…õc…ôk d…ônt…Ēf, k'oloku: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, m…ôb…Ēl'em! Fum w…ôciya iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē kusu k…ôwos k…Ē, nk…Ēn k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanayi m…Ē f…ôp, teta lop y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanasump…ôr m…Ē.  
\v 10 It…Ē p…ônayi s…Ē asol a Sim…ĒŇč, Sak k…Ē IsaŇč, awut a Sebede. K…Ē Yesu oloku Sim…ĒŇč: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ! K…ôy…õf…õ m…Ēk…Ē, afum Ňč…Ē m…ônde m…ôcf…õk…ôs oŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 11 K'asump…ôr lop akak…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ cibil d…õgb…õp, k…Ē Ňčasak ca f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč. 
\s1 Yesu …Ēs…Ēk…ôs w…ôt…Ētamn…õ 
\r Mat 8.1-4; Mark 1.40-45 
\p  
\v 12 Dare d…Ēl…Ēma d…Ē Yesu …õnayi. K…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ sen s…ônasump…ôr dis f…ôp m…Ē, ender. Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk Yesu m…Ē, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf, k'…õnc…ôp…õ Yesu tobu, k'…õl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē: ¬ęMariki, k…Ē m…ôfaŇč ti-…õ, m…ôntam k…ôs…Ēk…ôs im.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Yesu …õnt…õnc k…ôca, k'oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęIfaŇč ti, m…ôs…Ēk!¬Ľ Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē sen s…ôsak fum w…ôkak…Ē.  
\v 14 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa m…ôloku ti fum o fum, mba m…ôk…Ē m…ôment…ôrn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ. M…ôken…õ k…Ē poloŇčn…õ teta k…ôs…Ēk…ôs kam p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa encic ti m…Ē, tendey…Ēn…õ afum f…ôp k…ôc…ôr…õ a m…ôntamn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 15 Tewe t…Ēn t…õncsam k…ôsam d…ôm, afum alar…ôm ŇčacloŇčkan…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē, k…ôt…õn ka k…ôtam…ôs ka docu daŇčan.  
\v 16 Mba k…Ē Yesu owur afum dac…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ \k d…ôk…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu\k*. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôtam…ôs k…Ēn fum nw…õ …õnat…Ētam k…ôk…Ēt m…Ē 
\r Mat 9.1-8; Mark 2.1-12 
\p  
\v 17 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma Yesu p…ôct…ôks…õ. AFarisi k…Ē at…ôks…õ a sariy…õ Ňčand…õ. Ňäay…õf…õ-y…õf…õ s…ôdare sa t…Ēf ya Kalile k…Ē Yude, k…Ē dare da Yerusal…õm. K…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Kanu K…ôp…ĒŇč f…ôyi k…Ē Yesu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôctam…ôs acuy m…Ē.  
\v 18 K…Ē afum Ňčander, ŇčagbaŇčn…õ fum nw…õ efi w…õc…ôk m…Ē d…ôpoko, Ňčacs…õp k…ôb…õr…õ k…ôk…Ēboc k…Ē f…Ēr ya Yesu kiriŇč.  
\v 19 Nt…õ d…õlay da afum d…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôt…Ēs…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamp…õs…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôroŇč, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčafeni k…ôl…Ē darenc k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma, k…Ē Ňčantor…õ w…ôt…Ēk…Ēt nw…õ p…ôyi d…ôyala y…Ēn afum dac…Ē, Yesu f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 20 Nt…õ Yesu …õn…ôŇčk k…ôlaŇč k…ôŇčan m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu oloku fum nw…õ: ¬ęW…ôrkun, aŇčaŇčn…õn'am kiciya kam!¬Ľ  
\v 21 At…ôks…õ sariy…õ k…Ē aFarisi Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ, Ňčacyifn…õ: ¬ęFum w…ôre …Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ …ĒŇčl…Ēm…ôs Mariki m…Ē? An'…õntam k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ kiciya, k…Ē p…ônt…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu sona-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Yesu …õnc…ôr…õ p…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ paŇčan, k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęT'ake t…Ē m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ mam…õ meyin…õ nu-…õ?  
\v 23 Mosom m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē mam…õ, tosom tere t…Ēt…Ēcuca k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻAŇčaŇčn…õn'am kiciya kam,‚Äļ k…Ē k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻM…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôk…Ēt‚Äļ-…õ?  
\v 24 Awa indey…Ē nu tant…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôc…ôr…õ a ina, Wan ka W…ôrkun, int…Ēmp…ôr k…ôtam nn…Ē doru dand…õ k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ka kiciya: K…Ē Yesu oloku w…ôfi w…õc…ôk, ‚ÄĻIlok'…ôm: M…ôy…õf…õ! M…ôl…õk poko pam, m…ôlukus nde ndaram!‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 25 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …õy…õf…õ f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč, k'…õl…õk poko p…Ēn, k'osump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…ôk…Ē nde nd…Ēr…Ēn p…ôckor-koru Kanu.  
\v 26 K…Ē cusu c…ôwos afum f…ôp, k…Ē Ňča s…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôkor-koru Kanu. K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôyi Ňča, Ňčacloku: ¬ęS…ôn…ôŇčk m…Ēk…Ē nt…õ s…ôntat…Ēn…ôŇčk m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôwe k…Ēn Lewy 
\r Mat 9.9-13; Mark 2.13-17 
\p  
\v 27 Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu owur k'…õn…ôŇčk w…ôbaŇč…ôs dut w…ôl…Ēma, nw…õ ancwe Lewy m…Ē, p…ônd…õ nde aŇčgbancan Ňča abaŇč…ôs dut. K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôc…õps'em dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē Lewy …õsak mes f…ôp, k'…õy…õf…õ k'…õnc…õps…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč.  
\v 29 K…Ē Lewy …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôboc…õ Yesu k…ôsata k…ôp…ĒŇč nde nd…Ēr…Ēn. AbaŇč…ôs dut alar…ôm Ňčanayi di, Ňčand…õs-nd…õs d…ôm…õsa k…Ē afum al…Ēma k…Ē Yesu.  
\v 30 AFarisi k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčacc…Ēp…õn…õ, Ňčacyif ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč: ¬ęT'ake t…Ē n…ôndin…õ yeri, n…ôcmun…ôs k…ôfo kin k…Ē abaŇč…ôs dut k…Ē aciya-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 31 Mba Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęBaf…Ē atamn…õ ŇčafaŇč w…ôt…õn c…Ēl de, mba acuy ŇčafaŇč k…Ē.  
\v 32 Baf…Ē alompu Ňč…Ē inder k…ôwe, mba aciya, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčas…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc, Ňčac…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…Ē k…ôsuŇč 
\r Mat 9.14-17; Mark 2.18-22 
\p  
\v 33 K…Ē Ňčaloku Yesu: ¬ęAc…õps…õ a SaŇč dar…ôŇč k…Ē aFarisi, ŇčaŇčsuŇč t…õm f…ôp Ňčacc…ôp…ôs, mba k…Ē aka m…ôna Ňčandi yeri Ňčacmun.¬Ľ  
\v 34 Mba k…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęN…ôntam k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum aŇč…õ awe k…ôgbaŇčn…õ m…Ē k…ôsuŇč, Ňčas…Ēr…Ēyi w…ôfura k…ôs…ôk ba?  
\v 35 D…Ēs…Ēk dendeb…ôp nd…õ Ňčandegb…õy…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôfura m…Ē, awa ŇčandesuŇč d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 36 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča s…Ē capaf…Ē nc…õ: ¬ęAli fum …Ēf…Ēwali k…ôpol d…ôk…ôloto k…ôfu k…ôk…Ēfap…ôr…õ yamos y…õm…ôc…õ-m…ôc…õ. Bawo t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôpol ka k…ôloto k…ôfu kaŇčk…Ē …õwali m…Ē, k…ôt…Ēmar yamos y…õm…ôc…õ-m…ôc…õ yay…Ēk…Ē …õfaŇč k…ôlomp…ôs m…Ē.  
\v 37 Fum o fum …Ēf…Ēb…õr w…õn wofu d…ôt…Ēl…Ēba pa akata pokur. K…Ē m…ôy…Ē ti-…õ, w…õn w…õŇčwes…ôli t…Ēl…Ēba, w…õn woloŇč…õ. M…ôyi oŇč m…ôs…Ēt…Ē f…õ t…Ēl…Ēba, m…ôs…Ēt…Ē f…õ s…Ē w…õn.  
\v 38 M…ôb…õr w…õn wofu d…ôt…Ēl…Ēba pofu!  
\v 39 Fum o fum omun w…õn wokur …Ēf…Ēs…ĒfaŇč wofu, bawo oloku: ‚ÄĻWokur w…õnt…ôŇčn…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\c 6  
\s1 AŇčnabi Yesu k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē 
\r Mat 12.1-8; Mark 2.23-28 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Yesu …õnccali dal…õ d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē,\f + \fr 6:1 \fqa Simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē\ft  sariy…õ s…ôm…Ēn…õ aHeb…ôre f…ôp k…ôb…ôc tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč lokun o lokun. Dif…Ē aŇčwe simiti ¬ęsimiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm¬Ľ.\f* k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôcŇčosuru s…ôbomp sa m…õŇčgb…õn Ňčacs…Ēm.  
\v 2 K…Ē aFarisi al…Ēma Ňčayif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ nt…õ Sariy…õ s…ônt…Ēwos…õ k…ôy…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęN…ôŇčkaraŇč f…õ Yecic…ôs Yosoku disr…õ t…Ēk…Ē Dawuda …õnay…Ē, nt…õ dor d…õnay…Ē k…Ē, nk…Ēn k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanasol m…Ē ba?  
\v 4 ‚ÄĒNt…õ Dawuda …õnab…ôr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…Ē, k'…õl…õk c…ôcom nc…õ ancloŇčn…õ Kanu m…Ē, k'…Ēs…Ēm ci, k'ompoc…õ s…Ē asol …Ēn ak…Ē dor d…õnay…Ē m…Ē, mba aloŇčn…õ gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňč…Ē Sariy…õ s…ônawos…õ k…ôs…Ēm ci.¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęWan ka W…ôrkun …Ēy…Ēn…õ mariki ma d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Fum w…ôfi k…ôca 
\r Mat 12.9-14; Mark 3.1-6 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē dendeb…ôp, k…Ē Yesu …ĒŇčk…Ē nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif p…ôct…ôks…õ afum. W…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi di p…ôd…õmt…ôr k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt.  
\v 7 At…ôks…õ sariy…õ k…Ē aFarisi ŇčaŇčk…Ēkc…õ Yesu belbel, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a …ĒŇčk…Ētam…ôs fum d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē. Ňäanay…Ē ti nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē teyems…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 8 Mba Yesu …õnac…ôr…õ m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ maŇčan, k'oloku w…ôrkun nw…õ …õnad…õmt…ôr k…ôca m…Ē: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ m…ôc…ôm…õ nn…Ē afum dac…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õy…õf…õ, k'…õnc…ôm…õ.  
\v 9 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęIcyif nu ma: C…ôke c…Ē Sariy…õ s…ôwos…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē-…õ? K…ôy…Ē ka p…ôt…Ēt ba, ka p…ôl…õc? Patam…ôs fum ba, ka pace k…Ē p…ôfi?¬Ľ  
\v 10 Awa, k…Ē Yesu …Ēm…Ēm…ôn Ňča d…ôc…ôro f…ôp faŇčan, k'oloku w…ôrkun nw…õ: ¬ęM…ôtenci k…ôca!¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ entenci ki, k…Ē k…ôca k…Ēn k…ôntamn…õ.  
\v 11 Mba k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ acic…ôs a sariy…õ k…Ē aFarisi p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ teta p…ôl…õc mp…õ Ňčantam k…ôy…Ē Yesu m…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôy…õk-y…õk Asom …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč 
\r Mat 10.1-4; Mark 3.13-19 
\p  
\v 12 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Yesu …õmp…õ nde d…ôt…Ēr…Ē k…ôk…Ēsali, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ pibi f…ôp k…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu.  
\v 13 Nt…õ dec d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, k'ewe ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč, k'…õy…õk-y…õk Ňča dac…Ē afum w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, aŇč…õ …õnas…ĒŇč tewe ta ¬ęasom¬Ľ m…Ē.  
\v 14 K'ewe Sim…ĒŇč, nw…õ Yesu …õnas…ĒŇč tewe ta Piy…õr m…Ē, k…Ē w…õnc And…ôre, Sak, IsaŇč k…Ē Filip, Bartelemy,  
\v 15 Matiye, T…Ēma, Sak wan ka Alfe, Sim…ĒŇč w…ôsims…õ teta at…Ēf,  
\v 16 Yude wan ka Sak, k…Ē Yudas w…ôka dare da Keriyot nw…õ …õnader p…ôl…ôps…ôr k…ôb…õr Yesu ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca m…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu p…ôct…ôks…õ p…ôctam…ôs 
\r Mat 4.23-25 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē Yesu Ňčantor k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôt…Ēr…Ē k…Ē Ňča, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ôm…õ k…ôfo k…ôt…ôŇčn…õn…õ nk…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč alar…ôm, k…Ē k…ônay ka afum alar…ôm: Afum aka Yude f…ôp, dare da Yerusal…õm, k…Ē afum aka k…ôba k…ôs…ôk nde s…ôdare sa Tir k…Ē Sid…ĒŇč.  
\v 18 Afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp Ňčanader k…ôdec…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē, p…ôtam…ôs…õn…õ s…Ē docu daŇčan. Afum aŇč…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…Ēnct…Ēr…ôs m…Ē, Ňčanatamn…õ.  
\v 19 Afum f…ôp Ňčacs…õp k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ē, bawo f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôncwur k…Ē nf…õ f…ônctam…ôs acuy f…ôp m…Ē. 
\s1 P…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôl…õc 
\r Mat 5.1-12 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Yesu …Ēm…Ēm…ôn ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč, k'oloku: 
\q1 ¬ęP…ôb…Ēt nu n…ôna at…Ēy…Ē daka, 
\q2 bawo n…ôn'eyi akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf! 
\q1  
\v 21 P…ôb…Ēt n…ôna aŇč…õ dor d…Ēy…Ē tant…õ m…Ē, 
\q2 bawo n…ônden…õmb…ôr…õ! 
\q1 P…ôb…Ēt nu, n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôyi k…ôbok m…Ē, 
\q2 bawo n…ôndesel! 
\p  
\v 22 P…ôb…Ēt nu k…Ē afum Ňčandeter nu-…õ, Ňčacb…õl…ôs nu, Ňčacl…Ēm…ôs nu, Ňčacl…ôs…ôr nu mewe bawo n…ôlaŇč dim da ¬ęWan ka W…ôrkun.¬Ľ  
\v 23 N…ôde n…ôwol…ôs k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē dendeder-…õ, n…ôyok-yok…õn…õ p…ôbotu, bawo k…ôpoc…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôŇčkar nu nde darenc. Tant…õ t…Ē atem aŇčan Ňčancy…Ē ad…ôŇčk a Kanu. 
\q1  
\v 24 P…ôl…õc peyi nu n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôy…Ē daka m…Ē! 
\q1 Bawo n…ôlip k…ôs…Ēt…Ē p…õn…õmp…ôs…õ ponu mp…õ p…ônamar nu k…ôdek…Ēs…Ēt…Ē m…Ē. 
\q1  
\v 25 P…ôl…õc peyi nu n…ôna aŇč…õ ca f…ôp y…õlar m…Ē, 
\q1 bawo dor dendek…Ēy…Ē nu! 
\q1 P…ôl…õc peyi nu n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôyi k…ôsel m…Ē, 
\q1 bawo n…ôndek…Ēyi k…ôbal k…Ē k…ôbok disr…õ! 
\q1  
\v 26 P…ôl…õc peyi nu n…ôna aŇč…õ afum f…ôp Ňčandeloku p…ôt…Ēt ponu m…Ē, 
\q1 tant…õ t…Ē atem aŇčan Ňčancy…Ē k…Ē ak…Ē ŇčancbaŇč…õn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ Sayib…õ sa Kanu m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka aŇč…õ Ňčanter nu m…Ē 
\r Mat 5.38-48; 7.12 
\p  
\v 27 ¬ęMba, iŇčloku ti n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl im m…Ē: N…ôb…Ēt…ôr ater…õn…õ anu, n…ôy…Ē p…ôt…Ēt aŇč…õ Ňčanter nu m…Ē!  
\v 28 N…ôtolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt aŇč…õ Ňčantolan…õ nu p…õl…õc m…Ē, n…ôtolan…õ aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčl…Ēm…ôs nu m…Ē!  
\v 29 K…Ē fum efer …ôm k…ôca d…ôkanca-…õ, m…ôcenc…õ k…Ē s…Ē akanca Ňča m…õr…ôŇč Ňč…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē fum …õl…õk…ôr …ôm burumus-…õ, m…ôce k…Ē s…Ē p…ôl…õk duma dam.  
\v 30 M…ôpoc…õ nw…õ o nw…õ ontol'am m…Ē, k…Ē fum …õl…õk…ôr …ôm paka mp…õ p…Ēy…Ēn…õ pam m…Ē, ta m…ôwer…ôs k…Ē pi.  
\v 31 N…ôy…Ēn…õ afum t…Ēk…Ē n…ôfaŇč a Ňčay…Ēn…õ nu m…Ē.  
\v 32 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ n…ôb…Ēt…ôr gb…ôc…ôr…ôm ak…Ē Ňčamb…Ēt…ôr nu m…Ē, k…ôway k…ôre k…Ē n…ôŇčgb…õk…ôr s…Ē mera-…õ? Ali aciya Ňčamb…Ēt…ôr aŇč…õ Ňčamb…Ēt…ôr Ňča m…Ē!  
\v 33 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a ak…Ē ŇčaŇčy…Ēn…õ nu p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňč…Ē m…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ p…ôt…Ēt-…õ, k…ôway k…ôre k…Ē m…ôntam k…ôgb…õk…ôr amera-…õ? Ali aciya, baf…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē ŇčaŇčy…Ē p…ôm…Ē n…ôna ba?  
\v 34 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a ak…Ē n…ôy…Ē amera k…ôdeluks…õ nu m…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňč…Ē n…ôntam k…ôb…Ēr-…õ, k…ôway k…ôre k…Ē n…ôna n…ôntam k…ôgb…õk…ôr amera-…õ? Bawo ali aciya s…Ē Ňčamb…Ēr aciya nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôdes…Ēt…Ē p…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ payi m…Ē.  
\v 35 N…ôb…Ēt…ôr ater anu, n…ôb…Ēr Ňča n…ôwur…õ k…ôluks…õ debe dad…Ēk…Ē amera. N…ôndes…Ēt…Ē k…ôpoc…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč, n…ôy…Ēn…õ s…Ē awut a W…ôb…õ w…ôka darenc, bawo Kanu k…ôntes…õ nn…Ē ap…ôl…ôrn…õ p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē ayeŇčki b…ôk…ôc Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 36 N…ôb…Ēt mera p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Papa konu …Ēmb…Ēt amera m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Ta n…ôcin afum al…Ēma 
\r Mat 7.1-5 
\p  
\v 37 ¬ęTa n…ôcin fum, af…Ēk…Ēcin nu. Ta n…ôkiti ak…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta andes…Ēkiti n…ôna m…Ē. N…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ak…Ē, andek…ĒŇčaŇčn…õn…õ nu.  
\v 38 N…ôpoc…õ, andek…Ēpoc…õ nu. Andek…Ēb…õr nde yuba yonu y…Ēp…ĒŇč ya duma donu potubc…õ p…Ēt…Ēt, pasump…ôr, pas…ôŇčk-s…ôŇčk, p…ôloŇč…ôr. Bawo potubc…õ mp…õ n…ôntubc…õ m…Ē, ip'andek…Ēs…Ētubc…õ nu k…ôluks…õ nu k…ôway.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 39 K…Ē Yesu olok-lok…ôr Ňča capaf…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk …õntam k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk ba? K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp m…Ē Ňčant…õmp…õn…õ abi disr…õ.  
\v 40 Ali w…ôc…õps…õ dar…ôŇč w…ôkin eyi f…õ nw…õ …õmb…õk d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôtas w…ôt…ôks…õ k…Ēn m…Ē, mba w…ôc…õps…õ dar…ôŇč nw…õ …õnt…ôks…õ belbel m…Ē, eyi p…ôm…Ē w…ôt…ôks…õ k…Ēn.  
\v 41 Ake's…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õ ayika nŇč…õ Ňčeyi w…õnc …ôm d…ôr…Ēf…Ēr m…Ē, mba ta m…ôŇčn…ôŇčk t…ômboŇčk ta k…ôt…Ēk mp…õ peyi m…ônas…ôrka d…ôr…Ēf…Ēr m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 42 P…ôlompu p…Ē ba, k…ôloku w…õnc …ôm: ‚ÄĻW…õnc im m…ôwos…õ a iliŇč …ôm ayika nŇč…õ Ňčey'…ôm d…ôr…Ēf…Ēr m…Ē,‚Äļ mba d…Ēf…Ēr da m…ôna d…Ēy…Ē t…ômboŇčk ta k…ôt…Ēk? M…ôna w…ôbaŇč…õn…õ k…ôlomp! M…ôliŇčn…õ k…ôr…õsna t…ômboŇčk ta k…ôt…Ēk d…Ēf…Ēr dam, it'…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôn…ôŇčk belbel ayika Ňč…Ēk…Ē m…ôfaŇč k…ôliŇč w…õnc …ôm d…ôr…Ēf…Ēr m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôt…Ēk k…Ē yokom ya ki 
\r Mat 7.16-20; 12.33-35 
\p  
\v 43 ¬ęK…ôt…Ēk k…ôt…Ēt k…ôf…Ēkom yokom y…õl…õc, k…ôt…Ēk k…ôt…Ētamn…õ k…ôf…Ēkom yokom y…Ēt…Ēt.  
\v 44 K…ôt…Ēk nk…õ o nk…õ k…Ē, yokom ya ki y'aŇčn…õp…ôl…õ ki. Af…Ēpim c…Ēyab…õ\f + \fr 6:44 \fq C…Ēyab…õ \ft  = C…ôTabo ¬ęfigue¬Ľ\f* k…Ē w…õn \f + \fr 6:44 \ft  Pokom mp…õ poŇčkom nde Yisrayel, pi p…Ēk…Ē aŇčf…Ēc k…ôs…Ēt…Ē member mm…õ aŇčwe ¬ęwen¬Ľ m…Ē.\f* d…ôb…õŇčk.  
\v 45 Fum w…ôt…Ēt nde ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēn Ňč…Ēt…Ēt …õŇčl…õk m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēt…Ēt, k…Ē fum w…ôl…õc nde ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēn Ňč…õl…õc …õŇčl…õk m…Ēy…Ē m…õl…õc. Bawo nt…õ o nt…õ kusu k…ôŇčloku m…Ē, ti teyi nde d…õb…ôk…ôc.¬Ľ 
\s1 W…Ēl…Ē m…õr…ôŇč 
\r Mat 7.24-27 
\p  
\v 46 ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčwen'em ‚ÄĻMariki! Mariki!‚Äļ ta n…ôŇčy…Ē mes m…Ēk…Ē iŇčloku m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 47 Nw…õ o nw…õ eder im, p…ône moloku mem, p…ôk…Ēt mi, iment…ôr nu nw…õ oŇčwur…õn…õ m…Ē:  
\v 48 Owur…õn…õ fum nw…õ eyi k…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē p…ôkay d…ônt…Ēf haŇč p…ôtukm…õ belbel, p…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn tasar teyeŇčki k…ôroŇč. Ali w…ôcaf…ôn p…ôtuf p…ôlar…ôm, m…ôncaca m…õy…õks…õ, k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k…ôf…Ētam k…ôwuŇč…õ, bawo anac…ômb…ôr ki gbiŇč.  
\v 49 Mba nw…õ o nw…õ ene moloku mem, ta …ĒŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ mi-…õ, fum w…ôkak…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ k…Ē nw…õ …õnc…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn katina d…ônt…Ēf, ta …õŇčkay p…ôtukm…õ p…ôc…ômb…ôr ki tasar k…ôroŇč m…Ē. K…Ē w…ôcaf…ôn ontuf, m…ôncaca m…õy…õks…õ-…õ, k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčwuŇč…õ katina, k…ôl…õc…õ few!¬Ľ 
\c 7  
\s1 AŇčnabi Yesu k…ôtam…ôs k…Ēn w…ôcar ka w…ôb…õ ka as…Ēdar 100 
\r Mat 8.5-13 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Yesu elip k…ôlok-lok…ôr afum aŇč…õ Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr…õ dare da Kaparnam.  
\v 2 D…ôndo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē, w…ôb…õ k'as…Ēdar w…ôRom w…ôl…Ēma …õnay…Ē w…ôcar nw…õ tet…Ēn t…õnayeŇčk k…Ē m…Ē. W…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē …õnatamn…õ f…õ, p…ôcfaŇč k…ôfi.  
\v 3 Nt…õ w…ôb…õ k'as…Ēdar nw…õ ene pacloku teta Yesu m…Ē, k'osom abeki aSuyif al…Ēma, Ňčak…Ēwen…õ k…Ē Yesu p…ôdetam…ôs…õ k…Ē w…ôcar k…Ēn.  
\v 4 K…Ē abeki akak…Ē Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Yesu k…Ē Ňčal…õts…õn…õ k…Ē Ňčacgb…Ēk…ôr…õ, Ňčacloku: ¬ę∆Üy…Ē dofum nd…õ p…ômar m…ôy…Ēn…õ k…Ē ti m…Ē,  
\v 5 bawo w…ôb…õ w…ôkaw…õ …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr at…Ēf Ňčosu, nk…Ēn …õnac…ômb…ôr d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif dosu.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Yesu …ĒŇčk…Ē k…Ē Ňča. Ňäanab…Ēl…õn…õ f…õ k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar, k…Ē w…ôs…Ēdar osom anapa …Ēn k…ôk…Ēloku k…Ē: ¬ęMariki, ta m…ôt…Ēr…ôsn…õ, bawo is…Ēt…Ē f…õ dofum d…õfayn…õn'am nde k…ôl…Ē kem disr…õ.  
\v 7 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ inas…ôrka int…Ēnak…Ē nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē. Mba m…ôloku toloku tin, w…ôb…ôc…õ kem …õntamn…õ.  
\v 8 Bawo ina w…ôkaw…õ yati ab…õ em Ňč'iyi d…ônt…Ēf, k'ina s…Ē iy…Ē as…Ēdar al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčay'im d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē. K'iloku w…ôkin: ‚ÄĻM…ôk…Ē,‚Äļ w…ôkayi …ĒŇčk…Ē. K'iloku w…ôk…Ē ‚ÄĻM…ôder,‚Äļ w…ôkayi ender. K'iloku w…ôcar kem: ‚ÄĻM…ôy…Ē nt…õ-…õ,‚Äļ …ĒŇčy…Ē ti.¬Ľ  
\v 9 Nt…õ Yesu ene moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē teta w…ôs…Ēdar nw…õ tenciyan…õ k…Ē. K'…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ, k'…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ k…ônay k'afum ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęIcloku nu, ali nde Yisrayel inan…ôŇčk f…õ k…ôlaŇč p…ôm…Ē kaŇčk…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē asom a w…ôs…Ēdar nw…õ, Ňčalukus nd…Ēr…Ēn. K…Ē Ňčab…ôp w…ôcar nw…õ …õnat…Ē-tamn…õ m…Ē, p…ôtamn…õ keŇč. 
\s1 Yesu …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôfi k…ôf…Ēt…õ 
\p  
\v 11 Nt…õ telip m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē dare nd…õ ancwe Nayin m…Ē. At…ôk…ôs …Ēn k…Ē afum alar…ôm Ňčanasol k…Ē nk…Ēn k…ôk…Ē.  
\v 12 Nt…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôb…õr…õ ka dare m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē afum Ňčanckek…ôr…õ fum w…ôfi d…ôk…ôwup, mba fum nw…õ sona gboŇč s…Ē k…õr…õ …õnakom k…Ē, wos p…ôfi s…Ē. Afum alar…ôm a dare dad…Ēk…Ē Ňčanckek…ôr…õ w…ôfi w…ôkak…Ē d…ôk…ôwup.  
\v 13 K…Ē Yesu …õn…ôŇčk w…ôran nw…õ, k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa m…ôbok!¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē Yesu …Ēnc…ĒŇčn…õ k'oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ kaŇčk…ôra ka w…ôfi. AŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr k…Ē m…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ. K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęW…ôt…õmp, in'olok'…ôm: M…ôy…õf…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôfi …õy…õf…õ k'…õnd…õ, k'oncop k…ôlok-loku. K…Ē Yesu oluks…õ w…ôfi nw…õ k…õr…õ.  
\v 16 K…Ē f…ôp f…ônes…õ, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ \k k…ôcam debeki\k* da Kanu, Ňčacloku: ¬ęW…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu w…ôp…ĒŇč …õy…õf…õ su dac…Ē! K…Ē Kanu k…ônder k…ômar afum …Ēn!¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ē ta Yesu tat…Ēk…Ē t…õsam at…Ēf Ňča Yude f…ôp, k…ôb…ôp ka s…ôdare s…ôk…Ē s…ôŇčk…õl Yude m…Ē. 
\s1 Asom a AŇčnabi SaŇč 
\r Mat 11.2-19 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē ac…õps…õ a AŇčnabi SaŇč dar…ôŇč ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē SaŇč ewe ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč dac…Ē afum m…õr…ôŇč,  
\v 19 k'osom Ňča k…ôk…Ēyif Mariki k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ eyi k…ôder k…ôdeyac afum a Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ f…õ nk…Ēn-…õ, p…ômar pakar s…Ē w…ôl…Ēma ba?  
\v 20 Nt…õ Ňčamb…ôp Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęSaŇč Batis osom su k…ôdeyif …ôm: ‚ÄĻM…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ eyi k…ôder m…Ē, ka p…ômar s…ôkar s…Ē w…ôl…Ēma ba?‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 21 Afum akak…Ē anasom m…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp Yesu p…ôctam…ôs docu da at…Ētamn…õ alar…ôm, lanyiru, aŇč…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…õnc…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēn…ôŇčk alar…ôm k…ôn…ôŇčk.  
\v 22 K…Ē Yesu oluks…õ Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôloku SaŇč t…Ēk…Ē n…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ône m…Ē: 
\q1 At…Ēn…ôŇčk Ňčan…ôŇčk, at…Ētam k…ôk…Ēt ŇčaŇčk…Ēt, 
\q1 k'as…Ēk…ôs acun…õ sen, at…Ēne Ňčane, 
\q1 afi Ňčaf…Ēt…õ, aŇčkawandi Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt nn…Ē at…Ēy…Ē daka Ňčayi m…Ē. 
\m  
\v 23 P…ôb…Ēt nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēdesak k…ôgb…õk…ôr im k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn \f + \fr 7:23 \ft  k…ôsol…õ\f* m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 24 Nt…õ asom a SaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčalukus m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…ôloku k…ônay ka afum teta SaŇč p…ôcyif: ¬ęAke n…ônak…Ē k…ôm…Ēm…ôn nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ-…õ: Fum nw…õ …õfan…õ p…ôm…Ē awo nŇč…õ afef Ňčeyik…ôc m…Ē ba?  
\v 25 Mba an…Ē n…ônak…Ē oŇč k…ôm…Ēm…ôn di-…õ, w…ôrkun w…ôs…ôk…ôp belbel ba? Mba n…ôc…ôr…õ a as…ôk…ôp belbel nde w…Ēl…Ē w'ab…õ w…Ē Ňčand…õ p…ôt…Ēt disr…õ.  
\v 26 Mba an…Ē n…ônak…Ē oŇč k…ôm…Ēm…ôn-…õ, Sayib…õ ba? ∆źy, icloku nu, SaŇč encep…ôr Sayib…õ f…ôp d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ.  
\v 27 Tet…Ēn t'ancic…ôs nde Yecic…ôs Yosoku disr…õ: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻIndekek…ôr…õ w…ôsom kem f…Ēr yam kiriŇč 
\q1 p…ôk…Ēlomps'am d…Ēp…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ\x - \xo 7:27 \xt Malaki 3.1\x* 
\p  
\v 28 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęIcloku nu, aŇč…õ aran ŇčaŇčkom m…Ē f…ôp, ali w…ôkin eyi f…õ nw…õ encep…ôr SaŇč d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ē. Mba nw…õ …õf…õt…õ nde d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, …Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ encep…ôr SaŇč d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ē.  
\v 29 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanane k…Ē k…ôlok-loku m…Ē f…ôp, k…ôb…ôp awer…ôs dut, k…Ē Ňčawos…õ dolompu da Kanu. Ti disr…õ k…Ē Ňčawos…õ a SaŇč p…ôgb…ôt Ňča d…ôromun teta Kanu.  
\v 30 Mba aFarisi k…Ē at…ôks…õ a sariy…õ Ňčanawos…õ f…õ nt…õ Kanu k…ônafaŇč…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčafati a SaŇč p…ôgb…ôt Ňča d…ôromun teta Kanu.  
\v 31 An'indetubc…õn…õ afum a d…õt…õmp dand…õ-…õ? An…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ-…õ?  
\v 32 AŇč…õ Ňč…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ: Ňäawur…õn…õ awut aŇč…õ Ňčand…õ k…ôfo nk…õ afum f…ôp Ňčamb…ôps…õn…õ m…Ē, a Ňčacwen…õn…õ k…ôk…Ēloku: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻS…ôfulan…õ nu luk, k…Ē n…ônt…Ēpis…õ! 
\p K…Ē s…ôleŇčs…õ nu meleŇč ma defi, k…Ē n…ônt…Ēbok.‚Äļ  
\v 33 Bawo nt…õ SaŇč Batis, nw…õ …õncgb…ôt afum d…ôromun …õnader m…Ē, oncsuŇč, ta oŇčmun w…õn-…õ, k…Ē n…ôloku a …Ēy…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc!  
\v 34 K…Ē Wan ka W…ôrkun ender, p…ôcdi yeri p…ôcmun w…õn k…Ē n…ôloku: ‚ÄĻW…ôc…õl…ôk k…Ē w…ôcis …Ēf…Ē, wanapa ka abaŇč…ôs dut k'aciya!‚Äļ  
\v 35 Mba awut a k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes ka Kanu Ňčawos…õ dolompu da ki.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu nde k…ôl…Ē ka Sim…ĒŇč w…ôFarisi 
\p  
\v 36 K…Ē w…ôFarisi w…ôl…Ēma ewe Yesu k…ôk…Ēdi yeri k…Ē nk…Ēn. K…Ē Yesu …õmb…õr…õ nde k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôFarisi w…ôkak…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ am…õsa kiriŇč.  
\v 37 W…ôran w…ôciya w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi dare dad…Ēk…Ē, k'ene a Yesu Ňčayi k…ôdi yeri nde k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôFarisi. W…ôran w…ôkak…Ē …õl…õk t…Ēk…Ēb…Ē pa alabat…ôr p…õlar…õ labund…õ,  
\v 38 k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ôm…õ Yesu kumunt dar…ôŇč p…ôsump…ôr k…Ē w…õc…ôk. K'…õy…õf…õ k…ôbok p…ôccaŇčk…ôs…õ m…õnc…ôr m…Ēn w…õc…ôk wa Yesu, k'…õf…õŇč…ôt…õ w…õc…ôk wa Yesu c…ôfon c…Ēn, p…ôccup wi, p…ôcloŇčs…ôr wi labund…õ.  
\v 39 Nt…õ w…ôFarisi nw…õ …õnawe Yesu nde nd…Ēr…Ēn, …õn…ôŇčk tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'olokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu-…õ, k'…õnc…ôr…õ w…ôran nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, fum nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ m…Ē‚ÄĒW…ôran w…ôciya.¬Ľ  
\v 40 K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk moloku, k'oloku: ¬ęSim…ĒŇč, iy…Ē toloku t…Ēl…Ēma tolok'…ôm.¬Ľ K…Ē Sim…ĒŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôlok'im ti, W…ôt…ôks…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 41 ¬ęW…ôb…Ēs-b…Ēs…ôr w…ôl…Ēma afum m…õr…ôŇč Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr…õ debe: W…ôkin nw…õ p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õ k…Ē gbeti m…õnc…ômb…ôl masar k…ôcam…ôt (500), k…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õ k…Ē m…õnc…ômb…ôl 50.  
\v 42 Mba nt…õ w…ôb…Ēs-b…Ēs…ôr nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk f…Ē al…õk…ôr …Ēn s…ôbe Ňčay…Ē f…õ gbeti boluks…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k'…õŇčaŇčn…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp. Akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč an…Ē endenaŇčkan…õ k…ôb…Ēt…ôr k…Ē p…ôtas w…ôk…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 43 K…Ē Sim…ĒŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęP…ôwur…õn'em, a w…ôk…Ē …õnat…Ēmp…ôr…õ k…Ē gbeti b…õlar…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęGb…õs, m…ôloku kance!¬Ľ  
\v 44 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ k'…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ w…ôran nw…õ, k'oloku Sim…ĒŇč: ¬ęM…ôn…ôŇčk w…ôran nw…õ? Imb…õr…õna nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē kam mba m…ôs…ĒŇčna f'em domun ibik…õn…õ w…õc…ôk, mba nk…Ēn …õncaŇčk…ôs…õ w…õc…ôk wem m…õnc…ôr m…Ēn, k'…õf…õŇč…ôt…õ wi c…ôfon c…Ēn.  
\v 45 M…ôncupna f'em, mba nk…Ēn k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ imb…õr…õna nn…Ē m…Ē, a k'oncop k…ôcup…ôs im w…õc…ôk m…Ē, haŇč nd…õk…ôl it…Ē eyi k…ôy…Ē.  
\v 46 M…ôsopna f'em moro d…ôromp,\f + \fr 7:46 \ft  Aka Yisrayel moro m…Ē Ňčancsop acik…ôra aŇčan alel\f* mba w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ osop im labund…õ d…ôw…õc…ôk.  
\v 47 It…Ē …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ intam k…ôlok'…ôm a, kiciya k…ôlar…ôm nk…õ enciya m…Ē, aŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē ki, bawo nk…Ēn …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr p…ônaŇčkan…õ. M…ôna nw…õ aŇčaŇčn…õn…õ pipic m…Ē, pipic p…Ē m…ômb…Ēt…ôr.¬Ľ  
\v 48 K…Ē Yesu oloku w…ôran nw…õ: ¬ęAŇčaŇčn…õn'am kiciya kam.¬Ľ  
\v 49 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ am…õsa kiriŇč k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē, Ňčancop k…ôclokun…õ d…ôb…ôk…ôc: ¬ęAn'…Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ …õŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ali kiciya m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 50 Mba k…Ē Yesu oloku w…ôran: ¬ęK…ôlaŇč kam k…ôyac …ôm, m…ôk…Ēn…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčoforu.¬Ľ 
\c 8  
\s1 Aran aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčsol k…Ē Yesu m…Ē 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu ende p…ôck…Ēt s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē s…ôf…õt sa d…Ēt…Ēf f…ôp, p…ôckawandi p…ôcd…ôŇčk Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt ka d…õb…õ da Kanu. Ňäasol k…Ē Asom …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč,  
\v 2 k…ôb…õr…õn…õ ka aran al…Ēma aŇč…õ …õnatam…ôs docu da dis k…Ē da y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc m…Ē: Mari w…ôk…Ē ancwe ¬ęW…ôka Makdala¬Ľ m…Ē, nw…õ anab…õl…ôs y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē,  
\v 3 Yohanna (w…ôran ka Cusa, w…ôlomp…ôs ka mes ma k…ôl…Ē disr…õ ka Herodu), Susan k…Ē aran alar…ôm al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčancwur…õ daka daŇčan k…ômar ka Yesu k…Ē Asom …Ēn m…Ē. 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca w…ôb…Ēf 
\r Mat 13.1-9; Mark 4.1-9 
\p  
\v 4 K…Ē k…ônay ka afum alar…ôm ay…õf…õ s…ôdare s…ôl…Ēma Ňčam…õp…ôn…õ k…Ē. K…Ē Yesu oloku totubc…õn…õ nt…õ:  
\v 5 ¬ęNt…õ w…ôb…Ēf owur k…ôk…Ēgbal defet d…Ēn m…Ē, eyi k…ôgbal defet k…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēl…Ēma m…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…Ēp…Ē. Afum Ňčacnas-nas mi, k…Ē b…õmp yender y…Ēs…Ēm mi.  
\v 6 K…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēl…Ēma m…õnt…õmp…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňča masar k…ôroŇč. Nt…õ mompoŇč m…Ē, k…Ē mowos, bawo m…õnas…Ēt…Ē f…õ p…ôd…ôm.  
\v 7 K…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēl…Ēma m…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…ôb…õŇčk, k…Ē b…õŇčk yompoŇč k…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē yendi mi.  
\v 8 K…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēl…Ēma m…õnt…õmp…õn…õ ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēt…Ēt k…ôroŇč. Nt…õ mam…Ēk…Ē mompoŇč m…Ē, k…Ē yoŇčkom…ôs, k…Ē popoŇč mp…õ o mp…õ poŇčkom m…õŇčgb…õn tasar tin (100).¬Ľ Yesu oncloku toloku tat…Ēk…Ē, p…ôcgb…ôŇč…õ: ¬ęM…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē l…ôŇč…ôs yenen…õ m…Ē, m…ône ti!¬Ľ 
\s1 Ta ake t…Ē Yesu onclok…õ totubc…õn…õ-…õ? 
\r Mat 13.10-17; Mark 4.10-12 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē ac…õps…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčayif k…Ē nt…õ totubc…õn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē toloku m…Ē.  
\v 10 K'oluks…õ Ňča: ¬ęN…ôna Ňč…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ kance k…ôgb…Ēpn…õ ka d…õb…õ d…Ēn, mba k…Ē ak…Ē d…ômotubc…õn…õ aloku Ňča ki, ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻŇäaŇčgb…ôtn…õ belbel mba Ňčaf…Ēn…ôŇčk, 
\q1 Ňčac…ôŇčk…ôl belbel mba Ňčaf…Ēc…ôr…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôloku tedisr…õ ta capaf…Ē ca w…ôb…Ēf 
\p  
\v 11 ¬ęTedisr…õ ta totubc…õn…õ tant…õ t…õnt…õ: Defet, Toloku ta Kanu t…Ē.  
\v 12 M…õŇčgb…õn mm…õ m…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…Ēp…Ē dac…Ē m…Ē, mi m…Ēy…Ēn…õ afum aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčne m…Ē, Ňä…ĒŇčk Ňä…õl…õc Ňčeder ŇčeliŇč Ňča d…ôb…ôk…ôc Toloku ta Kanu t…Ēk…Ē …õnane m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ payam…ôs…ôr Ňča k…ôlaŇč nk…õ k…ôntam k…ôyac Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 13 M…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēk…Ē meyi k…ôfo ka masar m…Ē, m…Ēy…Ēn…õ afum aŇč…õ Ňčanck…Ēnane Toloku ta Kanu, p…ôb…Ēt Ňča m…Ē. Mba Ňčay…Ē f…õ nc…Ēnc,\f + \fr 8:13 \fqa K…ônt…õnt…ôl, nt…õnt…ôl\ft  = ¬ęk…ôc…Ēnc¬Ľ, ¬ęnc…Ēnc¬Ľ\f* ŇčalaŇč t…õm t…Ēl…Ēma, k…Ē t…õm teyeŇčki tender Ňča-…õ, Ňčasak ti few.  
\v 14 M…õŇčgb…õn mm…õ m…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…ôb…õŇčk m…Ē, mi m…Ēy…Ēn…õ afum aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl Toloku ta Kanu, k…Ē Ňčalas…ôrn…õ mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč mm…õ mendi toloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē: M…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õlar…ôm, k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka daka k…Ē m…õfaŇč mobotu ma doru, m…Ēf…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ti k…ôkom yokom yololu.  
\v 15 M…õŇčgb…õn mm…õ meyi ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēt…Ēt m…Ē, afum Ňč…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl…õ Toloku ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēt…Ēt Ňčosoku, Ňčam…õŇčk…ôrn…õ ti, Ňčac…ôm…õ ti dar…ôŇč m…Ē, Ňča ŇčaŇčs…ĒŇč yokom y…Ēt…Ēt.¬Ľ 
\s1 Totubc…õn…õ ta lamp 
\r Mark 4.21-25 
\p  
\v 16 ¬ęNw…õ o nw…õ …Ēf…Ēmot lamp a p…ôgb…ôp…ôr di k…ôfala, …Ēf…Ēs…Ēb…õrs…õn…õ di k…ôf…ônc d…ônt…Ēf, mba …õnd…õt di k…ôd…õt d…ôm, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aŇč…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ d…ôk…ôl…Ē m…Ē, Ňčan…ôŇčkn…õ p…ôwaŇčk…ôra.  
\v 17 Paka mp…õ o mp…õ p…ĒŇčgb…Ēpn…õ m…Ē, andetam pi k…ôn…ôŇčk. Tes nt…õ o nt…õ aŇčm…õŇčk m…Ē, andetam ti k…ôc…ôr…õ, towur t…Ēy…Ē afum waŇčk…ôra.  
\v 18 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ t…Ēk…Ē n…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl m…Ē, bawo andek…Ēb…õr…õn…õ w…ôk…Ē …Ēy…Ē m…Ē, pabel…ôr w…ôk…Ē …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē m…Ē ali p…Ēk…Ē …õŇčgb…õk…ôr amera k…ôy…Ēn…õ p…Ēn m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Iya k…Ē aw…õnc a Yesu 
\r Mat 12.46-50; Mark 3.31-35 
\p  
\v 19 K…Ē iya ka Yesu k…Ē aw…õnc …Ēn Ňčander Ňčab…ôp k…Ē, mba Ňčanctam f…õ k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē nt…õ afum Ňčala m…Ē.  
\v 20 K'aŇčk…Ē paloku Yesu: ¬ęIya kam k…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčanc…ôm…õ nde dabaŇčka, m…ôna ŇčafaŇč k…ôn…ôŇčk.¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęIya kem k'aw…õnc im aŇča, Ňčay…Ēn…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta Kanu Ňčac…ôm…õ s…Ē ti dar…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôs k…Ēn afef Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč 
\r Mat 8.23-27; Mark 4.35-41 
\p  
\v 22 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma k…Ē Yesu …õmb…õk…õ debil k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč. K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęPacali ntende k…ôba mokuru.¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčayekti ab…õla k…ôk…Ē.  
\v 23 Ňäayi k…ôcali, k…Ē Yesu endir…ôrn…õ. K…Ē afef Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč Ňč…õy…õf…õ k…ôwur d…ôk…ôba k…Ē abil Ňč…õfaŇč k…ôkal…õ, k…Ē Ňčayi d…ôp…ôw…õy-w…õy.  
\v 24 K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčander Ňčatimi k…Ē, Ňčackul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ! W…ôt…ôks…õ! K…ôfi k…Ē s…ônder!¬Ľ Nt…õ entim…õ m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr afef k…Ē yam y…Ēp…ĒŇč y…Ēk…Ē y…õnay…õf…õ m…Ē, k…Ē y…õsak few. K…Ē p…ôy…Ē yeŇč, ali tes ancne f…õ s…Ē.  
\v 25 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęDeke k…ôlaŇč konu k…ôyi-…õ?¬Ľ Nt…õ Ňčanes…õ a k…Ē cusu c…ôwos Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayif…õn…õ aŇč…õ k…Ē ak…Ē: ¬ęAn'…Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ? W…ôkaw…õ …õŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr ali afef k…Ē yam, y…õc…ôm…õ s…Ē t…õfaŇč t…Ēn dar…ôŇč m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôtam…ôs ka fum nw…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…õnac…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč m…Ē 
\r Mat 8.28-34; Mark 5.1-20 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn ŇčaŇčk…Ē mokuru nde kulum ka Kerasa, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Kalile m…Ē.  
\v 27 Nt…õ Yesu owur debil m…Ē, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma w…ôka dare dad…Ēk…Ē ender p…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē f…Ēr kiriŇč, nk…Ēn y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…õlar…ôm y…õnayi m…Ē. K…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ p…ônawon m…Ē, …õncb…õrn…õ f…õ duma, …õnayi f…õ d…ôk…ôl…Ē, m…õn…õ p…ôyi nde cufu dac…Ē.  
\v 28 Nt…õ fum nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ Yesu w…õc…ôk d…ônt…Ēf, k'oloku p…ôp…ĒŇč: ¬ęT'ake t…Ē m…ômb…õr…õn…õ mes mem-…õ, Yesu Wan ka Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi darenc m…Ē? Il…õts…õn'am ta m…ôt…Ēr…ôs im!¬Ľ  
\v 29 Fum w…ôkak…Ē …õnaloku ti bawo Yesu oncloku Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc nŇč…õ Ňč…õnab…õr…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē d…ôris p…ôwon m…Ē k…ôwur. C…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, anckot…ôr…õn…õ fum w…ôkaw…õ gbekce d…ôw…õc…ôk k…Ē af…õc Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč, mba onccopu yi, Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňčosol…õ k…Ē Ňčekek…ôr…õ nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.  
\v 30 K…Ē Yesu eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē aŇčw'am-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku Yesu: ¬ęIna aŇčwe ‚ÄĻK…ônay‚Äļ.¬Ľ K'oloku ti bawo y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…õlar…ôm y…õnac…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč.  
\v 31 K…Ē y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc ny…õ y…õl…õts…õn…õ Yesu k…ôsak yi, ta p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ yi k…ôwur y…Ēk…Ē d…ôp…ôŇčal-Ňčal.  
\v 32 Awa, Ňčanab…Ēl…õn…õ f…õ s…Ēp y…õlar…ôm ny…õ y…Ēncs…Ēm…ôt d…ôndo t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē. K…Ē y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…õl…õts…õn…õ Yesu k…ôce yi y…õb…õr…õ d…ôs…Ēp ny…õ, k…Ē Yesu owos…õn…õ yi.  
\v 33 K…Ē y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc yowur d…ôfum, k…Ē y…ĒŇčk…Ē y…õmb…õr…õ d…ôs…Ēp. K…Ē s…Ēp ny…õ f…ôp yontor k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôt…Ēr…Ē, k…Ē y…ĒŇčk…Ē yotor d…ôk…ôba, k…Ē y…õŇčgb…ôts…õ, k…Ē yefis-fis f…ôp.  
\v 34 Nt…õ ak…õk s…Ēp aŇč…õ Ňčan…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčasams…ôr…õn…õ toloku tat…Ēk…Ē dare k…Ē aka s…ôdare s…ôk…ôs…ôk.  
\v 35 K…Ē afum Ňčander k…ôm…Ēm…ôn t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr di m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčander nn…Ē Yesu eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp fum w…ôk…Ē y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…õnawur d…ôris m…Ē, p…ôs…ôk…ôp p…ônd…õ Yesu d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē amera Ňč…Ēn f…ôp, afum aŇč…õ Ňčanader k…ôm…Ēm…ôn m…Ē Ňčanes…õ.  
\v 36 Afum ak…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr m…Ē, Ňčal…Ēm…ôr ak…Ē Ňčanader k…ôm…Ēm…ôn t…Ēk…Ē anayac k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 37 K…Ē afum a at…Ēf Ňča Kerasa f…ôp Ňčal…õts…õn…õ Yesu a p…ôy…õf…õ ndaraŇčan p…ôk…Ē, bawo ŇčananaŇčkan…õ k…ônes…õ. K…Ē Yesu …õmb…õr…õ debil, k'olukus.  
\v 38 Fum w…ôk…Ē Yesu …õnaluks…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc dar…ôŇč m…Ē, …õl…õts…õn…õ Yesu a p…ôtam k…ôce k…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf. Mba k…Ē Yesu ombup…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôcloku:  
\v 39 ¬ęM…ôlukus nn…Ē ndaram. M…ôk…Ē m…ôcloku afum t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ôy…Ēn'am m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ K…Ē fum nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôloku dare disr…õ f…ôp mes m…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnay…Ēn…õ k…Ē m…Ē. 
\s1 Wan w…ôran w…ôka Sayirus, k…Ē w…ôran w…ôk…Ē …õnagbuŇč…õn…õ yamos ya Yesu m…Ē 
\r Mat 9.18-26; Mark 5.21-43 
\p  
\v 40 Yesu k…ôlukus k…Ēn, k…Ē afum ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčafayn…õ k…Ē, bawo f…ôp f…ônckar k…Ē.  
\v 41 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …õnader pacwe k…Ē Yayir…Ēs, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif m…Ē. K…Ē Yayir…Ēs ontontn…õ k'osump…ôr Yesu w…õc…ôk, p…ôcl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôwos…õ k…ôder ka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn.  
\v 42 Bawo …õnay…Ē wan w…ôran w…ôkin gboŇč, nw…õ …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, p…ôcfi. Nt…õ Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē k…ônay k…ôm…õpn…õ k…Ē haŇč Ňčacyam…ôs…ôr k…Ē k…ôŇčes…ôm.  
\v 43 W…ôran w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi di, p…ôy…Ē docu da k…ôwur mecir t…õnas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ta p…ônc…ômb…ôr…ôs-…õ. W…ôran nw…õ …õnab…õrs…õ daka d…Ēn f…ôp nn…Ē at…õn c…Ēl Ňčayi m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ patam…ôs k…Ē m…Ē. Mba ali fum …õnatam f…õ k…ôtam…ôs k…Ē.  
\v 44 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yesu tadar…ôŇč, k'oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ dobol da yamos y…Ēn. Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē k…ôwur mecir kaŇčk…Ē k…ônayi k…Ē m…Ē k…ôsak…õ.  
\v 45 K…Ē Yesu eyif: ¬ęAn…Ē ogbuŇč…õn'em-…õ?¬Ľ Nt…õ afum f…ôp Ňčambup…ôr…õ ti m…Ē, k…Ē Piy…õr oloku: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ afum ŇčaŇčk…õl …ôm waca nw…õ f…ôp!¬Ľ  
\v 46 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęFum w…ôl…Ēma oŇčgbuŇč…õn'em, bawo inc…ôr…õ a f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôl…Ēma f…ôwur im d…ôris.¬Ľ  
\v 47 Nt…õ w…ôran nw…õ …õnc…ôr…õ a Yesu …õnc…ôr…õ a fum oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k'ender p…ôcyikc…õ, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ Yesu w…õc…ôk d…ônt…Ēf. K'oloku afum f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč tes t…Ēk…Ē t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ ka duma da Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē docu d…Ēn d…õnatamn…õ gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 48 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęWan kem, k…ôlaŇč kam k…ôntam…ôs …ôm, m…ôk…Ēn…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčoforu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 49 Yesu eyi k…ôlok-loku kaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma ender k…ôy…õf…õ ka ndena w…ôb…õ ka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif da dare, k'ender p…ôloku: ¬ęWan kam efi, ali m…ônt…Ēr…ôs f…õ s…Ē w…ôt…ôks…õ k…ôk…Ē di.¬Ľ  
\v 50 Mba Yesu …õnane fum nw…õ k…ôloku ka w…ôb…õ w…ôka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif defi da wan k…Ēn, k'oloku w…ôb…õ nw…õ: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ! M…ôlaŇč gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, wan kam …õntamn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 51 Nt…õ Ňčander d…õk…õr m…Ē, Yesu owos…õ f…õ fum k…ôb…õr…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn m…õn…õ Piy…õr, IsaŇč, Sak, wan w…ôran nw…õ kas k…Ē k…õr…õ gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, Ňč…Ē …õnawos…õ k…ôb…õr…õ nn…Ē wan w…ôran w…ôfi nw…õ eyi m…Ē.  
\v 52 K…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčambok Ňčacl…Ēm p…ôcuy paŇčan tet…Ēn. K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęTa n…ôbok! Efi f…õ, k…ôdir…õ k'…õnd…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 53 K…Ē afum Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôfani Yesu, bawo afum aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôr…õ a wan w…ôran nw…õ efi.  
\v 54 K…Ē Yesu osump…ôr wan w…ôran nw…õ k…ôca, k'olok…õ dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč: ¬ęWan kem, m…ôy…õf…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 55 K…Ē amera Ňč…Ēn Ňčoluks…ôrn…õ k…Ē d…ôris, gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k'…õy…õf…õ, k…Ē Yesu oloku a pas…ĒŇč k…Ē yeri.  
\v 56 K…Ē cusu c…ôwos akomb…ôra aka wan w…ôran nw…õ, k…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča a ta Ňčal…Ēm…ôr nw…õ o nw…õ nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē. 
\c 9  
\s1 Yesu osom ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč 
\r Mat 10.5-15; Mark 6.7-13 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu ewe ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa k…ôtam ka k…ôb…õl…ôs y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc f…ôp, k…Ē k…ôtam…ôs ka docu.  
\v 2 K…Ē Yesu osom Ňča k…ôk…Ēd…ôŇčk d…õb…õ da Kanu, k…Ē k…ôtam…ôs ka acuy.  
\v 3 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ daka o daka teta d…Ēp…Ē, ta n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr togbo, ta n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr t…Ēl…Ēba, ta n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr tocom, ta n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr p…ôsam, ta nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr s…ôburumus m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 4 K…Ē n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē nk…õ o nk…õ-…õ, n…ôyi di, dif…Ē n…ôndek…Ēy…õf…õ a n…ôsump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē donu k…ôk…Ē.  
\v 5 Nn…Ē o nn…Ē afum Ňčant…Ēk…Ēwos…õ nu k…ôyi m…Ē, k…Ē n…ôndewur dare dad…Ēk…Ē-…õ, n…ôkoŇč-koŇč w…õc…ôk wonu, it'endey…Ēn…õ sede a ŇčanabaŇč f…õ nu.  
\v 6 K…Ē asom aŇč…õ Ňčawur Ňčack…Ēt s…ôdare, Ňčacd…ôŇčk toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Kanu, Ňčactam…ôs acuy mofo f…ôp. 
\s1 P…ôciyan…õ pa Herodu 
\r Mat 14.1-12; Mark 6.14-29 
\p  
\v 7 Nt…õ Herodu nw…õ …õnat…Ēmp…ôr d…õb…õ Kalile ene mes mm…õ menccep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônciyan…õ k…Ē, bawo al…Ēma Ňčancloku a SaŇč …Ēf…Ē, nk…Ēn …Ēf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē,  
\v 8 al…Ēma Ňčacloku, a Eli eder, al…Ēma Ňčacloku, a w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôl…Ēma oluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôder.  
\v 9 K…Ē Herodu nk…Ēn oloku: ¬ęInagbinti SaŇč domp! An'…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum w…ôkaw…õ aŇčloku tet…Ēn m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Herodu …õfaŇč k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ ka afum wul k…ôcam…ôt (5000) k…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ 
\r Mat 14.13-21; Mark 6.30-34; IsaŇč 6.1-14 
\p  
\v 10 K…Ē asom Ňčander Ňčaluks…õ Yesu t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…Ē m…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk Ňča k…Ē Ňčawurn…õ k…ôs…ôk, ntende dare da B…õtsayida.  
\v 11 K…Ē afum Ňčanc…ôr…õ k…ôwur k…ôŇčan k…Ē Ňčanc…õps…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč. K…Ē Yesu owos…õ Ňča k…ôder, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôcloku Ňča teta d…õb…õ da Kanu, k'…õntam…ôs s…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ētamn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 12 Nt…õ dec d…õy…õf…õ k…ôkal…õ m…Ē, k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē Ňčacloku: ¬ęM…ôy…Ē oŇč m…ôsak afum akaŇč…õ Ňčak…Ē Ňčat…õn d…ôk…ôdir…õ k…Ē yeri nde s…ôdare s…ôcs…ôk k…Ē d…ômadare m…õf…õt m…õf…õt mm…õ m…õŇčk…õl nn…Ē m…Ē, bawo d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ ayi w…ôkaw…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ônas…ôrka n…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča yeri.¬Ľ K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôcom k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē lop m…õr…ôŇč gb…ôc…ôr…ôm y…Ē s…ôy…Ē, m…ôfaŇč oŇč a s…ôk…Ē s…ôway…õ k…ônay kaŇčk…õ yeri ba?¬Ľ  
\v 14 Mba afum aŇč…õ Ňčancb…ôp arkun wul k…ôcam…ôt (5000). K…Ē Yesu oloku Asom …Ēn: ¬ęN…ôy…Ē Ňča ŇčaloŇčkan…õ arkun w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50-50).¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē asom …Ēn Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnaloku Ňča k…ôy…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčand…ôs Ňča f…ôp.  
\v 16 K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk c…ôcom nc…õ k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē lop ny…õ m…õr…ôŇč, k'eyekti f…Ēr darenc, k'eyif Kanu barka. K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda k'entepi c…ôcom nc…õ a k'endes…ĒŇč…ôs ci ac…õps…õ a Ňčayer…ôs k…ônay kaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 17 K…Ē f…ôp f…ôs…Ēm ci k…Ē Ňčan…õmb…ôr…õ. Nt…õ anaw…õt…ôs yeri y…õl…ôp…ôs ny…õ m…Ē, y…õnay…Ē c…ôfala w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč. 
\s1 Piy…õr oloku a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē 
\r Mat 16.13-19; Mark 8.27-29 
\p  
\v 18 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma Yesu \k p…ôclok-lok…ôr Kanu\k* taciŇča, ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč ŇčaloŇčkan…õ k…Ē k…ôs…ôk. K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęToloku ta afum, an…Ē iy…Ēn…õ-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 19 K'ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ al…Ēma Ňčaloku m…Ē, a AŇčnabi SaŇč m…ôy…Ēn…õ, k'al…Ēma Ňčaloku a Eli m…ôy…Ēn…õ, al…Ēma a sayib…õ s…ôl…Ēma s…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ nw…õ …õy…õf…õ afi dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 20 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęP…õc…õmc…õmn…õ ponu, an'iy…Ēn…õ-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Piy…õr oloku Yesu: ¬ęKrist w…ôy…õk-y…õk w…ôka Kanu m…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôcam defi d…Ēn k…Ē k…ôdey…õf…õ k…Ēn afi dac…Ē 
\r Mat 16.20-28; Mark 8.30-9.1 
\p  
\v 21 K…Ē Yesu entiŇč-tiŇč Ňča k…ôcaŇčk…õ ti, ta Ňčaloku ti ali fum.  
\v 22 K'…Ēn…Ēc…ôr a p…ônamar dis d…Ēl…Ēl Wan ka W…ôrkun belbel. Abeki, aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ Ňčandew…õn…ôs k…Ē, padif k…Ē, p…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē tataka ta maas. 
\p  
\v 23 K'oloku afum f…ôp nt…õ: ¬ęK…Ē fum …õfaŇč k…ôc…õps'em dar…ôŇč-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôsak k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ teta nk…Ēns…ôrka, p…ôgbaŇčn…õ k…ôt…Ēk k…Ēn k…ôp…ômp…ôl d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk, p…ôc…ôm'em dar…ôŇč.  
\v 24 Bawo, nw…õ o nw…õ …õŇčs…õp k…ôyac k…ôyi doru k…Ēn m…Ē, k…ôŇčsalp…ôr k…Ē, mba nw…õ o nw…õ kiyi k…Ēn doru k…ôŇčsalp…ôr k…Ē tetem m…Ē, endeyac ki.  
\v 25 D…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ dere d…Ē t…Ēy…Ē fum k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…Ēn doru k…Ērk…Ēr-…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a w…ôkayi eyi k…ôs…Ēl…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôkayi p…ôcl…ôs…ôrn…õ-…õ?  
\v 26 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õlap…ôrn'em k…Ē moloku mem, Wan ka W…ôrkun endek…Ēs…Ēd…ômn…õ lap…ôrn…õ m…ôna w…ôkayi k'endeder n…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn, da Papa, k…Ē da m…õl…õk…õ mecempi-…õ.  
\v 27 Icloku nu kance: Afum akin akin Ňčayi nn…Ē k…ôfo kaŇčk…õ aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēdefi ta Ňčantan…ôŇčk k…ôder ka d…õb…õ da Kanu-…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Piy…õr, IsaŇč k…Ē Sak Ňčan…ôŇčk Yesu p…ôyi p…ômotu pa debeki da Kanu disr…õ 
\r Mat 17.1-8; Mark 9.2-8 
\p  
\v 28 Nt…õ Yesu oloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē mata cam…ôt-maas mencep…ôr, k'…õl…õk Piy…õr, IsaŇč k…Ē Sak, k…Ē Ňčamp…õ t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč \k k…ôk…Ētola Kanu\k*.  
\v 29 Yesu eyi k…ôsali, k…Ē k…ôro k…Ēn k…õs…ôkp…ôr, k…Ē yamos y…Ēn y…õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôfer…õ yocmot…ôr-mot…ôr.  
\v 30 P…ôwon f…õ k…Ē afum m…õr…ôŇč Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôlok-loku k…Ē nk…Ēn: AŇčnabi Musa k…Ē AŇčnabi Eli Ňčanayi,  
\v 31 aŇč…õ ancn…ôŇčk \k p…ômot pa p…ôlel\k* pa debeki da Kanu disr…õ m…Ē. Ňäacloku Yesu k…ôk…Ē k…Ēn nk…õ k…ôŇčk…Ēyi Yerusal…õm m…Ē.  
\v 32 T…õt…ôŇčn…õ Piy…õr k'asol …Ēn Ňčacdir…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč. Nt…õ Ňčantim…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk Yesu p…ômot pa debeki da Kanu disr…õ, k…Ē afum m…õr…ôŇč ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē.  
\v 33 T…õm nt…õ afum akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčancgb…õy…õn…õ k…Ē Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Piy…õr oloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ p…ôntes…õ su kiyi ka nn…Ē. S…ôc…ômb…ôr \k Ňčgbancan Ňčecep…õ-cep…õ\k* maas, Ňčin Ňčam, Ňčin Ňča Musa, k…Ē Ňčin Ňča Eli.¬Ľ Piy…õr …õnac…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ oloku m…Ē.  
\v 34 Nt…õ oncloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp k…ônder k…ôgb…ôp…ôrn…õ Ňča k…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôsump…ôr ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč nt…õ Ňčanan…ôŇčk k…ôp kaŇčk…Ē k…ôcder k…ôgb…ôp…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 35 K…Ē dim dowur k…ôp kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ, docloku: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ wan kem, nk…Ēn iy…õk-y…õk: N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 36 Nt…õ ane dim dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'an…ôŇčk Yesu p…ôc…ôm…õ sona. K'ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč ŇčancaŇčk ali fum …õnaloku f…õ s…Ē w…ôkos t…Ēl…Ēma nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk m…Ē mata mam…Ēk…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôtam…ôs ka wan nw…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…õnatoŇčkulu-toŇčkulu 
\r Mat 17.14-18; Mark 9.14-27 
\p  
\v 37 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk nt…õ Ňčantor k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôt…Ēr…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē afum alar…ôm Ňčander k…ôdefayn…õ Yesu.  
\v 38 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma oŇčkul…ôrn…õ k…ônay kaŇčk…Ē dac…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, il…õts…õn'am m…ôm…Ēm…ôn wan kem, bawo w…ôkin w…ôkaw…õ gboŇč iy…Ē.  
\v 39 Ňä…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…Ēl…Ēma Ňč…õmb…õr…õ k…Ē, k…Ē Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčeyik…ôc k…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôfoc k…ôwur k…Ē d…ôkusu, k…Ē Ňč…Ēl…Ēl…ôs k…Ē dis, p…ôŇčyeŇčk a Ňčendesak k…Ē.  
\v 40 Il…õts…õn…õ ac…õps…õ am dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs ka Ňči, mba Ňčantam f…õ ti.¬Ľ  
\v 41 K…Ē Yesu oŇčkul…ôrn…õ: ¬ęN…ôna afum a d…õt…õmp da t…õm tant…õ d…õkaf…ôl…õ-kaf…ôl…õ, d…Ēt…ĒlaŇč Kanu, ake t…õm t'indes…Ēyi k…Ē n…ôna-…õ? T…õm c…ôke t…Ē p…ômar s…Ē ic…ôm…õ nu d…ônt…Ēf-…õ? M…ôk…õr…õ wan kam nn…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 42 Nt…õ wan w…ôkak…Ē …Ēncl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õŇčgbal k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē Ňčeyik…ôc k…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč. Mba k…Ē Yesu …õŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, k'…õntam…ôs wan w…ôkak…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē kas.  
\v 43 K…Ē cusu c…ôwos afum f…ôp k…ôn…ôŇčk ka f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôp…ĒŇč fa Kanu. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ k…Ēn k…ôloku defi d…Ēn 
\r Mat 17.22-23; Mark 9.30-32 
\p Nt…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē Yesu …Ēncy…Ē m…Ē mecciy…õn…õ afum m…Ē, k'oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč:  
\v 44 ¬ęN…ôna n…ôsu l…ôŇč…ôs, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl belbel moloku mam…õ: K…ôb…õr k'ander Wan ka W…ôrkun afum d…ôwaca.  
\v 45 Mba ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ tedisr…õ ta toloku tat…Ēk…Ē oncloku m…Ē. T…õnagb…Ēpn…õ Ňča, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčanc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčanes…õ k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē tedisr…õ ta toloku tat…Ēk…Ē. 
\s1 An…Ē ecep…ôr nu f…ôp-…õ? 
\r Mat 18.1-5; Mark 9.33-37 
\p  
\v 46 K'ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyif…ôt…õn…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôr…õ nw…õ encep…ôr Ňča d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ē.  
\v 47 Yesu nw…õ …õnac…ôr…õ m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ mm…õ meyi Ňča d…ôcor m…Ē, …õl…õk wan w…ôf…õt w…ôkin, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr…ôrn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 48 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęNw…õ o nw…õ …õbaŇč wanf…õt w…ôkaw…õ k…ôbaŇč k…ôt…Ēt tetem m…Ē, …õmbaŇč s…Ē inas…ôrka p…ôt…Ēt. Nw…õ o nw…õ …õbaŇč im, …õmbaŇč s…Ē w…ôk…Ē osom im m…Ē. Bawo fum w…ôk…Ē …õnc…ômb…ôrn…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ d…õf…õt m…Ē, …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôk…Ē encep…ôr nu f…ôp m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēc'am m…Ē, …õfaŇč …ôm 
\r Mark 9.38-40 
\p  
\v 49 K…Ē IsaŇč …õl…õk moloku k'oloku: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ s…ônan…ôŇčk fum w…ôl…Ēma p…ôcb…õl…ôs…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc tewe tam, k…Ē s…ôfaŇč k…ôm…Ēn…õ k…Ē, bawo w…ôkayi …õnc…ôm…õ f'am dar…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē s…ôna.¬Ľ  
\v 50 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa n…ôm…Ēn…õ k…Ē ti, bawo fum nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēc'am m…Ē, …õfaŇč …ôm.¬Ľ 
\s1 Dare d…Ēl…Ēma da Samari k…ôfati k…ôbaŇč ka Yesu 
\p  
\v 51 Nt…õ d…Ēs…Ēk d…õl…õk da Yesu doru d…Ēncl…Ēt…ôs m…Ē, k'olokun…õ a m…õn…õ p…ôk…Ē Yerusal…õm gb…ôs.  
\v 52 K'osom afum al…Ēma Ňčayi k…Ē kiriŇč. K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčayi kiriŇč k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp dare da Samari d…Ēl…Ēma, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčalomp…ôsn…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 53 Mba k…Ē aka dare dad…Ēk…Ē Ňčafati k…ôbaŇč k…Ē, bawo Yerusal…õm Ňčanck…Ē.  
\v 54 Nt…õ afum aŇč…õ Ňčan…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč, IsaŇč k…Ē Sak Ňčaloku: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, m…ôfaŇč s…ôloku n…õnc dotor k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm d…õl…ôs…ôr Ňča?¬Ľ  
\v 55 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ k'…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ Ňča, k'…õgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňča.  
\v 56 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē dare d…Ēl…Ēma. 
\s1 AŇč…õ ŇčafaŇč k…ôc…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč m…Ē 
\r Mat 8.19-22 
\p  
\v 57 Nt…õ Ňčanayi d…Ēp…Ē k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIndec…ôm'am dar…ôŇč nn…Ē o nn…Ē m…ôndek…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 58 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…Ēs…ĒŇčk m…Ēy…Ē bi d…ôk…ôdir…õ k…Ē b…õmp y…Ēy…Ē w…Ēl…Ē d…ôk…ôdir…õ, mba ina Wan ka W…ôrkun iy…Ē f…õ k…ôfo nk…õ intam k…ôboc domp dem m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 59 K…Ē Yesu oloku fum w…ôl…Ēma: ¬ęM…ôc…ôm'em dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ K…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē oloku k…Ē: ¬ęMariki, m…ôwos'em k…ôr…õsna ik…Ē iwup papa kem.¬Ľ  
\v 60 K…Ē Yesu oloku fum w…ôkak…Ē: ¬ęM…ôce afi Ňčawup afi, k…Ē m…ôna, m…ôk…Ē m…ôd…ôŇčk d…õb…õ da Kanu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 61 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma oloku: ¬ęK…ôc…ôm'am k'inder dar…ôŇč W…ôb…õ, mba m…ôkar ik…Ē k…ôr…õsna ilemb…ôrn…õ aka k…ôl…Ē kem disr…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 62 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęNw…õ o nw…õ edebift…õ c…ôna a w…ôkayi p…ôcm…Ēm…ôn tadar…ôŇč m…Ē, …Ēy…Ē f…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ 
\c 10  
\s1 K…ôsom ka ac…õps…õ dar…ôŇč 72 
\r Mat 10.7-16 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē W…ôb…õ …õy…õk-y…õk s…Ē afum 72 al…Ēma, k'osom Ňča m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč Ňčayi k…Ē tekiriŇč k…ôk…Ēt ka s…ôdare k…Ē mofo f…ôp mm…õ p…ônamar k…Ē k…ôk…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 2 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęDal…õ d…õt…õl d…õmb…õk, mba at…õl Ňčampic…õ. N…ôl…õts…õn…õ Mariki ma k…ôt…õl p…ôb…õr…õn…õ s…Ē at…õl al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčandet…õl…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 3 Awa! Isom nu n…ôŇčk…Ēyi p…ôm…Ē nt…õ meŇčkesiya meŇčyi calma dac…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 4 Ta n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ p…ôsam pa delek, ta n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ l…Ēba, ta n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ c…Ēfta, ta n…ôyif…õn…õ s…Ē k…Ē fum o fum d…Ēp…Ē.  
\v 5 K…ôl…Ē nk…õ o nk…õ n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ m…Ē, n…ôkul…õ k…ôr…õsna: ‚ÄĻKanu k…ôb…õrs…õ p…ôforu k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…õ!‚Äļ  
\v 6 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ, fum w…ôka p…ôforu eyi k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē-…õ, p…ôforu ponu peŇčyi k…Ē k…ôroŇč, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, p…ôforu pap…Ēk…Ē poluks…ôrn…õ nu.  
\v 7 N…ôyi k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē, n…ôdi yeri, n…ômun domun da k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē, bawo p…ômar w…ôb…ôc p…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôway k…Ēn. Ta n…ôccal-cali w…Ēl…Ē de!  
\v 8 Dare nd…õ o nd…õ n…ôb…õr…õ a pabaŇč nu m…Ē, n…ôdi yeri y…Ēk…Ē aŇčs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē.  
\v 9 N…ôtam…ôs acuy ak…Ē Ňčayi di m…Ē, n…ôloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻD…õb…õ da Kanu d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ nu.‚Äļ  
\v 10 Dare nd…õ o nd…õ n…ôk…Ē ta ambaŇč nu m…Ē, n…ôk…Ē nde abaŇčka ŇčaŇčan n…ôloku:  
\v 11 ‚ÄĻS…ôŇčkoŇč…ôr nu k…ôf…ôl ka dare donu ali nk…õ k…ôsopt…õ su d…ôw…õc…ôk m…Ē, s…ôluks…õ nu ki, n…ôtam k…ôc…ôr…õ a d…õb…õ da Kanu d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 12 Icloku nu a d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Kanu k…ôndekiti afum f…ôp, t…Ēy…Ē nt…õ andey…Ē dare dand…õ m…Ē, tendeyeŇčk t…õtas ta aka dare da Sodom.¬Ľ 
\s1 S…ôdare ns…õ s…ôfati k…ôlaŇč m…Ē 
\r Mat 11.20-24 
\p  
\v 13 ¬ęP…ôl…õc p…Ēp…ĒŇč peyi m…ôna dare da Korasin! P…ôl…õc p…Ēp…ĒŇč peyi m…ôna, dare da B…õtsayida! Bawo k…Ē t…Ēcy…Ēn…õ a mes m…õw…õy-w…õy mm…õ Kanu k…ônay…Ē nn…Ē ndoronu m…Ē, m'anay…Ē aka s…ôdare sa Tir k…Ē Sid…ĒŇč-…õ, k…Ē Ňčanas…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc p…ôwon, Ňčac…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč, Ňčab…õrn…õ yamos ya k…ôbal, Ňčand…õ Ňčam…Ēncn…õ!  
\v 14 It'endes…ĒŇč…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Kanu k…ôndekiti afum f…ôp m…Ē, p…ôndeyeŇčk…ôr n…ôna p…ôtas aka s…ôdare sa Tir k…Ē Sid…ĒŇč.  
\v 15 K…Ē n…ôna aka Kaparnam, n…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a andep…õn…õ nu haŇč d…ôk…Ēm ba? Ala! Andetor…õ nu d…ônt…Ēf haŇč nde afum afi Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 16 Nw…õ …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl nu m…Ē, …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl im. K…Ē nw…õ …õŇčw…õn…ôs nu m…Ē, …õw…õn…ôs s…Ē ina, k'…õw…õn…ôs w…ôk…Ē osom im m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôlukus ka ac…õps…õ dar…ôŇč 72 
\p  
\v 17 K…Ē afum 72 aŇč…õ anasom m…Ē Ňčalukus p…ôbotu disr…õ k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęW…ôb…õ! Ali y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc f…ôp y…õnayi su d…ônt…Ēf tewe tam.¬Ľ  
\v 18 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęIndenan…ôŇčk Sentani k…ôt…õmp…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ darenc p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ôŇčmot m…Ē.  
\v 19 N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl: Is…ĒŇč nu k…ôtam k…ôk…Ēt ka bok k…Ē mek…ôlenc…ôr k…ôroŇč k…ôl…õk…õn…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa ater anu f…ôp, daka o daka d…Ēf…Ētam k…ôyams…õ nu ti.  
\v 20 Mba ta p…ôb…Ēt nu nt…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc yeyi nu d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, mba p…ôb…Ēt nu nt…õ ancic mewe monu nde darenc, ndena Kanu m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 P…ôbotu pa Yesu 
\r Mat 11.25-27; 13.16-17 
\p  
\v 21 T…õnat…ôŇčn…õ, \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ p…ônaŇčkan…õ k…ôb…Ēt Yesu, k'oloku: ¬ęIŇčkor-kor'…ôm Papa, Mariki ma d…ôk…Ēm k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf, bawo m…ôm…õŇčk…ôr mes mam…Ēk…Ē ac…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes k…Ē asoku s…ôbomp, k…Ē m…ôment…ôr mi af…õt d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ. ∆źy, Papa, bawo tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē m…ôfaŇč ti.  
\v 22 Icloku nu a Papa kem …õmb…õr im ca f…ôp d…ôwaca. Nw…õ o nw…õ …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ Wan m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…Ēy…Ēn…õ Papa-…õ. Nw…õ o nw…õ …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ s…Ē nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ Papa m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…Ēy…Ēn…õ Wan-…õ, k…Ē afum ak…Ē Wan …õŇčfaŇč k…ôment…ôr k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 23 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ k'…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč, k'…õy…õl dim, p…ôcloku Ňča: ¬ęP…ômb…Ēt aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčn…ôŇčk m…Ēk…Ē n…ôyi k…ôn…ôŇčk m…Ē!  
\v 24 Bawo sayib…õ s…ôlar…ôm k…Ē ab…õ a t…Ēf y…õlar…ôm ŇčanafaŇč k…ôn…ôŇčk mam…õ n…ôyi k…ôn…ôŇčk m…Ē, mba Ňčanan…ôŇčk f…õ mi, ŇčanafaŇč k…ône mam…õ n…ôyi k…ône m…Ē, mba Ňčanane f…õ mi.¬Ľ 
\s1 Totubc…õn…õ ta w…ôSamari w…ôt…Ēt 
\p  
\v 25 K…Ē w…ôt…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif w…ôl…Ēma …õy…õf…õ k'oloku Yesu, nt…õ …õfaŇč k…ôc…ôp…õ k…Ē towul d…ômoloku m…Ē. K'eyif Yesu: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, c…ôke c…Ē p…ômar im k…ôy…Ē, is…Ēt…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 26 K…Ē Yesu eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē ancic nde buk ba sariy…õ-…õ? C…ôke c…Ē m…ôŇčkaraŇč bi disr…õ-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku Yesu: ¬ęP…ômar m…ôb…Ēt…ôr…õ Mariki Kanu ab…ôk…ôc Ňčam f…ôp, af…Ēk…ôl Ňčam f…ôp, s…Ēk…ôt sam f…ôp, k…Ē m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ mam f…ôp. K…Ē telip-…õ, m…ôb…Ēt…ôr w…õnc …ôm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ômb…Ēt…ôrn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôloku ti belbel, m…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôyi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 29 Mba nt…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka sariy…õ nw…õ …õfaŇč k…ôment…ôr dolompu d…Ēn m…Ē, k'eyif Yesu: ¬ęAn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…õnc im-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 30 K…Ē Yesu …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ moloku k'oloku: ¬ęFum w…ôl…Ēma …õnay…õf…õ Yerusal…õm p…ôck…Ē Yeriko. K…Ē w…ôfum w…ôkak…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…õr…õ afum al…õc dac…Ē, k…Ē afum al…õc akak…Ē ŇčambaŇč…ôr k…Ē daka d…Ēk…Ē …õnat…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčasut k…Ē haŇč p…ôcbut k…ôfi, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.  
\v 31 K…Ē tosur…õn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôl…Ēma osoln…õ s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē din dad…Ēk…Ē. Nt…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk fum w…ôk…Ē anasut m…Ē, k'encep…ôr d…Ēp…Ē ntende p…ôb…Ēl…õ k…Ē.  
\v 32 K…Ē w…ôLewy w…ôl…Ēma ender s…Ē k…ôfo kin kaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē s…Ē …õn…ôŇčk fum nw…õ, k…Ē nk…Ēn s…Ē encep…ôr ntende p…ôb…Ēl…õ k…Ē.  
\v 33 K…Ē w…ôSamari w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ …Ēnck…Ē mar…ônt m…Ē, ender p…ôb…ôp fum w…ôkaw…õ nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr deyi k…Ē.  
\v 34 K…Ē w…ôSamari nw…õ …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ fum nw…õ, k'oloŇč…ôr runc y…Ēn member, k'…Ēmb…Ēy yi moro, k'esekt…ôr yi. K…Ē w…ôSamari nw…õ …õl…õk fum w…ôkak…Ē k'endeŇč k…Ē p…Ēk…Ēt…õn…õ p…Ēn k…ôroŇč, k'eŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē karwaŇčse k…ôl…Ēma, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôboc k…Ē di, k'…õnc…ôm…õ tet…Ēn.  
\v 35 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē w…ôSamari nw…õ owur…õ gb…ôleŇč m…õr…ôŇč ba p…ôsam, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč bi w…ôka karwaŇčse. K'oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôgb…õk…ôr…õ k…Ē, mp…õ o mp…õ mendes…ĒŇč k…Ē m…Ē, indeluks'am pi d…ôk…ôlukus dem.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 36 K…Ē Yesu …Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ maas dac…Ē an…Ē m…ôna m…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…õnc ka fum w…ôk…Ē afum al…õc Ňčanasut m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka sariy…õ nw…õ oloku: ¬ęNw…õ …õnament…ôr k…Ē amera Ňčobotu m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloku w…ôb…õ w…ôka sariy…õ nw…õ: ¬ęAwa, m…ôna s…Ē m…ôk…Ē m…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu ndena Marta k…Ē Mari 
\p  
\v 38 Yesu Ňčayi d…Ēp…Ē k…ôk…Ē k…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ dare d…Ēl…Ēma, k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Marta, …õmbaŇč k…Ē nde nd…Ēr…Ēn.  
\v 39 Marta …õnay…Ē w…õnc w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ ancwe Mari m…Ē, k…Ē w…õnc nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ W…ôb…õ d…ônt…Ēf, p…ôcc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku m…Ēn.  
\v 40 Marta nk…Ēn p…ôsump…ôr y…õb…ôc y…õlar…ôm. K…Ē Marta ender p…ôloku Yesu: ¬ęW…ôb…õ t…Ēf…Ēt…Ēr…ôs …ôm tant…õ w…õnc im w…ôran ende p…ônd'am d…ônt…Ēf p…ôsak…ôr'em y…õb…ôc yay…õ sona m…Ē? M…ôloku k…Ē p…ôde p…ômar im.¬Ľ  
\v 41 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęMarta, Marta! M…ôyi k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…Ē k…ôsims…õ teta mes m…õlar…ôm.  
\v 42 Mba tes tin gboŇč t…Ēy…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ. Mari …õl…õk da p…ôntes…õ m…Ē, af…Ēs…ĒbaŇč…ôr k…Ē d…ônda.¬Ľ 
\c 11  
\s1 Yesu k…Ē sali 
\r Mat 6.9-13; 7.7-11 
\p  
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma Yesu \k p…ôclok-lok…ôr Kanu\k* k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma. Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôc…õps…õ k…Ēn dar…ôŇč w…ôl…Ēma eyif k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, m…ôt…ôks…õ su k…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē SaŇč …õnat…ôks…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč k…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 2 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē n…ônde n…ôctola Kanu-…õ, n…ôloku: 
\q1 Kas kosu! 
\q1 M…ôs…ĒŇč…õ palel…ôs decempi da tewe tam topus. 
\q1 M…ôs…ĒŇč…õ a d…õb…õ dam deder! 
\q1  
\v 3 M…ôpoc…õ su d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk k…ôcom kosu. 
\q1  
\v 4 M…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ su kiciya kosu 
\q1 p…ôm…Ē nt…õ s…ôŇčŇčaŇčn…õn…õ nw…õ o nw…õ enciyan…õ su m…Ē. 
\q1 Ta m…ôsak su s…ôy…Ē mes mm…õ m…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôciya m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęAn'…õntam k…ôy…Ē w…ôkos w…ôkin nu dac…Ē, nw…õ …õŇčy…õf…õ c…õk-c…õk p…ôk…Ē p…ôb…ôp wanapa k…Ēn nde nd…Ēr…Ēn p…ôcloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻWanapa m…ôb…Ēr im c…ôcom maas,  
\v 6 bawo w…ôb…Ēt kem w…ôl…Ēma eder nde nderem c…õk-c…õk canc…õ, mba ali paka iy…Ē f…õ mp…õ iŇčs…ĒŇč k…Ē p…ôdi m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 7 K…Ē wanapa k…Ēn w…ôkak…Ē, eyi duk…ôl…Ē m…Ē oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻTa m…ôt…Ērs im! AŇčgb…ôt kumba, s…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē awut em, if…Ētam k…ôy…õf…õ is…ĒŇč …ôm c…ôcom,‚Äļ  
\v 8 icloku nu ti: Ali p…ôy…Ēn…õ a …Ēf…Ēy…õf…õ p…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē ci bawo wanapa k…Ēn …Ēf…Ē, endey…õf…õ p…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē daka o daka nd…õ …õfaŇč m…Ē, bawo wanapa k…Ēn …õŇčgb…ôc gb…õs a m…õn…õ p…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē ina, iloku nu: N…ôtola, n…ôndes…Ēt…Ē. N…ôt…õn, n…ônden…ôŇčk. N…ôsut-sut kumba, andegbit…õ nu.  
\v 10 Bawo nw…õ o nw…õ ontola Kanu m…Ē, ompoc…õ k…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ …õnt…õn m…Ē, …õŇčn…ôŇčk. Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčsut-sut kumba m…Ē, aŇčgbit…õ k…Ē.  
\v 11 Kas k…ôre k…ôyi nu dac…Ē, nk…õ wan k…Ēn ontola k…Ē alop, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē abok m…Ē?  
\v 12 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, wan k…Ēn p…ôtola k…Ē ames Ňč…õgb…õŇč, nk…Ēn p…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē tek…ôlenc…ôr-…õ?  
\v 13 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôl…õc…õ m…Ē, n…ônc…ôr…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč awut anu ca y…Ēt…Ēt-…õ, Kas k…ôndenaŇčkan…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ēn k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôK…Ēm aŇč…õ Ňčantola k…Ē Ňči m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôluks…õ moloku ma yem ny…õ anabonc…õ k…Ē m…Ē 
\r Mat 12.22-30; Mark 3.22-27 
\p  
\v 14 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma Yesu p…ôcb…õl…ôs Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc nŇč…õ Ňč…õnas…ĒŇč…õ fum w…ôl…Ēma k…ôt…Ēlok-loku m…Ē. Nt…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčowur k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôt…Ēlok-loku w…ôkak…Ē …õy…õf…õ k…ôlok-loku, k…Ē cusu c…ôwos k…ônay k'afum f…ôp.  
\v 15 Mba k…Ē afum al…Ēma Ňčaloku: ¬ęB…õls…õbul, w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc, …õmb…õls…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc.¬Ľ  
\v 16 Nt…õ al…Ēma ŇčafaŇč k…ôsump…ôr k…Ē d…ômoloku m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawer k…Ē a p…ôment…ôr \k t…Ēy…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…õw…õy-w…õy tin nt…õ tement…ôr a Kanu k…ôsom k…Ē m…Ē\k*.  
\v 17 Mba nt…õ Yesu …õnac…ôr…õ p…õc…õmc…õmn…õ paŇčan m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęAt…Ēf o at…Ēf ny…õ Ňč…õŇčy…õf…ôrn…õ Ňčis…ôrka m…Ē, Ňč…õŇčl…ôps…ôr k…ôl…õc…õ. W…Ēl…Ē wa Ňči w…õt…õmp…õn…õ win win.  
\v 18 Awa, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a Sentani s…ôyi k…ôy…õf…ôrn…õ sis…ôrka-…õ, c…ôke c…Ē d…õb…õ da si d…õntam k…ôc…ôm…õ gbiŇč-…õ? Bawo n…ôloku a B…õls…õbul imb…õls…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc.  
\v 19 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ina Yesu, B…õls…õbul imb…õls…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc-…õ, afum anu oŇč, an'…Ē Ňčamb…õls…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc-…õ? Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ akak…Ē yati Ňčandey…Ēn…õ akiti anu m…Ē.  
\v 20 Mba k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a k…ôtam ka Kanu k'imb…õls…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc-…õ, awa d…õb…õ da Kanu dender haŇč nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē fum w…ôka s…Ēk…ôt …Ēnt…Ēmp…ôr posutn…õn…õ-…õ, ombum daka d…Ēn belbel ta t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…õn…ôŇčk di-…õ.  
\v 22 Mba k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ …õmb…õk k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr ender p…ôsut k…Ē k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ p…ôtam k…Ē-…õ, w…ôkak…Ē …õmbaŇč…ôr k…Ē yosutn…õn…õ y…Ēn ny…õ …õnalaŇč m…Ē, p…ôl…õk daka d…Ēn f…ôp p…ôyer…ôs.  
\v 23 Nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēyi k…Ē ina m…Ē, enter im, mba nw…õ …Ēnt…ĒloŇčkan'em m…Ē, …õsams…ôr'em.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôlukus ka Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc 
\r Mat 12.43-45 
\p  
\v 24 ¬ęNt…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčowur fum nw…õ d…ôris m…Ē, Ňč…õcyara-yara mofo mowosu Ňč…õct…õn d…ôk…ôŇčes…ôm, mba Ňč…õnas…Ēt…Ē f…õ, k…Ē Ňčolokun…õ: ‚ÄĻIlukus nde k…ôl…Ē kem nk…õ inawur disr…õ m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 25 Nt…õ Ňčolukus m…Ē, k…Ē Ňč…õmb…ôp k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē paf…õŇč ki, palomp…ôs ki belbel.  
\v 26 Awa! K…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ē, Ňč…õt…õn y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ny…õ y…õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôl…õc…õ y…õtas Ňči m…Ē, k…Ē y…õmb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē disr…õ k…Ē y…õnd…õ. Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôl…õc p…ônaŇčkan…õ fum nw…õ p…ôtas t…Ēk…Ē p…ônayi k…Ē t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 P…ôt…Ēt posoku 
\p  
\v 27 Yesu eyi k…ôloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma oŇčkul…ôrn…õ k…ônay ka afum akak…Ē dac…Ē: ¬ęP…ôb…Ēt kor nk…õ k…ônab…õk…ôs …ôm m…Ē, k…Ē m…õs…õ mm…õ anam…õs…ôr'am m…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 28 Mba k…Ē Yesu oŇčkul…õ: ¬ęP…ôb…Ēt aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta Kanu, Ňčam…õŇčk…ôrn…õ ti m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôwe ka \k t…Ēy…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…Ēl…Ēma nt…õ t…õy…õf…õ nde Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē\k* 
\r Mat 12.38-42 
\p  
\v 29 Nt…õ k…ônay ka afum k…ôncm…õpn…õ Yesu m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôloku: ¬ęD…õt…õmp d…õl…õc dentes…õ f…õ. \k T…õgb…õk…ôr…õ nt…õ tement…ôr a Kanu k…ôsom im m…Ē \k* t…Ē Ňčayi k…ôwer im, mba ali tin af…Ēs…Ēment…ôr Ňča k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ta Yunusa-…õ.  
\v 30 Bawo t…Ēk…Ē teta Yunusa t…õnay…Ēn…õ aka Niniwe t…Ēy…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…õw…õy-w…õy m…Ē, it…Ē teta Wan ka W…ôrkun tendes…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…õt…õmp dant…õ t…Ēy…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…õw…õy-w…õy.  
\v 31 W…ôb…õra ka at…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčeyi Yisrayel k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt m…Ē, endetim…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da kiti k…Ē afum a d…õt…õmp dand…õ, p…ôbonc…õ Ňča k…ôt…Ēwos…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes k…ôt…Ēt, bawo p…ôb…Ēl…õ p'…õnay…õf…õ k…ôdec…ôŇčk…ôl k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes k…ôt…Ēt ka Sulemani. Mba fum eyi d…õ nw…õ …õntas Sulemani d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ē.  
\v 32 Afum a Niniwe Ňčandey…õf…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Kanu k…ôndeboc kiti ka afum f…ôp m…Ē, Ňčabonc…õ afum a d…õt…õmp dand…õ k…ôt…Ēs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc, bawo kawandi ka Yunusa k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ aka Niniwe k…ôs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan y…õl…õc k…Ē Ňčalomp. Fum eyi nu dac…Ē nw…õ …õntas Yunusa d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca lamp da dis 
\r Mat 5.15; 6.22-23 
\p  
\v 33 ¬ęFum nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēf…Ēmot lamp p…ôk…ôŇčk di k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ p…ôm…õŇčk di, mba p…ôfos p…Ē anc…ômb…ôr di nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aŇč…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ m…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk p…ôwaŇčk…ôra.  
\v 34 D…Ēf…Ēr dam d…Ēy…Ēn…õ lamp da dis. K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēr dam dentes…õ-…õ, dis dam f…ôp doŇčmotn…õ, mba k…Ē d…Ēf…Ēr dam d…Ēnt…Ētes…õ-…õ, dis dam s…Ē kubump k…Ē deŇčyi.  
\v 35 M…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ta p…ôwaŇčk…ôra mp…õ pey'…ôm d…ôris m…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn'am kubump.  
\v 36 K…Ē dis dam domot ta tofo o tofo teyi nt…õ teyi kubump m…Ē, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē dis dam f…ôp d…õmar, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē lamp doŇčmot …ôm k…Ē dendemar-…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôbonc…õ aFarisi k…Ē at…ôks…õ a sariy…õ kiciya 
\r Mat 23.1-36; Mark 12.38-40 
\p  
\v 37 Nt…õ Yesu …õnayi k…ôlok-loku m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôFarisi w…ôl…Ēma …õl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôk…Ēdi yeri d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē nde nd…Ēr…Ēn. K…Ē Yesu …õmb…õr…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ am…õsa kiriŇč.  
\v 38 K…Ē p…ônciyan…õ w…ôFarisi nw…õ nt…õ Yesu …õnat…Ēsump…ôr saliye \f + \fr 11:38 \ft  C…ôFarisi, k…Ē fum …ĒŇčk…Ē k…ôdi yeri-…õ, m…õn…õ p…ôgb…ôt k…ôr…õsna waca d…ôromun.\f* k…ôr…õsna a p…ôdedi yeri m…Ē.  
\v 39 Mba k…Ē W…ôb…õ oloku k…Ē: ¬ęN…ôna aFarisi, ap…ôlet k…Ē ap…Ēt tak…ôroŇč y…Ē n…ôŇčs…Ēk…ôs, mba b…ôk…ôc yonu disr…õ n…ôlas…ôrn…õ deke d…ôris k…Ē k…ôy…Ē mes m…õl…õc.  
\v 40 N…ôna at…Ēc…ôr…õ mes, Kanu nk…õ k…ôlomp…ôs tadar…ôŇč m…Ē, baf…Ē ki k…ôlomp…ôs s…Ē tedisr…õ ba?\f + \fr 11:40 \fq Kanu nk…õ k…ôlomp…ôs tadar…ôŇč m…Ē, baf…Ē ki k…ôlomp…ôs s…Ē tedisr…õ ba?\ft  k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ¬ęnw…õ olomp…ôs tadar…ôŇč m…Ē, baf…Ē nk…Ēn olomp…ôs s…Ē tedisr…õ ba?¬Ľ\f* 
\v 41 N…ôcpoc…õ at…Ēy…Ē daka mp…õ peŇčyi s…ôp…Ēt k…Ē d…ôp…ôlet yonu m…Ē, f…ôp fa yi f…ôndes…Ēk nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 42 Mba p…ôl…õc peyi nu n…ôna aFarisi! Bawo n…ôn'…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč Kanu faril…õ fa m…õrk…õt k…Ē malaŇčkan, mba n…ôcsak dolompu k…Ē k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka Kanu. Mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē p…ômar pacy…Ē, mba ta n…ôcp…ôl…ôrn…õ k…ôcy…Ē m…õlp…ôs m…Ēk…Ē de.  
\v 43 P…ôl…õc…ôr nu n…ôna aFarisi, bawo n…ômb…Ēt…ôr pacs…ĒŇč nu d…ôk…ônd…õ mofo mm…õ aŇčlel…ôs nu m…Ē, nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif k…Ē k…ôyif k…ôlel nde amb…ôps…õn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 44 P…ôl…õc peyi nu, bawo n…ôyi p…ôm…Ē cufu nc…õ ant…Ēgb…õk…ôr…õ m…Ē, pack…Ēt ci k…ôroŇč ta anc…ôr…õ-…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 45 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma at…ôks…õ a sariy…õ dac…Ē …õl…õk moloku, k'oŇčkul…ôrn…õ: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, k…Ē m…ôloku tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, m…ôŇčsunu s…Ē s…ôna!¬Ľ  
\v 46 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęP…ôl…õc…ôr s…Ē n…ôna, at…ôks…õ a sariy…õ! Bawo n…ôn'…õŇčsar…ôs…ôr afum y…õsar…õ ny…õ yoncuca k…ôsar…õ m…Ē, ta n…ôŇčwos…õ k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õn…õ yi ali t…õl…ôr tonu-…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 47 ¬ęP…ôl…õc peyi nu! Bawo n…ôn'…õnc…ômb…ôr…õ cufu ca sayib…õ masar m…õc…õm-c…õm…ôs, sayib…õ aŇč…õ atem anu Ňčanadif…ôt m…Ē.  
\v 48 K…ôment…ôr k…Ē m…ônd…õ tant…õ a m…ôna s…Ē m…ôwos…õ m…Ēy…Ē ma atem anu mam…Ēk…Ē, bawo Ňča Ňčanadif…ôt sayib…õ sa Kanu, k…Ē n…ôna n…ôc…ômb…ôr cufu c…ôŇčan!  
\v 49 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes ka Kanu disr…õ, k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻIndeken…õ Ňča sayib…õ k…Ē asom.‚Äļ K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt aŇč…õ, k…Ē Ňčant…Ēr…ôs ak…Ē.  
\v 50 It'endes…ĒŇč…õ afum a t…õm tant…õ k…ôdek…Ēsar…õ kiciya ka k…ôdif ka sayib…õ saŇčs…õ f…ôp, k…ôl…õk nt…õ doru doncop m…Ē,  
\v 51 k…ôy…õf…õ mecir ma Ab…õl, haŇč k…ôb…ôp ka ma Sakary, nw…õ anadif aŇčgbip k…Ē \k tetek toloŇčn…õ \k* dac…Ē m…Ē. ∆źy, iloku nu ti: Andek…Ēyif ti afum a d…õt…õmp dand…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 52 ¬ęP…ôl…õc peyi nu, n…ôna at…ôks…õ sariy…õ! Bawo n…ôliŇč tasapa pa k…ôc…ôr…õ. N…ônas…ôrka n…ômb…õr…õ f…õ, n…ôyams…ôr s…Ē ak…Ē ŇčafaŇč k…ôb…õr…õ m…Ē Ňčab…õr…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 53 Nt…õ Yesu owur nde k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ at…ôks…õ sariy…õ k…Ē aFarisi nn…Ē eyi m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr k…Ē, Ňčacyif…ôt k…Ē mes f…ôp,  
\v 54 Ňčacc…ôp…õ k…Ē mowul, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčanen…õ k…Ē yem d…ômoloku m…Ē. 
\c 12  
\s1 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ta n…ôbaŇč…õn…õ dofum 
\r Mat 10.26-27 
\p  
\v 1 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē afum wul wul ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ, p…ôwur…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē ŇčadeŇčs…ôr…õn…õ, k…Ē Yesu oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč k…ôr…õsna: ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ lebin da aFarisi nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôbaŇč…õn…õ dofum m…Ē.  
\v 2 Tes o tes t…Ēgb…Ēpn…õ teyi f…õ nt…õ ant…Ēdec…õŇč paloku m…Ē, nt…õ o nt…õ t…ĒŇčgb…Ēpn…õ f…õ nt…õ ant…Ēdec…ôr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 3 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ o nt…õ aŇčloku nu kubump m…Ē, n…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ ti k…ôloku daŇč peŇč, k…Ē nt…õ n…ôŇčm…õŇčk…ôs fum d…õl…ôŇč…ôs dukul…Ē m…Ē, anded…ôŇčk ti p…ôp…ĒŇč mofo m…õb…ôps…õn…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Nw…õ p…ômar n…ônes…õ m…Ē 
\r Mat 10.28-31 
\p  
\v 4 ¬ęIcloku nu ti, n…ôna anapa em: Ta n…ônes…õ aŇč…õ Ňčandif dis gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, k…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda ta Ňčantam t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm s…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 5 Indement…ôr nu nw…õ p…ômar n…ônes…õ m…Ē: N…ônes…õ nw…õ endif p…ôkaf…ôl…õ s…Ē p…ôtam k…ôl…ôm …ôm yahanama m…Ē. ∆źy! Icloku nu, nk…Ēn p…ômar n…ônes…õ!  
\v 6 Baf…Ē gbaŇča k…ôcam…ôt y'ancam…ôs f…ôr…õŇčk m…õr…ôŇč? Awa! Icloku nu a Kanu k…ôf…Ēp…ôl ali Ňčin yi dac…Ē.  
\v 7 Ali d…õlay da c…ôfon ca domp donu Kanu k…ônc…ôr…õ di f…ôp. Ta n…ônes…õ, nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē n…ôy…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ nd…õ d…õmb…õk d…õtas da gbaŇča yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčendet…ôks…õ p…ômar ac…õps…õ a Yesu k…ôloku m…Ē 
\r Mat 10.32-33; 12.32; 10.19-20 
\p  
\v 8 ¬ęIcloku nu ti: Nw…õ o nw…õ owos…õ afum f…Ēr kiriŇč a ina Yesu …Ēy…Ē k…Ē m…Ē, Wan ka W…ôrkun endes…Ēr…ômn…õwos…õ nn…Ē f…Ēr ya m…õl…õk…õ a Kanu kiriŇč, a w…ôk…Ēn fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ.  
\v 9 Mba m…ôna nw…õ m…ôndek…Ēbup…ôr…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ kem afum f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, Wan ka W…ôrkun endek…Ēs…Ēr…ômn…õ sim…õ m…ôna w…ôkayi m…õl…õk…õ a Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 10 Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčloku p…ôl…õc pa Wan ka W…ôrkun m…Ē, andek…ĒŇčaŇčn…õn…õ w…ôkayi, mba nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēl…Ēm…ôs \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* m…Ē, af…Ēdek…ĒŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 11 ¬ęK'ande packek…ôr…õ nu nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti nda aboc kiti, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti ab…õ-…õ, ta n…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ p…ôlar…ôm t…õyacn…õ tonu, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēloku m…Ē,  
\v 12 bawo \k Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu\k* Ňčendek…Ēt…ôks…õ nu gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar n…ôndek…Ēloku m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca w…ôka daka w…ôt…Ēc…ôr…õ tes 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma oloku Yesu k…ônay kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, m…ôloku w…õnc im a s…ôyer…õn…õ k…õ kosu!¬Ľ  
\v 14 K…Ē Yesu oloku fum w…ôkak…Ē: ¬ęAn'…õc…ômb…ôr im k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôboc kiti nu dac…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôyer nu daka donu-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda, k…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka k…ôy…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm, bawo baf…Ē daka dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēt…Ēmp…ôr tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta fum doru, ali w…ôkayi p…ôy…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 16 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča capaf…Ē c…ôl…Ēma: ¬ęFum w…ôka daka w…ôl…Ēma …õnay…Ē nt…Ēf ny…õ yenctes…õ y…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 17 P…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ, p…ôcyifn…õ: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c…Ē indey…Ē-…õ? Bawo iy…Ē f…õ k…ôfo nk…õ iŇčk…ĒloŇčka y…õt…õl yem f…ôp m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 18 K…Ē fum nw…õ olokun…õ, ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē indey…Ē: K…ôw…Ēk…ôc k'iŇčk…Ē c…õl…õ cem, is…õl nc…õ c…ômb…õk m…Ē, iloŇčka ci disr…õ mal…Ē k…Ē ca yem y…Ēl…Ēma.  
\v 19 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, ilokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ¬ęIy…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm d…õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ meren m…õlar…ôm. IŇčes…ôm oŇč, idi, imun, iwol…ôs.¬Ľ‚Äļ  
\v 20 Mba k…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôna W…ôtoŇčkulu, W…ôt…Ēc…ôr…õ tes! Pibi pa m…Ēk…Ē yati p…Ē andewer …ôm kiyi kam doru. T…Ēk…Ē m…ôlomp…ôs m…Ē, an…Ē m…ôndesak…ôr…õ ti-…õ?‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 21 K…Ē Yesu …Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęIt…Ē p…ôyi fum nw…õ endeloŇčka daka d…Ēn, a ta Kanu k…ôŇčn…ôŇčk k…ôy…Ē k…Ēn daka m…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôlaŇč Kanu 
\r Mat 6.25-34 
\p  
\v 22 K…Ē Yesu oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč: ¬ęIt' …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ iloku nu: Ta n…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ p…ôlar…ôm tecep…ôr…õn…õ tonu doru, paka mp…õ n…ôndedi m…Ē. Ta n…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ s…Ē teta dis donu p…Ēk…Ē n…ôndeb…õrn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 23 Bawo k…ôyi w…ôyeŇč k…ôncep…ôr yeri, k…Ē dis dencep…ôr yamos.  
\v 24 N…ôk…Ēkc…õ b…õmp yaser: Y…Ēf…Ēgbal defet, y…Ēf…Ēt…õl, y…Ēf…Ēm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ, y…Ēy…Ē f…õ c…õl…õ, mba Kanu k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč yi yeri. N…ôna n…ôncep…ôr b…õmp yay…Ēk…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ!  
\v 25 Fum w…ôre eyi nu dac…Ē nw…õ m…õc…õmc…õmn…õ m…Ēn m…õntam k…ôb…Ēl…ôs kiyi k…Ēn doru ali kururu katin gboŇč m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 26 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a n…ôf…Ētam ali tes t…õf…õt-…õ, ake n…ôŇčk…Ēc…õm-c…õmn…õn…õ t…Ēk…Ē t…õnc…ôm…õ m…Ē?  
\v 27 N…ôk…Ēkc…õ nt…õ y…õl…õŇčk ya dal…õ yompoŇč m…Ē: Y…Ēf…Ēb…ôc, y…Ēf…Ēdu yamos, mba icloku nu, ali w…ôb…õ Sulemani k…Ē daka da debeki d…Ēn f…ôp …õnas…Ēt…Ē f…õ yamos ny…õ y…õnates…õ p…ôm…Ē p…õl…õŇčk pap…Ēk…Ē pin m…Ē.  
\v 28 Yika yeyi m…Ēk…Ē dal…õ, alna pacl…ôm yi d…ôn…õnc, mba Kanu k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ômar yi. N…ôna, apic…õ k…ôlaŇč, n…ôntam k…ôlaŇč tes tin: Pipic…õ oŇč c…ôke o c…ôke, Kanu k…ôndeb…õr n…ôna apic…õ k…ôlaŇč yamos p…ôcep…ôr tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 29 K…Ē n…ôna, ta n…ôt…Ēr…ôsn…õ k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ teta yeri y…Ēk…Ē n…ônde n…ôcdi m…Ē, ta n…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ teta yomun…ôs y…Ēk…Ē n…ônde n…ôcmun…ôs m…Ē.  
\v 30 Bawo mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē at…Ēc…ôr…õ Kanu a doru dand…õ Ňčant…õn t…õm f…ôp. Mba n…ôna, Kas konu k…ônc…ôr…õ a p…ômar n…ôy…Ē ca yay…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 31 N…ôt…õn d…õb…õ da Kanu, nk…Ēn Kanu endedeŇč…ôr…õ nu ca yay…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Daka kiyi ka darenc 
\r Mat 6.19-21 
\p  
\v 32 ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ, n…ôna ac…õps'em dar…ôŇč! Bawo p…ômb…Ēt Papa konu k…ôs…ĒŇč nu d…õb…õ.  
\v 33 N…ôcam…ôs daka donu, n…ôpoc…õ k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē at…Ēy…Ē daka. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ daka da alna ndena Kanu m…Ē. Daka da ndena Kanu d…Ēf…Ēlip! D…ôndo w…ôke eyi f…õ nw…õ …ĒŇčl…Ēt…ôrn…õ di m…Ē. Ate Ňčeyi f…õ nŇč…õ Ňč…ĒŇčs…Ēm di m…Ē.  
\v 34 Bawo k…ôfo nk…õ daka donu deŇčyi m…Ē, dif…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňčonu ŇčeŇčyi.¬Ľ 
\s1 Ab…ôc aŇč…õ Ňčambum m…Ē 
\p  
\v 35 ¬ęN…ôgb…ôncn…õ s…ôb…õl…õt d…ôfi, n…ômot s…ôlamp sonu, n…ôc…ôm…õ belbel!  
\v 36 N…ôyi p…ôm…Ē abum aŇč…õ Ňčandekar w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan k…ôder k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôŇčgbaŇčn…õ m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôkak…Ē …Ēnck…Ēnader p…ôsut-sut kumba, Ňča Ňčagbit…õ k…Ē ki kat…ôna m…Ē.  
\v 37 P…ôb…Ēt acar akak…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan, …Ēnck…Ēnader p…ôb…ôp k…Ē p…ôckar k…ôgbit…õ k…Ē m…Ē. Amina! Icloku nu ti: Endegb…ôncn…õ b…õl…õt, p…ôd…ôs acar akak…Ē d…ôm…õsa k…ôk…Ēdi yeri, nk…Ēn p…ôyer…ôs Ňča yi.  
\v 38 Ali p…ôy…Ēn…õ a c…õk-c…õk c'ender, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ d…Ēs…Ēka, mba k'…õmb…ôp Ňča ta Ňčandir…õ-…õ, p…ôb…Ēt Ňča!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 39 ¬ęN…ôc…ôr…õ nt…õ belbel a k…Ē w…ôka k…ôl…Ē …õnc…ôr…õ t…õm nt…õ w…ôke endeder m…Ē-…õ, …Ēf…Ēsak k…Ē p…ôb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ.  
\v 40 N…ôna s…Ē, n…ôc…ôm…õ n…ôckar! Bawo Wan ka W…ôrkun endeder t…õm nt…õ n…ônt…Ēy…Ē k…Ē amera m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 W…ôb…ôc w…ôlompu k…Ē w…ôb…ôc w…ôt…Ēlomp 
\r Mat 24.45-51 
\p  
\v 41 K…Ē Piy…õr eyif Yesu: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, s…ôna gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňč…Ē m…ôŇčloku capaf…Ē canc…õ, ka f…ôp f…Ē m…ôŇčloku ci ba?¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 42 K…Ē Mariki oloku: ¬ęW…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka w…ôre esekt…ôrn…õ mariki m…Ēn, p…ôck…Ēt…õn…õ amera k…ôy…Ē p…ôt…Ēt-…õ? Nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ mariki oŇčloku: ‚ÄĻIs…ĒŇč …ôm y…õb…ôc ny…õ: M…ôcs…ĒŇč yeri afum aŇč…õ Ňčayi k…ôb…ôc'em m…Ē, t…õm nt…õ p…ômar m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 43 P…ôb…Ēt w…ômar…ôs w…ôkak…Ē mariki m…Ēn mender m…õb…ôp k…Ē p…ôsump…ôr y…õb…ôc ny…õ …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē!  
\v 44 Iloku nu ti, kance k…Ē: Mariki m…Ēn mendes…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ka daka d…Ēn f…ôp!  
\v 45 Mba k…Ē w…ômar…ôs olokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ‚ÄĻMariki mem …õntay…õf…õ f…õ k…ôder,‚Äļ p…ôy…õf…õ k…ôsut ka amar…ôs arkun k…Ē aran, p…ôcdi yeri, p…ôcmun haŇč p…ôcis-…õ,  
\v 46 mariki ma w…ômar…ôs w…ôkak…Ē endeder d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē k…Ē amera m…Ē, dec nd…õ …Ēnt…Ēc…ôr…õ m…Ē, p…ôb…õl…ôs w…ômar…ôs w…ôkak…Ē, p…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ant…Ēr…ôs acar at…Ēnen…õ mariki maŇčan m…Ē.  
\v 47 W…ôcar nw…õ …õnc…ôr…õ t…õfaŇč ta mariki m…Ēn m…Ē, ta olomp…ôsn…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, ta …ĒŇčy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē mariki m…Ēn …õfaŇč m…Ē, aŇčsut w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē k…ôsut k…ôp…ĒŇč.  
\v 48 Mba w…ôcar nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēc…ôr…õ t…õfaŇč ta mariki m…Ēn m…Ē, p…ôciya-ciya k…ôlomp…ôs m…Ē, w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē p…ôpic p…Ē aŇčsut k…Ē. K'anas…ĒŇč fum p…ôlar…ôm-…õ, p…ôlar…ôm p'aŇčwer k…Ē. K'anas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôm…õŇčk p…ôlar…ôm-…õ, aŇčnaŇčkan…õ k…ôwer k…Ē p…ôlar…ôm.¬Ľ 
\s1 Teta Yesu t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôgb…õy…õn…õ 
\r Mat 10.34-36 
\p  
\v 49 ¬ęN…õnc d'inder k…ôb…õr doru, k'ifaŇč…õ di k…ômar!  
\v 50 P…ômar is…Ēt…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun teta Kanu, k…Ē k…ôŇčwon im k…ôyi.  
\v 51 N…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a p…ôforu p'iŇčk…õr…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč doru ba? Ala de, mba icloku nu a k…ôgb…õy k'iŇčk…õr…õ.  
\v 52 K…ôy…õf…õ oŇč tant…õ aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ Ňčayi k…ôcam…ôt k…ôl…Ē disr…õ m…Ē, Ňčandegb…õy…õn…õ ak…Ē Ňčayi maas ak…Ē Ňčayi m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 53 Kas k…ôgb…õy wan k…Ēn w…ôrkun, wan w…ôrkun p…ôgb…õy kas, k…õr…õ k…ôgb…õy wan k…Ēn w…ôran, wan w…ôran p…ôgb…õy k…õr…õ, k…Ēnc…ôra k…ôgb…õy w…ôran ka wan k…Ēn, wans…Ē p…ôgb…õy k…Ēnc…ôra.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôc…ôr…õn…õ ka k…Ēm 
\r Mat 16.2-3 
\p  
\v 54 K…Ē Yesu oloku s…Ē k…ônay ka afum: ¬ęK…Ē n…ôn…ôŇčk k…ôp k…ôgb…ôp…ôrn…õ ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, n…ôŇčkul…õ katina: ‚ÄĻK…ôder k…Ē w…ôcaf…ôn endeder!‚Äļ P…ôf…Ēwon w…ôcaf…ôn p…ôder.  
\v 55 Mba k…Ē n…ôn…ôŇčk afef Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt Ňčocwur-…õ, n…ôloku: ‚ÄĻK…ôwon…õ k…Ē p…ônder,‚Äļ t…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčloku ti m…Ē, it…Ē teŇčyi.  
\v 56 N…ôna AbaŇč…õn…õ dofum! N…ôntam k…ôc…ôr…õ m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ma t…Ēk…Ē ant…Ēf k…Ē k…Ēm yeŇčyi m…Ē. Ta ake t…Ē n…ônt…Ētam k…ôc…ôr…õn…õ t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta t…õm tant…õ n…ôyi m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ 
\s1 M…ôt…õn k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē w…ôter…õn…õ kam 
\r Mat 5.25-26 
\p  
\v 57 ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônt…Ēc…ôr…õn…õ n…ônas…ôrka t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar n…ôy…Ē m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 58 K…Ē m…ôndek…Ē k…Ē w…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ kam d…ôŇčkiti-…õ, m…ôwos…õ n…ôt…ôŇčn…õ d…Ēp…Ē k…ôr…õsna. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, eŇčkek…ôr'am dab…õ. W…ôboc kiti p…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm w…ôs…Ēdar nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēb…õr …ôm d…ôbili m…Ē.  
\v 59 Iclok'…ôm m…ôf…Ēwur d…ôndo ta m…ôlip k…ôluks…õ tap…ôsam p…Ēk…Ē m…ônt…Ēmp…ôr…õ k…Ē m…Ē-…õ. 
\c 13  
\s1 N…ôs…ôkp…ôr mera, n…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, n…ôŇčfi! 
\p  
\v 1 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē k…Ē afum al…Ēma Ňčanader Ňčal…Ēm…ôr Yesu t…Ēk…Ē Pilat …õnadif…ôt aKalile al…Ēma nt…õ ŇčancloŇčn…õ Kanu m…Ē. It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Pilat …õnan…ĒŇčk…ôl mecir ma afum k…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôŇčan.  
\v 2 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a k'anadif…ôt aKalile akak…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, a tement…ôr oŇč a ŇčananaŇčkan…õ k…ôciya Ňčatas aKalile alp…ôs ak…Ē anat…Ēdif m…Ē ba?  
\v 3 Ala! Icloku nu: Mba k…Ē n…ônt…Ēs…ôkp…ôr mera n…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč-…õ,\f + \fr 13:3 \fq N…ôntubi\ft  it…Ē ¬ęN…ôs…ôkp…ôr…õ m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēt…Ēt m…Ēy…Ē m…õl…õc.¬Ľ\f* tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē n…ôndel…ôs…ôrn…õ f…ôp p…ôm…Ē akak…Ē.  
\v 4 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, afum aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-maas aŇč…õ k…ôl…Ē ka Siloye k…ônaw…õk…ôrn…õ k…ôdif m…Ē, n…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a Ňča ŇčananaŇčkan…õ k…ôciya Ňčatas aka Yerusal…õm alp…ôs aŇč…õ ba?  
\v 5 Ala, icloku nu, mba k…Ē n…ônt…Ēs…ôkp…ôr mera n…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč-…õ, n…ôna s…Ē f…ôp n…ôŇčfi p…ôm…Ē Ňča!¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca k…ôt…Ēk k…ôkom nk…õ k…ônat…Ēy…Ē yokom m…Ē 
\p  
\v 6 K…Ē Yesu oloku s…Ē capaf…Ē nc…õ: ¬ęFum w…ôl…Ēma …õnab…Ēf k…ôt…Ēk ka fik dal…õ d…Ēn dac…Ē. K'ender k…ôt…õn yokom ya ki, mba k'…õmb…ôp k…ôt…Ēk ka fik nk…õ ta k…ôŇčkom-…õ.  
\v 7 Awa, k'oloku w…ôb…ôc k…Ēn w…ôk…Ē oncbum…õ k…Ē dal…õ m…Ē: ‚ÄĻMeren maas m…Ē mam…õ nt…õ inder k…ôpim yokom ya k…ôt…Ēk kaŇčk…õ m…Ē, mba if…Ēs…Ēt…Ē. Awa m…ôc…õp ki! Ta ake t…Ē k…ôndec…ôm…õn…õ, k…ôbaŇč ant…Ēf gb…ôc…ôr…ôm-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 8 K…Ē w…ôbum ka dal…õ oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻMariki, m…ôsak k…ôt…Ēk k…ôkom kaŇčk…õ k…ôren nk…õ gb…ôc…ôr…ôm pam…Ēm…ôn s…Ē. Indekay haŇč in…ĒŇčk…ôr, ib…õr ma s…Ē nc…õk-c…õk-a.  
\v 9 K…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē teyi-…õ, t…Ēl…Ēma k…ôŇčkom dok, k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, m…ôc…õp ki.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôtam…ôs ka w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē 
\p  
\v 10 K…ôt…ôks…õ k…Ē Yesu …õncnd…õ d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif d…Ēl…Ēma d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē.  
\v 11 W…ôran w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi d…ônda nw…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…õnas…ĒŇč…õ k…ôt…Ēk…Ēt k…ôy…õf…õ meren w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-maas m…Ē. …õnanutn…õ, ta …õntam k…ôt…õnc…õ-…õ.  
\v 12 Nt…õ Yesu …õn…ôŇčk w…ôran nw…õ m…Ē, k'ewe k…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôran, docu dam d…õsak …ôm.¬Ľ  
\v 13 K…Ē Yesu endeŇč k…Ē k…ôca. Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õnt…õnc…õ, k'…õy…õf…õ \k k…ôcam\k* debeki da Kanu.  
\v 14 Mba k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif dad…Ēk…Ē, nt…õ Yesu …õnatam…ôs w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôb…õ nw…õ oloku afum: ¬ęMata cam…ôt-tin meyi mm…õ p…ômar pacb…ôc m…Ē, n…ôder n…ôt…õn k…ôtam…ôsn…õ mata mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, mba ta n…ôder d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm da Kanu.¬Ľ  
\v 15 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęN…ôna abaŇč…õn…õ dofum: D…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē, an'…Ēnt…Ēgbeki wana w…Ēn, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, s…Ēfale s…Ēn p…ôkek…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēmun-…õ?  
\v 16 A w…ôran nw…õ owur dokom da Abraham, a k…Ē Sentani s…ôsump…ôr s…ôkot k…ôy…õf…õ meren w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-maas m…Ē, p…ômar f…õ pasik…ôli k…Ē b…ônda yay…Ēk…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm ba?¬Ľ  
\v 17 Yesu k…ôloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ater …Ēn f…ôp k…ôlap…ôrn…õ, mba p…ônab…Ēt k…ônay f…ôp, m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēp…ĒŇč mam…Ēk…Ē Yesu …Ēncy…Ē m…Ē. 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca t…õŇčgb…õn t…õf…õt 
\r Mat 13.31-32; Mark 4.30-32 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē Yesu eyif s…Ē: ¬ęAke d…õb…õ da Kanu dowur…õn…õ-…õ? Ak'indetubc…õn…õ di-…õ?  
\v 19 T…õŇčgb…õn t…õf…õt\f + \fr 13:19 \fq T…õŇčgb…õn t…õf…õt \ft = t…õŇčgb…õn t…õf…õt ta t…Ēk ya dal…õ, nt…õ tompoŇč m…Ē-…õ, k…ôt…Ēk ka ki k…ômb…õk p…ôtas t…Ēk y…Ēl…Ēma ya dal…õ.\f* nt…õ fum …õl…õk, p…ôb…Ēf dal…õ d…Ēn disr…õ m…Ē. T…õŇčgb…õn tat…Ēk…Ē topoŇč, p…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôt…Ēk k…ôp…ĒŇč, b…õmp yeder y…Ēl…Ē wara waw…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Totubc…õn…õ ta lebin 
\r Mat 13.33 
\p  
\v 20 K…Ē Yesu oloku s…Ē: ¬ęAk'indetubc…õn…õ d…õb…õ da Kanu-…õ?  
\v 21 \k D…õb…õ da Kanu\k* dowur…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē lebin nd…õ w…ôran …õŇčl…õk p…ôn…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ di k…ômbefe kilo w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) m…Ē. K…Ē k…ômbefe f…ôp k…ômp…õ!.¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ d…õw…õk…õn…õ 
\r Mat 7.13-14; 21-23 
\p  
\v 22 Nt…õ Yesu …õncali s…ôdare s…ôf…õt k…Ē s…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôk…Ē ka Yerusal…õm m…Ē, p…ôct…ôks…õn…õ s…Ē afum.  
\v 23 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma eyif k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, afum apic Ňč…Ē Kanu k…ôndek…Ēyac ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča:  
\v 24 ¬ęN…ôna s…Ē n…ôs…õp k…ôdek…Ēb…õr…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ d…õw…õk…õn…õ dad…Ēk…Ē, bawo icloku nu: Afum alar…ôm Ňčandes…õp k…ôb…õr…õ ka di, mba Ňčaf…Ēdek…Ētam.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 25 ¬ęK…Ē w…ôka k…ôl…Ē endek…Ēy…õf…õ p…ôcaŇč kumba, n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôŇčyi doru m…Ē, n…ôdey…õf…õ k…ôsut-sut kumba, n…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻMariki m…ôgbit…õ su!‚Äļ T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē endeluks…õ nu: ‚ÄĻInc…ôr…õ f…õ k…ôca nk…õ n…ôy…õf…õ m…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 26 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē n…ôndek…Ēcop k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻS…ônadi yeri, s…ômun k…Ē m…ôna, m…ôct…ôks…õ nde s…ôp…Ē s…ôp…ĒŇč sa dare dosu.‚Äļ  
\v 27 Nk…Ēn p…ôcloku nu, ‚ÄĻInc…ôr…õ f…õ aka nde n…ôy…Ēn…õ m…Ē! N…ôb…Ēl'em day, f…ôp fonu n…ôŇčy…Ē mes m…õl…õc!‚Äļ  
\v 28 Dif…Ē k…ôbok k…Ē k…ôŇčaŇč…ôr…õn…õ sek k…ôndek…Ēyi, k…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēn…ôŇčk Abraham, Siyaka, Yakuba k…Ē sayib…õ sa Kanu f…ôp d…õb…õ da Kanu disr…õ, pal…ôm n…ôna dabaŇčka.  
\v 29 Afum Ňčandeder k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ k…Ē nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, k…Ē k…ômerya, Ňčader Ňčand…õ d…õm…õsa nde d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 30 Ti disr…õ, adar…ôŇč Ňčayi aŇč…õ Ňčandek…Ēy…Ēn…õ akiriŇč m…Ē, k…Ē akiriŇč Ňčayi aŇč…õ Ňčandek…Ēy…Ēn…õ adar…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…Ē Yerusal…õm 
\r Mat 23.37-39 
\p  
\v 31 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē aFarisi al…Ēma Ňčander Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ nn…Ē m…Ēk…Ē! bawo Herodu …õfaŇč k…ôdif …ôm.¬Ľ  
\v 32 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôloku ay…Ēf…ôn ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē: K…ôb…õl…ôs y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc k…Ē k…ôtam…ôs k'iyin…õ m…Ēk…Ē k…Ē alna, a indel…ôp…ôs y…õb…ôc yem tataka ta maas.  
\v 33 Mba m…õn…õ ik…Ēt m…Ēk…Ē, alna k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk…Ē, bawo p…ômar f…õ w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu p…ôfi k…ôfo k…ôcuru ta p…ôy…Ēn…õ Yerusal…õm-…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 34 ¬ęYerusal…õm, Yerusal…õm, m…ôna nw…õ m…ôndif sayib…õ m…Ē, m…ôcca-cas aŇč…õ Kanu k…ôŇčsom nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē, is…õp p…ôlar…ôm k…ôloŇčka ka awut am p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ac…Ēk…Ē Ňčokomb…ôra ŇčoŇčloŇčka awut banca ya Ňči d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē! Mba m…ônawos…õ f…õ ti.  
\v 35 Awa n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl! Andesak…ôr…õ nu k…ôl…Ē konu k…ôy…Ē fos. Mba icloku nu: N…ôf…Ēs…Ēn…ôŇčk im, haŇč t…õm t…õb…ôp nt…õ n…ôndeloku: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻKanu k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt nw…õ ender…õn…õ tewe ta Mariki m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\c 14  
\s1 Yesu k…ôtam…ôs ka w…ôcuy w…ôl…Ēma 
\p  
\v 1 Simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm d…Ēl…Ēma, k'awe Yesu nde k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôb…õ ka aFarisi w…ôl…Ēma k…ôk…Ēdi yeri, k…Ē akak…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēkc…õ k…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ docu d…õnak…ôf…ôs m…Ē, p…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē f…Ēr kiriŇč.  
\v 3 K…Ē Yesu eyif at…ôks…õ a sariy…õ k…Ē aFarisi: ¬ęAŇčwos…õ k…ôtam…ôs ka w…ôt…Ētamn…õ simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm ba, ka af…Ēwos…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ ŇčancaŇčk. Awa k…Ē Yesu oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ w…ôt…Ētamn…õ nw…õ, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õntamn…õ, k'…õsak k…Ē a p…ôk…Ē.  
\v 5 Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęAn'eyi nu dac…Ē nw…õ wan k…Ēn, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti wana w…Ēn w…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…ôk…ôl…ômp d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm, ta …õmp…õn…õ wi d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē yati m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē ab…õ akak…Ē Ňčant…Ētam k…ôluks…õ k…Ē m…Ēc…Ēp. 
\s1 Nt…õ aŇčy…õk-y…õk d…ôk…ônd…õ, k…Ē nt…õ aŇčwen…õ fum tes m…Ē 
\p  
\v 7 K…Ē Yesu olok-lok…ôr afum aŇč…õ anawe d…ôk…ôsata m…Ē, bawo …õnak…Ēkc…õ nt…õ akak…Ē ancgbut…ôl…õn…õ d…ôk…ônd…õ d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. K'oloku Ňča:  
\v 8 ¬ęK…Ē fum ew'am k…ôk…Ēt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôsata ka k…ôgbaŇčn…õ k…Ēn-…õ, ta m…ôk…Ē m…ônd…õ d…ôk…ônd…õ d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, bawo t…Ēl…Ēma w…ôka k…ôsata ewe s…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē, nw…õ encep…ôr m…ôna m…Ē.  
\v 9 Ta t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôk…Ē ewe nu k…ôsata m…Ē, k…ôdelok'…ôm: ‚ÄĻM…ôy…õf…õ m…ôsak…ôr…õ nw…õ d…ôk…ônd…õ dad…Ēk…Ē.‚Äļ K…ôlap…ôrn…õ k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…ônd…õ d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē dad…Ēk…Ē k…ôk…Ēnd…õ dadar…ôŇč d…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 10 Mba, k'aw'am k…ôsata-…õ, m…ôk…Ē m…ônd…õ d…ôk…ônd…õ dadar…ôŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nw…õ ew'am k…ôsata m…Ē k'ender p…ôn…ôŇčk …ôm-…õ, p…ôlok'…ôm: ‚ÄĻWanapa, m…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ kiriŇč.‚Äļ Awa t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē m…ôna m…ôlel…õ nn…Ē afum aŇč…õ n…ôŇčk…ĒpaŇčn…õ am…õsa k…ôdi yeri m…Ē.  
\v 11 Nw…õ o nw…õ oyokn…õ m…Ē, andetor…õ k…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ ontor…õ banca m…Ē, andep…õn…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 12 K…Ē Yesu oloku fum nw…õ …õnawe k…Ē k…ôsata m…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē m…ôwe afum k…ôdi yeri y…õraŇč, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti y…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy-…õ, ta m…ôwen…õ yi akos'…ôm aŇča, ta m…ôwen…õ yi aw…õnc …ôm aŇča, ta m…ôwen…õ yi akom…õn…õ am, ta m…ôwen…õ yi and…õ am aka daka. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčadetam k…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča k…ôwen…õ yeri m…Ē.  
\v 13 Mba k…Ē m…ôndewen…õ afum yeri-…õ, m…ôwe at…Ēy…Ē daka, lanyiru, ator…ôr k…Ē at…Ēn…ôŇčk.  
\v 14 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē p…ôb…Ēt …ôm, bawo Ňčay…Ē f…õ daka nd…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ēluks'am k…ôway ka p…ôt…Ēt pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. Kanu gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ôndek…Ētam k…ôluks'am k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē, nde ay…Ē p…ôt…Ēt Ňčandek…Ēy…õf…õ defi m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca yeri ya k…ôsata 
\r Mat 22.1-10 
\p  
\v 15 Nt…õ afum Ňčane moloku mam…õ m…Ē, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ …õnand…õ d…õm…õsa m…Ē, oloku Yesu: ¬ęP…ôb…Ēt m…ôna nw…õ m…ôndek…Ēdi yeri nde akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Yesu oloku fum w…ôkak…Ē: ¬ęFum w…ôl…Ēma …õnaboc k…ôsata k…ôp…ĒŇč, k'ewen…õ ki afum alar…ôm.  
\v 17 Nt…õ t…õm ta k…ôdi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē tendeb…ôp m…Ē, k'osom w…ôcar k…Ēn k…ôk…Ēloku afum aŇč…õ ewe k…ôsata m…Ē: ‚ÄĻN…ôder! Alip k…ôcoŇč.‚Äļ  
\v 18 Mba k…Ē kan-kan …õy…õf…õ k…ôl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē. K…Ē w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôŇčaŇčn…õn'em, dal…õ d'iway id…Ē p…ômar ik…Ē im…Ēm…ôn. Il…õts…õn'am ta m…ôsump…ôr'em ti!‚Äļ  
\v 19 K…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻIway c…ôna c…ôbifti w…ôco, ic'ifaŇč k…ôk…Ēwak. Il…õts…õn'am ta m…ôsump…ôr'em ti!‚Äļ  
\v 20 K…Ē w…ôka maas oloku s…Ē: ‚ÄĻInt…õp k…ôcgbaŇčn…õ, it…Ē int…Ētam k…ôk…Ēn…õ!‚Äļ  
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôcar nw…õ ender p…ôluks…õ mosom mam…Ēk…Ē mariki m…Ēn, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ k…Ē, k'oloku w…ôcar: ‚ÄĻM…ôk…Ē kat…ôna nde mofo m…Ēp…ĒŇč k…Ē nde s…ôp…Ē s…ôp…ĒŇč sa dare! M…ôwen'em at…Ēy…Ē daka, lanyiru, ator…ôr k…Ē at…Ēn…ôŇčk.‚Äļ  
\v 22 K…Ē w…ôcar ender p…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻMariki nt…õ m…ôsom im m…Ē telip, mba yeri y…Ēs…Ēr…Ēc…ôm…õ!‚Äļ  
\v 23 K…Ē mariki m…Ēn oloku k…Ē s…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôk…Ē s…ôp…Ē sa d…ôkulum k…Ē d…ôŇčgbancan, m…ôloku afum Ňčab…õr…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôl…Ē kem k…ôlar…õ m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 24 Bawo, icloku nu: Arkun akak…Ē inanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôwe k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ m…Ē, ali w…ôkin …Ēf…Ēs…Ēdi yeri ya ki.¬Ľ 
\s1 C…ôke c…Ē aŇčyi a patam k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôc…õps…õ ka Yesu dar…ôŇč-…õ 
\r Mat 10.37-38 
\p  
\v 25 K…ônay k…ônac…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč, k…Ē Yesu …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ, k'oloku Ňča:  
\v 26 ¬ęM…ôna nw…õ m…ônc…õps'em dar…ôŇč m…Ē, p…ômar m…ôtam k…ôce wisi k…Ē wiri, k…Ē w…ôran kam, k…Ē awut am, aw…õnc …ôm aŇča arkun, akir…õ am k…Ē kiyi kam doru yati, k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēf…Ētam k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôc…õps…õ kem dar…ôŇč.  
\v 27 M…ôna nw…õ o nw…õ m…ônt…Ēwos…õ k…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…Ē k…ôfi m…Ē, m…ôf…Ētam k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôc…õps…õ kem dar…ôŇč.  
\v 28 Bawo n…ôna akaŇč…õ dac…Ē, m…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčfaŇč k…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē m…Ē, m…ôf…Ēnd…õ k…ôr…õsna m…ôl…Ēm daka d…Ēk…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēb…õrs…õ teta k…ôl…Ē kam m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a daka dad…Ēk…Ē d…õntam k…ôlip k…ôc…ômb…ôr ka k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē-…õ.  
\v 29 Mba k…Ē n…ôncop k…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē ta n…ôlip k…ôc…ômb…ôr ki, nw…õ o nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk ki m…Ē, endesel…ôr nu  
\v 30 p…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻAfum akaŇč…õ Ňčancop k…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē mba Ňčantam f…õ ki k…ôl…ôp…ôs.‚Äļ  
\v 31 It…Ē p…ôyi w…ôb…õ nw…õ …õŇčfaŇč k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôl…Ēma m…Ē, m…õn…õ p…ônd…õ p…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ, afum wul w…ôco (10.000) Ňčantam k…ôsut…õn…õ k…Ē afum wul w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20.000) aka w…ôb…õ w…ôk…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēsut…õn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 32 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ŇčaŇčs…Ēr…õb…Ēl…õn…õ, w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum wul w…ôco (10.000) p…ôsom nda w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum wul w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20.000) w…ôk…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēsut…õn…õ m…Ē, nt…õ p…ômar p…ôk…Ēt ta Ňčasut…õn…õ m…Ē.  
\v 33 Awa, m…ôna nw…õ o nw…õ m…ônt…Ēce ca y…Ēk…Ē m…ôy…Ē m…Ē, m…ôf…Ētam k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôc…õps…õ kem dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ 
\s1 M…õr mm…õ m…õnd…õnc…õ m…Ē 
\r Mat 5.13; Mark 9.50 
\p  
\v 34 ¬ęPaka p…Ēt…Ēt p…Ē m…õr m…Ēy…Ēn…õ, mba k…Ē m…õr m…õnd…õnc…õ-…õ, ak'antam mi k…ôb…Ēts…õ-…õ?  
\v 35 M…õr m…õd…õnc m…Ēf…Ētes…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ant…Ēf, m…Ēf…Ētes…õ nc…õk-c…õk ya y…Ēb…Ēf, m…õn…õ pagbal mi d…ôyika. M…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē l…ôŇč…ôs m…ôcne m…Ē, m…ône ti!¬Ľ 
\c 15  
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca aŇčkesiya nŇč…õ Ňč…õnas…Ēl…õ, k'an…ôŇčk s…Ē Ňči m…Ē 
\r Mat 18.12-14 
\p  
\v 1 AbaŇč…ôs dut k…Ē afum aciya Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yesu k…ôk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē.  
\v 2 AFarisi k…Ē acic…ôs a sariy…õ Ňčacc…Ēp…õn…õ: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ eŇčsel…õn…õ aciya, p…ôwos…õ k…ôdi yeri k…Ē Ňča.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 3 Mba k…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča capaf…Ē nc…õ:  
\v 4 ¬ęN…ôna afum akaŇč…õ dac…Ē, an'…ĒŇčy…Ē Ňčkesiya tasar tin (100), a Ňčin Ňč…Ēs…Ēl…ôr k…Ē, ta …õsak y…Ēk…Ē w…ôco cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (99) d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn Ňčin Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ēs…Ēl…ôr k…Ē m…Ē, haŇč p…ôn…ôŇčk Ňči-…õ?  
\v 5 K…Ē w…ôkayi …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôn…ôŇčk Ňči-…õ, p…ôgbaŇčn…õ Ňči amera Ňčobotu disr…õ,  
\v 6 …Ēnck…Ēnab…õr…õ nde nd…Ēr…Ēn, ewe anapa …Ēn k…Ē and…õ …Ēn nde nd…Ēr…Ēn, p…ôloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻN…ôwol…ôs k…Ē ina, bawo in…ôŇčk aŇčkesiya Ňčem Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnas…Ēl…ôr im m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 7 Icloku nu: P…ôbotu p…ĒŇčk…Ēyi dar…õnc teta fum w…ôkin nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēs…ôkp…ôr amera p…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē dolompu dar…ôŇč m…Ē, p…ôtas teta afum w…ôco cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ (99) aŇč…õ p…ônt…Ēmar k…ôs…ôkp…ôr mera, bawo Ňčalomp m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč mp…õ p…õnas…Ēl…õ, k'an…ôŇčk s…Ē pi m…Ē 
\p  
\v 8 ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, w…ôran w…ôre …ĒŇčy…Ē p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč w…ôco, a gb…ôleŇč bin b…Ēs…Ēl…ôr k…Ē ta omot lamp, ta …õf…õŇč k…ôl…Ē, ta …õnt…õn pi belbel, haŇč p…ôn…ôŇčk pi m…Ē?  
\v 9 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč mp…õ-…õ, eŇčwe anapa …Ēn, k…Ē and…õ …Ēn, p…ôloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻN…ôwol…ôs k…Ē ina bawo in…ôŇčk p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč mp…õ p…õnas…Ēl…ôr im m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 10 Icloku nu, p…ôbotu peyi m…õl…õk…õ a Kanu dac…Ē teta fum w…ôciya w…ôkin gboŇč nw…õ …õŇčs…ôkp…ôr amera p…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč m…Ē. 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca w…ôt…õmp w…ôs…Ēl…õ, k'an…ôŇčk k…Ē s…Ē m…Ē 
\p  
\v 11 K…Ē Yesu oloku s…Ē: ¬ęFum w…ôl…Ēma …õnay…Ē awut arkun m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôk…Ē …õf…õt…õ m…Ē, oloku kas: ‚ÄĻPapa m…ôs…ĒŇč im da p…ômar ides…Ēt…Ē k…õ kam m…Ē.‚Äļ K…Ē kas eyer daka d…Ēn awut …Ēn akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē.  
\v 13 Nt…õ mataka mepic mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē wan w…ôf…õt …õncam…ôs daka d…Ēk…Ē …õnas…Ēt…Ē m…Ē f…ôp. K'osump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…Ēl…õ, at…Ēf Ňčocuru. Nde …õnak…Ē p…ôyi yamayama p…ôcl…ôs…ôr-l…ôs…ôr daka d…Ēk…Ē …õnay…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 14 Nt…õ wan nw…õ elip k…ôdi daka d…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē dor d…Ēp…ĒŇč d…õmb…õr…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē …õnayi m…Ē, k…Ē ca yoncop k…ôbut k…Ē.  
\v 15 K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi nda fum w…ôl…Ēma w…ôka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, w…ôk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôk…õk ka s…Ēp y…Ēn m…Ē.  
\v 16 Wan nw…õ p…ôfaŇč k…ôdi yeri ya s…Ēp, mba ali fum …õnas…ĒŇč f…õ k…Ē yi.  
\v 17 Awa, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ teyi t…Ēn, k'olokun…õ: ‚ÄĻAfum c…ôke Ňčayi k…ôb…ôc ndena papa kem aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ē c…ôcom c…ôlar…ôm m…Ē, a ina icfin…õ nn…Ē dor.  
\v 18 K…ôy…õf…õ k'inder ik…Ē ndena papa kem ik…Ē iloku k…Ē: Papa inciya Kanu, k'inciya s…Ē m…ôna.  
\v 19 Imbut p…ôleli mp…õ p…ômar m…ôsump…ôr'em p…ôm…Ē wan kam m…Ē. Mba m…ôsump…ôr im oŇč p…ôm…Ē w…ôb…ôc kam.‚Äļ  
\v 20 K…Ē wan nw…õ …õl…õk d…Ēp…Ē k'olukus ndena kas.¬Ľ 
\p ¬ę∆Üs…Ēr…Ēb…Ēl…õ, k…Ē kas …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē, k…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr d…Ēp…ĒŇč dosump…ôr k…Ē. K…Ē kas …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēfay…ôn…õ k…Ē, k'…õn…õps…ôrn…õ k…Ē d…ôkilim, k'oncup k…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē wan oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻPapa, inciya Kanu, k'inciy'am, p…ômar f…õ s…Ē m…ôsump…ôr im p…ôm…Ē wan kam.‚Äļ  
\v 22 Mba k…Ē kas k…ôloku acar …Ēn: ‚ÄĻN…ôk…õr…õ duma d…Ēt…Ēt n…ôb…õr k…Ē! N…ôb…õr k…Ē kurund…õ d…ôt…õl…ôr, n…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē c…Ēfta!  
\v 23 N…ôk…õr…õ tana tetifi t…Ēk…Ē, n…ôdif pi. Padi yeri, pawol…ôs!  
\v 24 Bawo wan kem w…ôkaw…õ n…ôŇčn…ôŇčk m…Ē, …õnafi, mba olukus s…Ē k…ôder doru! ∆źnas…Ēl…õ, mba in…ôŇčk k…Ē s…Ē!‚Äļ K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôwol…ôs.  
\v 25 T…õnat…ôŇčn…õ Coco p…ôyi dal…õ. Nt…õ w…ôkak…Ē ender p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčan m…Ē, k'ene t…Ēk…Ē aŇčfer pacpis…õ m…Ē.  
\v 26 K…Ē Coco ewe w…ôcar w…ôkin k'eyif k…Ē tes nt…õ teyi k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčan m…Ē.  
\v 27 K…Ē w…ôcar oloku Coco: ‚ÄĻW…õnc …ôm eder, mba nt…õ olukus k…ôtamn…õ disr…õ m…Ē, it…Ē papa kam endif…õ tana petifi p…Ēk…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 28 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Coco nw…õ, ta …õfaŇč s…Ē k…ôb…õr…õ d…õk…õr-…õ. K…Ē kas owur k…ôk…Ēl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 29 Mba k…Ē wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nw…õ oloku kas: ‚ÄĻMeren m…õlar…ôm m…Ē mam…õ, iy'…ôm dar…ôŇč icb…ôc'am p…ôm…Ē w…ôcar, ali d…Ēs…Ēk din iŇčgb…õk…ôl f…õ mosom mam, mba ali d…Ēs…Ēk din s…Ē m…ôna m…ôs…ĒŇč f'em tir idif s…ôwol…ôs k…Ē anapa em.  
\v 30 Mba nt…õ wan kam w…ôkaw…õ ender m…Ē, nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôl…ôs…ôr-l…ôs…ôr daka dam k…Ē aran ayamayama m…Ē, nk…Ēn taŇč m…ôndif…õ k…Ē tana petifi p…Ēk…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 31 K…Ē kas k…ôloku Coco, ‚ÄĻM…ôna wan kem, s…ôn'eyi d…õ k…Ē m…ôna, daka nd…õ o nd…õ iy…Ē nn…Ē m…Ē, dam d…Ē!  
\v 32 Mba p…ômar yati paboc k…ôsata, pawol…ôs: Bawo w…õnc …ôm w…ôkaw…õ m…ôŇčn…ôŇčk m…Ē, …õnafi, k'olukus s…Ē k…ôyi doru. ∆źnas…Ēl…õ, k'an…ôŇčk k…Ē s…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\c 16  
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca w…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč: ¬ęFum w…ôka daka w…ôl…Ēma …õnay…Ē w…ôc…ômb…ôr…õ-c…ômb…ôr…õ daka, k'ander payems…õn…õ k…Ē, a …õŇčl…ôs…ôr-l…ôs…ôr daka da mariki m…Ēn.  
\v 2 K…Ē mariki m…Ēn mewe k…Ē, p…ôcloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c'ine tetam-…õ? M…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē m…ônc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka dem m…Ē, bawo m…ôf…Ēs…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka dem.‚Äļ  
\v 3 K…Ē w…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka nw…õ olokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c'indey…Ē-…õ, bawo w…ôka daka nw…õ oloku k…ôwur'em k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka d…Ēn? Iy…Ē f…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr k…ôdey…Ēn…õ w…ôbifti ant…Ēf, ilap…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôctola.  
\v 4 Inc…ôr…õ oŇč nt…õ indey…Ē, a afum ŇčabaŇč im w…Ēl…Ē waŇčan disr…õ k…Ē w…ôkaw…õ owur'em k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka d…Ēn-…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 5 K…Ē w…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr daka nw…õ ewe fum w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôk…Ē …õnat…Ēmp…ôr…õ mariki m…Ēn debe m…Ē. K'eyif k…Ē: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c…Ē m…ônt…Ēmp…ôr…õ mariki mem debe-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻMoro ma olif kokos tasar tin (100).‚Äļ ‚ÄĒ‚ÄĻAwa, m…ôl…õk areka, m…ônd…õ m…ôcic: 50.‚Äļ  
\v 7 K'eyif s…Ē w…ôl…Ēma: ‚ÄĻA m…ôna-a, c…ôke c…Ē m…ônt…Ēmp…ôr-…õ?‚Äļ K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oloku: ‚ÄĻMal…Ē busul tasar tin (100).‚Äļ ‚ÄĒ‚ÄĻAwa, m…ônd…õ m…ôl…õk areka, m…ôcic 80.‚Äļ  
\v 8 K…Ē w…ôka daka nw…õ oŇčkor-koru w…ôc…ômb…ôr…õ-c…ômb…ôr…õ k…Ēn daka w…ôt…Ēlomp nw…õ nt…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēt belbel m…Ē. Awa, afum a doru Ňčanc…ôr…õ k…ôy…Ē mes taŇčan p…ôtas ak…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ aka p…ôwaŇčk…ôra m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē Yesu …Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęIcloku nu: N…ôt…õn…õ daka d…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk anapa, it…Ē …ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē dendelip-…õ, pabaŇč nu nde n…ôŇčk…Ēyi doru o doru m…Ē.  
\v 10 M…ôna nw…õ aŇčlaŇč teta tes t…õf…õt m…Ē, antam s…Ē k…ôlaŇč …ôm teta tes t…Ēp…ĒŇč. M…ôna nw…õ m…ônt…Ēlomp teta tes t…õf…õt m…Ē, m…ôf…Ēlomp teta tes t…Ēp…ĒŇč.  
\v 11 K…Ē m…ônt…Ēlomp k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ka daka d…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ deyi doru dand…õ m…Ē, an'endes…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ka daka dosoku-…õ?  
\v 12 K…Ē m…ônt…Ēlomp teta daka da fum-…õ, an'endes…ĒŇč …ôm nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ dam m…Ē-…õ?  
\v 13 Ali w…ôcar w…ôkin …Ēf…Ētam k…ôb…ôc…õ ab…õ m…õr…ôŇč. K…Ē teyi-…õ, enter w…ôkin p…ôb…Ēt…ôr w…ôk…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, p…ôsekt…ôrn…õ w…ôkin, p…ôb…õr w…ôk…Ē kumunt. N…ôf…Ētam k…ôb…ôc…õ Kanu k…Ē p…ôsam t…õm tin.¬Ľ 
\s1 Moloku m…Ēn…ĒŇčks…ôl ma Yesu 
\r Mat 11.12-13; 5.31-32; Mark 10.11-12 
\p  
\v 14 AFarisi, aŇč…õ Ňčanab…Ēt…ôr p…ôsam m…Ē, k…ône ka moloku mam…õ, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôfani Yesu.  
\v 15 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôna, n…ônc…ômb…ôrn…õ afum alompu nn…Ē aw…õnc nu aŇča Ňčayi m…Ē, mba Kanu k…ônc…ôr…õ nu b…ôk…ôc, bawo nt…õ afum Ňčamp…õn…õ darenc m…Ē, it…Ē Kanu nk…Ēn ence.  
\v 16 T…õm ta Sariy…õ sa Musa k…Ē ta sayib…õ t…õnawon haŇč t…õm ta SaŇč. K…ôy…õf…õ oŇč t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, k'ancop k…ôd…ôŇčk Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt ka d…õb…õ da Kanu, nw…õ o nw…õ k…ôsim…ôs…õ k'…õnd…õ k…ôb…õr…õ ka di d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 17 Mba p…ôf…ôf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ēm k…Ē ant…Ēf k…ôs…Ēl…õ, p…ôtas tofo t…õf…õt ta pecic pin\f + \fr 16:17 \ft  It…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ c…ôsoma ¬ęsigir…õ¬Ľ\f* pa sariy…õ k…ôt…õmp…õn…õ.  
\v 18 Nw…õ ence w…ôran k…Ēn p…ôk…Ē p…ôn…õnc…õ w…ôl…Ēma m…Ē, d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da w…ôsump…ôr dalak…Ē d'eyi. Nw…õ o nw…õ …õn…õnc…õ w…ôran nw…õ wos ence m…Ē, d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da w…ôsump…ôr dalak…Ē d'eyi.¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca w…ôka daka k…Ē Lasar 
\p  
\v 19 ¬ęW…ôka daka w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi, p…ôcb…õrn…õ yamos y…Ēt…Ēt, yeyeŇčki k…ôway. D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk p…ôyi p…ôt…Ēt disr…õ, p…ôcdi yeri y…Ēt…Ēt.  
\v 20 K…ôl…Ē k…Ēn kiriŇč, fum w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka o daka w…ôl…Ēma, nw…õ ancwe Lasar m…Ē, p…ôy…Ē runc, p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ kusuŇčka k…Ēn.  
\v 21 Lasar nw…õ p…ôfaŇč k…ôcburuk yeri ny…õ y…õnt…õmp…õn…õ-t…õmp…õn…õ am…õsa d…ônt…Ēf Ňča w…ôka daka nw…õ m…Ē, p…ôdi. Mba k…Ē cen yender y…õcn…õnt…ôs runc y…Ēn.  
\v 22 K…Ē Lasar efi, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mender m…õl…õk k…Ē, k…Ē meŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē k…ôk…ĒŇčes…ôm nde Abraham k…ôs…ôk. K…Ē w…ôka daka nw…õ ender p…ôfi, k'awup k…Ē.  
\v 23 Nde k…ôfo nk…õ afi ŇčaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôka daka eyekti f…Ēr, k'…õn…ôŇčk p…ôb…Ēl…õ Abraham k…Ē Lasar p…ôcŇčes…ôm k…Ē k…ôs…ôk.  
\v 24 K…Ē w…ôka daka nw…õ oŇčkul…ôrn…õ: ‚ÄĻPapa Abraham, m…ôy…Ēn'em n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr! M…ôsom Lasar p…ôgb…ôt t…õl…ôr t…Ēn d…ôromun p…ôder p…ôcaŇčk…ôs im temer, bawo k…ôt…Ēr…Ē k'ind…õ nn…Ē n…õnc dand…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 25 K…Ē Abraham oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻWan kem, m…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ a m…ônas…Ēt…Ē daka dam nt…õ m…ônayi doru m…Ē, k…Ē Lasar nk…Ēn …Ēs…Ēt…Ē p…ôcuy kiyi k…Ēn doru. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, k…ôŇčes…ôm k'eyi, m…ôna m…ôyi s…Ē d…ômn…õ p…ôcuy.  
\v 26 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, dobo d…Ēp…ĒŇč deyi su dac…Ē k…Ē n…ôna nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nw…õ …õŇčfaŇč k…ôcep…ôr p…ôder nn…Ē s…ôyi m…Ē, ta …õntam-…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 27 K…Ē w…ôka daka nw…õ oloku: ‚ÄĻIl…õts…õn'am, Papa, m…ôsom Lasar nde k…ôl…Ē ka papa kem.  
\v 28 Bawo, iy…Ē di aw…õnc aŇča k…ôcam…ôt, Lasar p…ôk…Ē p…ôloku Ňča nt…õ teyi nn…Ē m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňča s…Ē Ňčadeder nn…Ē p…ôcuy pamp…õ peyi m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 29 K…Ē Abraham oloku: ‚ÄĻAla, aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčay…Ē Musa k…Ē ad…ôŇčk a Kanu. Ňčac…ôŇčk…ôl Ňča.‚Äļ  
\v 30 K…Ē w…ôka daka nw…õ oloku Abraham: ‚ÄĻAla, Papa, k…Ē fum …õy…õf…õ nn…Ē afi Ňčayi m…Ē p…ôk…Ē p…ôlok-lok…ôr Ňča-…õ, ŇčaŇčs…ôkp…ôr mera Ňčac…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč.‚Äļ  
\v 31 K…Ē Abraham oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻK…Ē Ňčant…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl Musa k…Ē ad…ôŇčk a Kanu-…õ, ali fum …õy…õf…õ nn…Ē afi dac…Ē, Ňčaf…Ēk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl w…ôkayi.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\c 17  
\s1 Kiciya k…Ē k…ôŇčaŇčn…õ ***** 
\r Mat 18.6-7; Mark 9.42 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč: ¬ęP…ôf…Ētam k…ôyi ta mes meyi mm…õ m…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ fum k…ôloŇč…õ m…Ē. Mba p…ôl…õc peyi nw…õ …ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ mi k…ôyi m…Ē.  
\v 2 P…ôf…ôf…ôr…õn…õ k…ôkot w…ôkayi tasar t…Ēp…ĒŇč d…ôkilim pagbal k…Ē d…ôk…ôba, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôkayi p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôf…ôf…ôr w…ôkin k…ôloŇč…õ-…õ\f + \fr 17:2 \fqa P…ôs…ĒŇč…õ fum w…ôf…ôf…ôr w…ôkin k…ôloŇč…õ\ft  = p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ fum w…ôf…ôf…ôr k…ôciya\f*.  
\v 3 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ belbel! 
\p K…Ē w…õnc'…ôm enciya-…õ, m…ôgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr k…Ē. \k K'…õs…ôkp…ôr amera p…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč-…õ\k*, m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 4 K…Ē w…õnc'…ôm enciy'am cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč d…Ēs…Ēk din disr…õ-…õ, a p…ôluks…ôrn…õ k…ôder'…ôm cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč p…ôclok'…ôm: ‚ÄĻK…ôs…ôkp…ôr k'inder amera few, inc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč-…õ,‚Äļ m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 5 K…Ē asom a Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčaloku W…ôb…õ: ¬ęM…ôb…õr…õn…õ su k…ôlaŇč!¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Mariki oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē n…ônt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôlaŇč nk…õ k…ôyi p…ôm…Ē t…õŇčgb…õn t…õf…õt m…Ē, n…ôntam k…ôloku k…ôt…Ēk nk…õ: M…ôgbukt…õ nn…Ē m…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ôm…õ nde d…ôk…ôba, k…ôt…Ēk kaŇčk…Ē k…ôy…Ē t…õfaŇč tonu.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 7 ¬ęN…ôna akaŇč…õ dac…Ē, an…Ē …Ēy…Ē w…ôcar nw…õ embifti, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôkayi p…ôck…õk, a p…ôck…Ēnay…õf…õ dal…õ, p…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôder kat…ôna m…ôder m…ônd…õ d…õm…õsa!‚Äļ  
\v 8 Nt…õ oŇčloku k…Ē m…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôlomp…ôs'em yeri yem, m…ôb…õrn…õ duma m…ôs…ĒŇč im yeri, haŇč ilip k…ôdi yeri imun. K'ilip-…õ, m…ôna m…ôdi yeri m…ômun.‚Äļ  
\v 9 W…ôka w…ôcar kak…Ē eŇčyek-yek…ôs k…Ē bawo …Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē mes m…Ēk…Ē …õfaŇč m…Ē ba? Ala!  
\v 10 Tin tayi t…Ē k…Ē n…ôna, k…Ē n…ôlip k'…Ēy…Ē mes m…Ēk…Ē afaŇč…ôr nu m…Ē f…ôp-…õ, n…ôloku: ‚ÄĻAcar gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ. Nt…õ p…ômar su k…ôy…Ē m…Ē, t…Ē s…ôy…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôtam…ôs k…Ēn acun…õ sen w…ôco 
\p  
\v 11 Yesu eyi k…ôk…Ē Yerusal…õm, k…Ē Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…ôcali at…Ēf Ňča Samari k…Ē Ňča Kalile dac…Ē.  
\v 12 Eyi k…ôb…õr…õ tadare t…Ēl…Ēma, k…Ē afum w…ôco acun…õ sen al…Ēma Ňčander Ňčafayn…õ k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õ.  
\v 13 K…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ sim Ňčacloku: ¬ęYesu, Mariki, m…ôy…Ēn…õ su n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr!¬Ľ  
\v 14 Nt…õ Yesu …õn…ôŇčk Ňča m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôment…ôrn…õ aloŇčn…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu.¬Ľ Afum aŇč…õ Ňčayi k…ôk…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a Ňčas…Ēk a k…Ē Ňčandeb…õr…õ di.  
\v 15 Nt…õ w…ôkin …õn…ôŇčkn…õ p…ôtamn…õ m…Ē, k'oluks…ôrn…õ p…ôccam debeki da Kanu dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč.  
\v 16 K'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ d…ônt…Ēf, k'osump…ôr Yesu w…õc…ôk, k'eyek-yek…ôs k…Ē.\f + \fr 17:16 \fq K'eyek-yek…ôs k…Ē\ft  = ¬ęk'eyif Yesu barka teta k…ôtam…ôs k…Ēn.¬Ľ\f* Fum w…ôkak…Ē, w…ôSamari …õnayi.  
\v 17 K…Ē Yesu eyif k…Ē: ¬ęBaf…Ē as…Ēk…ôs afum aŇč…õ w…ôco? Deke alp…ôs aŇč…õ cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ Ňčayi-…õ?  
\v 18 Ali w…ôkin …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ f…õ k…ôluks…ôrn…õ \k p…ôdecam debeki da Kanu\k*, m…õn…õ w…ôcik…ôra w…ôkin w…ôkaw…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ m…ôk…Ē, k…ôlaŇč kam k…ôyac …ôm.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôder ka d…õb…õ da Kanu 
\r Mat 24.23-28,37-41 
\p  
\v 20 Nt…õ aFarisi Ňčayif Yesu t…õm nt…õ d…õb…õ da Kanu dendeder m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ę\k D…õb…õ da Kanu\k* d…Ēf…Ēder pagb…ôtn…õ di f…ôp.  
\v 21 Af…Ēkul…õ di, ‚ÄĻId'…õnd…õ nn…Ē!‚Äļ, ‚ÄĻId…Ēk…Ē nde!‚Äļ Bawo d…õb…õ da Kanu n…ôna Ňč…Ē deyi dac…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 22 Nt…õ Yesu elip k…ôloku Ňča ti m…Ē, k'oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč: ¬ęD…Ēs…Ēk dendeb…ôp nd…õ n…ôndefaŇč k…ôn…ôŇčk d…Ēs…Ēk din da Wan ka W…ôrkun m…Ē, mba n…ôf…Ēs…Ēn…ôŇčk di.  
\v 23 Andeloku nu: ‚ÄĻEyi nn…Ē!‚Äļ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ ‚ÄĻEyi nde!‚Äļ Ta n…ôdek…Ē di, ta n…ôdey…õks…ôrn…õ k…ôk…Ē di.  
\v 24 Ti disr…õ, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Wan ka W…ôrkun endeder m…Ē p…ôndeyi p…ôm…Ē nt…õ p…ômot p…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pa darenc k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôs…ôk kin haŇč ka m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.  
\v 25 Mba m…õn…õ p…ôt…Ēr…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôr…õsna, afum a t…õm tant…õ Ňčaw…õn…ôs k…Ē.  
\v 26 T…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr t…õm ta Nuha m…Ē, tendecep…ôr s…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da Wan ka W…ôrkun.  
\v 27 Afum Ňčancdi yeri, Ňčacmun, arkun k…Ē aran Ňčacn…õnc…õn…õ haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Nuha …õnab…õr…õ debil m…Ē: K…Ē kutup k…ônder nk…õ k…ônam…ôl…ôk afum f…ôp m…Ē.\x - \xo 17:27 \xt D…ôk…ôcop 6.9-7.24\x* 
\v 28 P…ôndeyi p…ôm…Ē t…õm ta L…Ēt. Afum Ňčancdi yeri, Ňčacmun, Ňčacway, Ňčaccam…ôs, Ňčacb…Ēf, Ňčacc…ômb…ôr w…Ēl…Ē.  
\v 29 Mba d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ L…Ēt owur Sodom m…Ē, n…õnc k…Ē p…ôrb…ôl…Ē y…õnatuf Sodom k…Ē y…õm…ôl…ôk ca ya di f…ôp.\x - \xo 17:29 \xt D…ôk…ôcop 19.24\x* 
\v 30 It…Ē p…ôndeyi d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ andement…ôr Wan ka W…ôrkun m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 31 ¬ęD…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē nw…õ eŇčyi dabaŇčka m…Ē, ta p…ôb…õr…õ d…ôk…ôl…Ē p…ôl…õk ca y…Ēn. Fum nw…õ t…õmb…ôp dal…õ m…Ē, ta p…ôlukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn.  
\v 32 N…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ w…ôran ka L…Ēt.\f + \fr 17:32 \ft M…ôm…Ēm…ôn D…ôk…ôcop 19.26\f* 
\v 33 M…ôna nw…õ m…ôndes…õp k…ôm…õŇčk k…ôyi doru kam m…Ē k…ôndesalp…ôr …ôm, k…Ē m…ôna nw…õ k…ôŇčsalp…ôr m…Ē, m…ôndes…Ēm…õŇčk ki.  
\v 34 Icloku nu: Pibi pap…Ēk…Ē, afum m…õr…ôŇč Ňčandef…ônt…ôr…õ k…ôf…ônc kin, pal…õk w…ôkin, pasak w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 35-36 Aran m…õr…ôŇč Ňčandeyi k…ôc…Ē kirir kin, pal…õk w…ôkin pasak w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč.\f + \fr 17:35-36 \ft AndeŇč…ôr yeycic…ôs y…Ēl…Ēma ¬ęArkun m…õr…ôŇč Ňčandeyi dal…õ din dayi, pasump…ôr w…ôkin pasak w…ôk…Ē.¬Ľ\f* 
\v 37 K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęDeke tat…Ēk…Ē tendek…Ēyi-…õ, Mariki?¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloks…õ Ňča: ¬ęNde pefi peyi m…Ē, dif…Ē y…Ēf…ôn yendeb…ôps…õn…õ.¬Ľ 
\c 18  
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca w…ôran nw…õ wos efi m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôboc kiti 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča capaf…Ē, k…ôment…ôr Ňča a m…õn…õ \k Ňčaclok-lok…ôr Kanu\k* t…õm o t…õm ta dis d…Ēl…Ēl Ňča.  
\v 2 K'oloku: ¬ęDare d…Ēl…Ēma d…õnayi d…Ēy…Ē w…ôboc kiti nw…õ …õnat…Ē k…ôcnes…õ Kanu m…Ē, ali fum ta elel…ôs-…õ.  
\v 3 Dare dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēy…Ē s…Ē w…ôran w…ôt…Ēl…Ē w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ encder p…ôcloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôboc'em kiti k…Ē w…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ kem dac…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 4 K…Ē w…ôboc kiti nw…õ …õfat…ôr k…Ē haŇč, k'ende p…ôlokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ‚ÄĻAli nt…õ int…Ēc…ôr…õ Kanu, ta ilel…ôs nw…õ o nw…õ m…Ē,  
\v 5 nt…õ w…ôran nw…õ wos efi, …Ēl…Ēl…ôs im dis m…Ē, iboc…õ k…Ē kiti k…Ē w…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ēn dac…Ē, nt…õ tendes…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôt…Ēgb…Ēk…ôr…õ-gb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôder m…Ē, p…ôdenaŇčkan…õ k…ôl…Ēl…ôs im dis.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Mariki …Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl nt…õ w…ôboc kiti w…ôt…Ēlomp oŇčloku m…Ē.  
\v 7 Kanu nk…Ēn …Ēf…Ēdek…Ēboc…õ afum …Ēn aŇč…õ kiti ba, aŇč…õ Ňčambok…ôr k…Ē pibi k…Ē daŇč m…Ē? Endes…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôwon k…ôkar ba?  
\v 8 Icloku nu: ∆Üf…Ēdes…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôwon k…ôkar, endeboc…õ Ňča kiti kat…ôna kat…ôna. Mba k…Ē Wan ka W…ôrkun endeder-…õ, endeb…ôp k…ôlaŇč doru ba?¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca w…ôFarisi k…Ē w…ôwer…ôs dut 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē Yesu oloku s…Ē capaf…Ē nc…õ afum al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôlomp, a Ňčacfani ak…Ē m…Ē:  
\v 10 ¬ęK…Ē afum m…õr…ôŇč Ňčamp…õ k…ôk…Ētola Kanu nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k*, w…ôkin nw…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôFarisi, w…ôk…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôwer…ôs dut.  
\v 11 W…ôFarisi nw…õ p…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôclok-lok…ôr Kanu d…õb…ôk…ôc nt…õ: ‚ÄĻKanu, iyif …ôm barka\f + \fr 18:11 \fq Iyif'…ôm barka\ft  = Iyek-yek…ôs'…ôm\f* nt…õ int…Ēyi p…ôm…Ē afum alp…ôs ak…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ abaŇč…ôs ca ya afum m…Ē, ta Ňčalomp, Ňčacsump…ôr dalak…Ē, nt…õ int…Ēyi p…ôm…Ē w…ôwer…ôs dut nw…õ m…Ē.  
\v 12 K…ôm…õr…ôŇč k'iŇčsuŇč d…Ēs…Ēk doluks…ôr disr…õ, ics…ĒŇč s…Ē faril…õ f…ôp fa y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē yem.‚Äļ  
\v 13 W…ôwer…ôs dut nw…õ nk…Ēn p…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õ, p…ôcnes…õ k…ôyekti f…Ēr darenc yati, mba p…ôcsut-sutn…õ ab…ôk…ôc k…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻKanu m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn'em, ina w…ôciya!‚Äļ  
\v 14 Icloku nu: Fum w…ôkak…Ē …õnalomp nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē, a k'endelukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn. Mba w…ôFarisi …õnalomp f…õ nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčyokn…õ m…Ē, andetor…õ k…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ otor…õ banca m…Ē, andep…õn…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôtolan…õ k…Ēn awut af…õt 
\r Mat 19.13-15; Mark 10.13-16 
\p  
\v 15 Afum Ňčanck…õr…õ Yesu ali c…ônaka nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôcdeŇč…ôr Ňča waca teta k…ôtolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt. Nt…õ ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčan…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňča. 
\p  
\v 16 Mba k…Ē Yesu …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ awut p…ôcloku: ¬ęN…ôsak awut Ňčader nn…Ē iyi m…Ē! Ta n…ôyams…ôr Ňča k…ôder, bawo afum aŇč…õ Ňčayi p…ôm…Ē awut af…õt akaŇč…õ m…Ē, Ňča Ňčay…Ē d…õb…õ da Kanu.  
\v 17 Awa! Kance icloku nu: Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēfayn…õ d…õb…õ da Kanu p…ôm…Ē wanf…õt m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēdek…Ēb…õr…õ di disr…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 W…ôrkun w…ôka daka d…õlar…ôm 
\r Mat 19.16-30; Mark 10.17-31 
\p  
\v 18 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôl…Ēma eyif k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ w…ôt…Ēt, c…ôke c…Ē p…ômar im k…ôy…Ē, is…Ēt…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē Yesu eyif k…Ē: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôwen'em ‚ÄĻW…ôt…Ēt‚Äļ-…õ? Ali fum …Ēy…Ēn…õ f…õ w…ôt…Ēt, m…õn…õ Kanu sona gboŇč.  
\v 20 M…ônc…ôr…õ mosom ma Kanu: Ta m…ôsump…ôr dalak…Ē, ta m…ôdif fum, ta m…ôkiy…õ, ta m…ôbaŇč…õ fum sede sa yem, m…ôlel…ôs wisi k…Ē wiri.¬Ľ  
\v 21 ¬ęIlel…ôs mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ is…Ēr…Ēf…õt…õ,¬Ľ fum w…ôkak…Ē p…ôcloku.  
\v 22 Nt…õ Yesu ene k…Ē dim m…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAwa tes tin gboŇč tobut …ôm: M…ôcam…ôs daka nd…õ m…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, m…ôyer p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē at…Ēy…Ē daka, m…ôndek…Ēs…Ēt…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm nde d…ôK…Ēm. K…Ē m…ôlip-…õ, m…ôder m…ôc…õps'em dar…ôŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 23 Nt…õ fum nw…õ ene moloku ma Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē ab…Ēc Ňč…õmb…õr…õ k…Ē, bawo …õnay…Ē daka p…ôcep…ôr…ôr.  
\v 24 Nt…õ Yesu …õn…ôŇčk ab…Ēc Ňč…õmb…õr…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęP…ôncuca aka daka k…ôb…õr…õ ka akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf.  
\v 25 P…ôf…ôf…ôr…õn…õ y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…ôb…õr…õ ka abi Ňča t…õs…õmb…õ p…ôtas w…ôka daka k…ôb…õr…õ ka akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ  
\v 26 AŇč…õ Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl Yesu m…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęAwa, an'…õntam oŇč k…ôfis-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęNt…õ t…õntamb…ôr afum m…Ē, Kanu k…ôntam ti.¬Ľ  
\v 28 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku: ¬ęS…ôna s…ôsak yos…Ēt…Ē yosu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ônc…ôm'am dar…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 29 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęAwa! Kance icloku nu: Fum eyi f…õ, nw…õ …õŇčsak k…ôl…Ē, w…ôran, aw…õnc, akom…õn…õ, k…Ē awut teta d…õb…õ da Kanu,  
\v 30 ta w…ôkayi …ĒŇčk…Ēs…Ēt…Ē p…ôla p…ôcep…ôr…ôr doru dand…õ, p…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru t…õm tekiriŇč.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu …õnd…ôŇčk tamaas defi d…Ēn k…Ē k…ôdey…õf…õ k…Ēn afi dac…Ē 
\r Mat 20.17-19; Mark 10.32-34 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk Asom …Ēn w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im, Yerusal…õm ayi k…ôp…õ. Mes mm…õ sayib…õ a Kanu Ňčanacic…ôs teta Wan ka W…ôrkun m…Ē f…ôp, mendek…Ēlar…õ.  
\v 32 Bawo andek…Ēl…õk k…Ē pab…õr at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif d…ôwaca. Andek…Ēfani k…Ē, andek…Ēt…Ēr…ôs k…Ē, andek…Ēyuks…ôr k…Ē lin,  
\v 33 andek…Ēsut…õ k…Ē t…Ēr…ĒŇčk…Ēn, a padedif k…Ē. Tataka ta maas ta defi d…Ēn p…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 34 Mba Asom …Ēn Ňčanane f…õ ti t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm. Ňäanac…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē toloku m…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôtam…ôs k…Ēn w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk 
\r Mat 20.29-34; Mark 10.46-52 
\p  
\v 35 Nt…õ Ňčayi k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yeriko m…Ē, t…õt…ôŇčn…õ w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk w…ôl…Ēma p…ônd…õ d…Ēp…Ē k…ôs…ôk p…ôctola.  
\v 36 K'ene p…Ēk…Ēt pa k…ônay, k'eyif daka nd…õ dender m…Ē.  
\v 37 K'aloku k…Ē: ¬ęYesu w…ôka Nasar…õt eyi k…ôcep…ôr!¬Ľ  
\v 38 K'oŇčkul…ôrn…õ: ¬ęYesu wan ka \f + \fr 18:38 \fq Wan ka Dawuda\ft  = Ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ tokul…õ ta aYisrayel = ¬ęw…ôyac k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ \f* Dawuda, m…ôy…Ēn'em n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr!¬Ľ  
\v 39 AŇč…õ Ňčanasol k…Ē Yesu Ňčayi k…Ē tekiriŇč m…Ē, Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr k…Ē a p…ôcaŇčk, mba p…ôcnaŇčkan…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęWan ka Dawuda, m…ôy…Ēn'em n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr!¬Ľ  
\v 40 K…Ē Yesu …õnc…ôm…õ, k'osom a pak…õr…õ k…Ē fum nw…õ. Nt…õ al…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k'eyif k…Ē:  
\v 41 ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôfaŇč a iy…Ēn'am-…õ?¬Ľ K'oloku: ¬ęMariki, iluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk!¬Ľ  
\v 42 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk! K…ôlaŇč kam k…ôntam…ôs …ôm.¬Ľ  
\v 43 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē fum nw…õ oluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk, k'…õy…õf…õ k'…õnc…ôm…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč \k p…ôccam debeki\k* da Kanu. Nt…õ afum f…ôp Ňčan…ôŇčk tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôkor-koru Kanu. 
\c 19  
\s1 Yesu k…Ē Sasey 
\p  
\v 1 Nt…õ Yesu …õmb…õr…õ Yerik…Ē m…Ē, k'…õncali dare.  
\v 2 Awa, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma, nw…õ ancwe Sasey, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka awer…ôs dut, p…ôy…Ē daka d…õlar…ôm,  
\v 3 p…ôct…õn k…ôc…ôr…õ fum nw…õ aŇčwe Yesu m…Ē, mba …õnctam f…õ ti, bawo afum Ňčanala, nk…Ēn p…ôbumps…õn…õ.  
\v 4 K…Ē fum nw…õ encep…ôr kiriŇč k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôf…ôr…ôŇčk d…ôk…ôt…Ēk nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk Yesu m…Ē, bawo dif'…õnak…Ē k…ôcep…ôr.  
\v 5 Nt…õ Yesu …õmb…ôp k…ôt…Ēt kaŇčk…Ē d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, k'eyekti f…Ēr k'…õn…ôŇčk fum nw…õ, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęSasey m…ôkuf…õ m…ôtor, bawo nde k…ôl…Ē kam iŇčk…Ē m…Ēk…Ē iyi.¬Ľ  
\v 6 K…Ē Sasey …õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôtor, k'…õmbaŇč Yesu p…ôbotu disr…õ.  
\v 7 Nt…õ afum Ňčan…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ, Ňčacloku: ¬ęNdena fum w…ôciya …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi.¬Ľ  
\v 8 Mba Sasey nw…õ …õnac…ôm…õ mariki f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, oloku: ¬ęMariki, indes…ĒŇč at…Ēy…Ē daka dac…Ē da k…ôs…Ēt…Ē kem. Nw…õ o nw…õ inanaŇčkan…õ k…ôbaŇč…ôr p…õlar…ôm m…Ē, indes…ĒŇč w…ôkayi k…ômaŇčk…ôl…õ ka t…Ēk…Ē inabaŇč…ôr k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…Ēk…Ē, Kanu k…ôyac aka k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…õ, bawo m…ôna s…Ē w…ôka Abraham m…ôy…Ēn…õ!  
\v 10 Bawo Wan ka W…ôrkun ender k…ôdet…õn k…Ē k…ôyac ka aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēl…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Capaf…Ē ca m…õnc…ômb…ôl ma k…õma 
\r Mat 25.14-30 
\p  
\v 11 Afum Ňčayi k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Yesu. K…Ē Yesu …Ēn…Ēc…ôr capaf…Ē c…ôl…Ēma, bawo Ňčanal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yerusal…õm, afum Ňčacc…õm-c…õmn…õ a d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ĒŇčk…Ēwur gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęFum w…ôt…Ēt tokom w…Ēl…Ēma, …õnay…õf…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē at…Ēf Ňčobol-bolu k…ôk…Ēt…õn d…õb…õ a p…ôdeder.  
\v 13 K…Ē fum nw…õ ewe acar …Ēn w…ôco, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča nw…õ o nw…õ t…õnc…ômb…ôl pa k…õma k…ôp…ĒŇč kin, k'oloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻN…ôckaf…ôl…õ-kaf…ôl…õ pi waca haŇč icder.‚Äļ  
\v 14 Mba afum aka dare dad…Ēk…Ē Ňčanater k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasom k…ôk…Ēloku nde fum nw…õ …Ēnck…Ē k…ôt…õn d…õb…õ m…Ē: ‚ÄĻS…ôfaŇč f…õ a fum w…ôkaw…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ su w…ôb…õ!‚Äļ  
\v 15 K…Ē fum nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôs…Ēt…Ē d…õb…õ, nt…õ olukus m…Ē, k'ewe acar …Ēn aŇč…õ w…ôco k…ôdec…ôr…õ nt…õ nw…õ o nw…õ …õŇčkaf…ôli-kaf…ôli waca m…Ē.  
\v 16 K…Ē w…ôcar w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ender, k'oloku: ‚ÄĻMariki, is…Ēt…Ē w…ôco wa k…õma k…ôŇčk…Ē m…ônas…ĒŇč im m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 17 K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku: ‚ÄĻTentes…õ, w…ôcar w…ôt…Ēt m…ôy…Ēn…õ, bawo m…ôlomp teta tes t…õf…õt. Ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ a is…ĒŇč am k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka s…ôdare w…ôco.‚Äļ  
\v 18 K…Ē w…ôcar w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč ender, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻMariki, k…ôcam…ôt ka k…ôŇčk…Ē m…ônas…ĒŇč im m…Ē, k'is…Ēt…Ē k…ôdeŇč…ôr ka ki.‚Äļ  
\v 19 K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku s…Ē w…ôkak…Ē: ‚ÄĻIs…ĒŇč …ôm s…ôdare k…ôcam…ôt, m…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan.‚Äļ  
\v 20 K…Ē w…ôl…Ēma ender p…ôloku: ‚ÄĻMariki k…õma kam k…ôŇčk…õ, inaf…Ēkt…ôr ki d…ôk…ôloto k…ôt…Ēt im…õŇčk.  
\v 21 Inanes'am, bawo fum w…ôcuca m…ôy…Ēn…õ: M…ôŇčl…õk mp…õ m…ônt…Ēboc m…Ē, m…ôpim nde m…ônat…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 22 K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn: ‚ÄĻMoloku mam m'indekit'…ôm, m…ôna w…ôcar w…ôl…õc! M…ônac…ôr…õ a incuca, k'iŇčl…õk mp…õ int…Ēboc m…Ē, icpim mp…õ int…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 23 Ak'…õnas…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…ônat…Ēs…ĒŇč p…ôsam pem am…õŇčk p…ôsam m…Ē-…õ? K…Ē nt…õ ilukus m…Ē, k'imbaŇč p…ôsam pem is…Ēt…Ē s…Ē pi k…ôroŇč k…ôntaŇčgb…õ.‚Äļ  
\v 24 K'oloku afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē: ‚ÄĻN…ôbaŇč…ôr k…Ē k…õma kaŇčk…Ē, n…ôs…ĒŇč ki w…ôk…Ē …Ēs…Ēt…Ēn'em kilo w…ôco m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 25 K…Ē afum Ňčaloku: ‚ÄĻW…ôb…õ, w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēt…Ē w…ôco!‚Äļ  
\v 26 K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻIcloku nu: M…ôna nw…õ m…ôy…Ē m…Ē, amb…õr…õn…õ s…Ē m…ôna w…ôkayi. Mba m…ôna nw…õ m…ônt…Ēy…Ē m…Ē, ambaŇč…ôr …ôm ali p…Ēk…Ē m…ôy…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 27 Tam…õr…ôŇč tayi, n…ôk…õr'em ater'em aŇč…õ Ňčanat…ĒfaŇč a iy…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôb…õ m…Ē, n…ôfay Ňča mera f…Ēr yem kiriŇč.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôk…Ē k…Ēn Yerusal…õm 
\r Mat 21.1-11; Mark 11.1-11; IsaŇč 12.12-19 
\p  
\v 28 Nt…õ Yesu elip k…ôloku afum moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'osump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē afum kiriŇč k…ôk…Ē Yerusal…õm.  
\v 29 Nt…õ Yesu …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ s…ôdare sa B…õtfase k…Ē Betani m…Ē, k…ôca ka t…Ēr…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčwe t…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu osom ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč,  
\v 30 p…ôcloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē nde dare nd…õ ant…õf…ôrn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēb…õr…õ-…õ, n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp di s…Ēfale s…ôf…õt pakot si, ns…õ fum o fum …õntat…Ēnd…õ m…Ē. N…ôsik…ôli si, n…ôk…õr'em.  
\v 31 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum p…ôyif nu: ‚ÄĻTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčsik…ôl…õ si-…õ?‚Äļ N…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻBawo Mariki …õfaŇč si.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 32 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ anasom m…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp s…Ēfale s…ôf…õt pakot si p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē.  
\v 33 Ňäayi k…ôsik…ôli s…Ēfale s…ôf…õt, k…Ē as…ôrka Ňčayif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčsik…ôl…õ s…Ēfale sas…Ēk…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 34 K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčaloku aka s…Ēfale: ¬ęMariki …õfaŇč si.¬Ľ  
\v 35 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčken…õ Yesu s…Ēfale s…ôf…õt ns…õ, k…Ē ŇčandeŇčs…ôr si suma s…ôŇčan sak…ôroŇč, k…Ē Yesu …õnd…õ si k…ôroŇč.  
\v 36 T…Ēk…Ē …Ēnck…Ē kiriŇč m…Ē, it…Ē afum Ňčancper-per…õ k…Ē suma s…ôŇčan sak…ôroŇč d…Ēp…Ē.  
\v 37 Nt…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yerusal…õm nde p…ôt…ômb…ôl…ôr pa t…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif m…Ē, k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt k…ônay k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ônac…õps…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč m…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôkor-koru Kanu p…ôp…ĒŇč, bawo Ňčanan…ôŇčk \k mes m…õw…õy-w…õy mm…õ Kanu k…ômment…ôr m…Ē\k*.  
\v 38 K…Ē Ňčaloku: 
\q1 ¬ęKanu k…ôpoc…õ p…ôt…Ēt w…ôb…õ nw…õ ender…õn…õ tewe ta Mariki m…Ē! 
\q1 P…ôforu peyi d…ôK…Ēm, 
\q1 k…Ē p…ôlel peyi Kanu mofo meŇčeci ma d…ôK…Ēm!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 39 AFarisi akin akin ak…Ē Ňčanayi k…ônay kaŇčk…Ē dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňčaloku Yesu: ¬ęMariki, m…ôloku ac…õps…õ am dar…ôŇč ŇčacaŇčk!¬Ľ  
\v 40 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē ŇčancaŇčk-…õ, masar moŇčkul…õ-kul…õ!¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôbok k…Ēn teta Yerusal…õm 
\p  
\v 41 Nt…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yerusal…õm, a k…Ē Yesu …õn…ôŇčk dare m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôbok teta di,  
\v 42 k'oloku: ¬ęYerusal…õm, m…ôn'…õnc…ôr…õ m…Ēk…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčy…Ē pas…Ēt…Ē p…ôforu m…Ē! Mba nd…õk…ôl tat…Ēk…Ē t…ĒŇčgb…Ēp…ôn'am, m…ôf…Ētam ti k…ôn…ôŇčk.  
\v 43 Bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dendeder nd…õ ater am Ňčanden…ĒŇčk…ôr …ôm kand…õ, Ňčak…õl …ôm, a Ňčadegb…ôc…ôr…õn'am waca f…ôp m…Ē.  
\v 44 Ňäandel…ôs…ôr …ôm haŇč awut am, ali tasar tin Ňčaf…Ēdesak…ôr'am mp…õ pendedeŇčs…õ p…Ēl…Ēm k…ôroŇč m…Ē, bawo m…ônac…ôr…õ f…õ t…õm nt…õ Kanu k…ônader k…ômar …ôm m…Ē!¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôb…õr…õ k…Ēn nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* 
\r Mat 21.12-17; Mark 11.15-19; IsaŇč 2.13-22 
\p  
\v 45 Nt…õ Yesu …õmb…õr…õ nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôb…õl…ôs acam…ôs.  
\v 46 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęD…ôyecic…ôs, Kanu k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻK…ôl…Ē kem, d…ôk…ôtola Kanu d…Ē k…ôndey…Ēn…õ,‚Äļ mba n…ôna n…ôŇčkaf…ôli ki t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta calbante.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 47 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk Yesu …õnct…ôks…õ afum d…ôndo \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* disr…õ. AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif, k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf Ňčact…õn k…ôdif k…Ē.  
\v 48 Mba ta Ňčanc…ôr…õ nt…õ ŇčaŇčy…Ē, bawo afum f…ôp Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku ma Yesu, ta ŇčafaŇč k…ôbut ali toloku t…Ēn tin k…ône-…õ. 
\c 20  
\s1 Deke k…ôtam mes ka Yesu k…ôy…õf…õ-…õ? 
\r Mat 21.23-27; Mark 11.27-33 
\p  
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, nt…õ Yesu eyi k…ôt…ôks…õ afum nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* m…Ē, p…ôcloku moloku m…Ēt…Ēt. AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, k…Ē at…ôks…õ a sariy…õ s'aSuyif k…ôl…õk…õn…õ abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf Ňčamb…õr…ôr k…Ē,  
\v 2 k…Ē Ňčaloku Yesu: ¬ęM…ôloku su ma: K…ôtam k…ôre k…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ mes mam…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, m…ôbonc…ôr su nw…õ …Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôtam kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęIna s…Ē, k'iyif nu k'inder toloku tin. N…ôluks'em ti:  
\v 4 K…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun ka SaŇč d…ôk…Ēm k…ôncy…õf…õ ba, ka nda afum?¬Ľ  
\v 5 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ taŇčan, Ňčacloku: ¬ęK…Ē s…ôluks…õ nd…õk…ôl a d…ôk…Ēm k…ôgb…ôt k…Ēn k…ônay…õf…õ-…õ, eŇčyif su: ‚ÄĻTa ake t…Ē n…ônat…ĒlaŇč…õ SaŇč-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 6 K…Ē s…ôloku a nda afum k…ôncy…õf…õ-…õ, aka d…Ēt…Ēf f…ôp Ňčancacas su, bawo f…ôp f…ônac…ôr…õ a SaŇč sayib…õ s'…õnay…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčaluks…õ Yesu: ¬ęS…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęIna s…Ē, if…Ēloku nu k…ôtam nk…õ iŇčy…Ēn…õ mam…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Totubc…õn…õ ta ab…ôc a Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē al…õc 
\r Mat 21.33-46; Mark 12.1-12 
\p  
\v 9 K…Ē Yesu …õy…õf…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr afum d…ôtotubc…õn…õ nt…õ: ¬ęFum …õnab…Ēf Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč yi ab…ôc al…Ēma, Ňčat…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē akak…Ē k…ôcs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôway, k…Ē nk…Ēn owur k'…ĒŇčk…Ē mar…ônt mowonu.  
\v 10 Nt…õ t…õm tepim t…õmb…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē osom w…ôcar nn…Ē ab…ôc Ňčayi m…Ē, k…ôk…ĒbaŇč yokom ya w…õn ny…õ p…ômar Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôway k…Ēn m…Ē. Mba k…Ē ab…ôc a Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē Ňčasut k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasak, k'olukus waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr.  
\v 11 K…Ē w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē nw…õ …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôsom w…ôcar w…ôl…Ēma, k…Ē ab…ôc akak…Ē Ňčasut s…Ē fum nw…õ, k…Ē Ňčalap…ôs k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasak, nk…Ēn s…Ē k'olukus waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr.  
\v 12 K…Ē w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē osom s…Ē w…ôka maas, k…Ē ab…ôc a Ňčgb…Ēnk…ôl…Ē Ňčambop…ôr s…Ē w…ôkak…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs k…Ē.  
\v 13 K…Ē w…ôka Ňčgb…Ēk…ôl…Ē nw…õ eyifn…õ: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c'indey…Ē-…õ? Wan kem nw…õ imb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē indesom. T…Ēl…Ēma ŇčaŇčk…Ēlel…ôs w…ôkak…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 14 Mba nt…õ ab…Ēf a Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk wan ka w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalok…õn…õ: ‚ÄĻW…ôl…õk k…Ēn k…õ …Ēf…Ē, w…ôkaw…õ. Padif k…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē yede y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yosu m…Ē.‚Äļ  
\v 15 K…Ē ab…ôc aŇč…õ Ňčasump…ôr wan ka w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ k…Ē saŇčka tadar…ôŇč, k…Ē Ňčandif.¬Ľ 
\p K…Ē Yesu eyif ac…ôŇčk…ôl …Ēn, ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē w…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē nw…õ endey…Ē Ňča-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 16 K…Ē Yesu …Ēn…Ēc…ôr: ¬ęW…ôka Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē p…ôder p…ôdif…ôt ab…ôc akak…Ē f…ôp, p…ôbaŇč s…Ē Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē y…Ēn p…ôs…ĒŇč y…õb…ôc ya yi ab…ôc al…Ēma.¬Ľ Nt…õ afum Ňčane moloku mm…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęTa tat…Ēk…Ē t…õtam k…ôyi!¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčkaf…ôli k…ôro k'…Ēm…Ēm…ôn Ňča, k'eyif: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē Yecic…ôs Yosoku yay…õ yoloku oŇč-…õ?: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻTogbu mp…õ ac…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē Ňčanace m…Ē, 
\q1 p…õnader p…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč togbu p…Ēt…Ēt, pa dac…Ē.‚Äļ 
\q1  
\v 18 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õnt…õmp…õn…õ pi k…ôroŇč m…Ē, …õnt…õp…õ. 
\q1 M…ôna nw…õ p…õnt…õmp…õn…õ s…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē, pomputuk …ôm.¬Ľ 
\s1 At…ôks…õ a sariy…õ s'aSuyif ŇčafaŇč k…ôc…ôp…õ Yesu towul 
\r Mat 22.15-22; Mark 12.13-17 
\p  
\v 19 At…ôks…õ a sariy…õ k…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč Ňčact…õn k…ôt…ôp Yesu waca t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, bawo Ňčanac…ôr…õ a tetaŇčan t'…õnalok…õ totubc…õn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē. Mba Ňčacnes…õ afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē.  
\v 20 Nt…õ ŇčanafaŇč k…ôsump…ôr Yesu d…ômoloku m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasom at…õn…ôs mes aŇč…õ ŇčanabaŇč…õn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ alompu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčatam k…ôb…õr k…Ē w…ôb…õ d…ôwaca, nw…õ …õnat…Ēmp…ôr k…ôtam k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa d…õb…õ da Rom m…Ē.  
\v 21 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ anasom m…Ē, ŇčancaŇč Yesu moloku: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, s…ônc…ôr…õ a moloku mam…õ m…ôŇčloku m…ôct…ôks…õ mi afum m…Ē m…Ēs…Ēk. M…ôf…Ēkiti fum k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ēn, mba d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu yati d…Ē m…ônt…ôks…õ afum d…ôkance.  
\v 22 Awa, m…ôloku su ma, p…ômar s…ôs…ĒŇč dut dosu Sesar w…ôb…õ w…ôka t…Ēf ya Rom ba, ka ta s…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē di?¬Ľ  
\v 23 Mba k…Ē Yesu …õn…õp…ôl towul taŇčan, k'oluks…õ Ňča:  
\v 24 ¬ęN…ôment…ôr im p…ôsam gb…ôleŇč bin. Alulu Ňča ana Ňčeyi p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē-…õ, k…Ē tewe ta w…ôkayi?¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčaloku, ¬ęSesar w…ôb…õ w…ôka Rom.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęAwa, n…ôs…ĒŇč Sesar p…Ēk…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu s…Ē p…Ēk…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēn m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 26 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôsump…ôr k…Ē d…ômoloku k…ônay nk…õ dac…Ē. Mba nt…õ moloku ma Yesu m…õnaciyan…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčancaŇčk. 
\s1 K…ôyif ka k…ôdey…õf…õ ka defi afi dac…Ē 
\r Mat 22.23-33; Mark 12.18-27 
\p  
\v 27 K…Ē aSadisi aŇč…õ Ňčanaloku a fum …Ēf…Ēy…õf…õ defi m…Ē, Ňčander Ňčayif Yesu moloku mm…õ:  
\v 28 ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, nt…õ t…Ē Musa …õnacic…õ su: ‚ÄĻK…Ē fum efi p…ôn…õnc…õ mba ta …õsak wan-…õ, w…õnc ka w…ôfi, p…ôl…õk w…ôc…ôbok…ôra p…ôs…ĒŇč w…õnc w…ôfi yuruya.‚Äļ  
\v 29 Aw…õnc cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňčanayi. K…Ē w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē …õn…õnc…õ, k'efi, …õsak f…õ wan.  
\v 30 K…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč …õnas…ôr w…ôran w…ôka w…õnc,  
\v 31 k…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda k…Ē w…ôka maas …õnas…ôr k…Ē. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē t…õnak…Ē haŇč k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča aŇč…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp Ňčan…õnc…õ w…ôran nw…õ, mba nw…õ o nw…õ …õsak f…õ wan.  
\v 32 T…õlp…ôs oŇč, k…Ē w…ôran s…Ē efi.  
\v 33 Ti disr…õ, k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk d…õy…õf…õ da afi dendeb…ôp-…õ, an'endel…õk w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ-…õ? Bawo afum akaŇč…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňčanan…õnc…õ k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 34 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęArkun k…Ē aran a doru dand…õ ŇčaŇčn…õnc…õn…õ.  
\v 35 Mba aŇč…õ andekiti pan…ôŇčk dolompu daŇčan m…Ē, p…ômar Ňčaf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē Ňčayi s…Ē w…ôyeŇč doru nd…õ dender m…Ē, Ňčaf…Ēde Ňčacn…õnc…õn…õ.  
\v 36 Ňäaf…Ētam s…Ē k…ôfi, bawo p…ôyi Ňča p…ôm…Ē m…õl…õk…õ, Ňča Ňčandey…Ēn…õ awut a Kanu, bawo Kanu k…ôyekti Ňča d…ôdefi.  
\v 37 Musa oloku p…ôsoku p…õs a afi Ňčandef…Ēt…õ nt…õ Kanu k…ônaloku k…Ē nde t…õr…ônt…ôm mp…õ p…õncmar m…Ē. D…ôndo Musa ewe Mariki: ‚ÄĻKanu ka Abraham, Kanu ka Siyaka, Kanu ka Yakuba.‚Äļ¬Ľ  
\v 38 K…Ē Yesu …Ēn…Ēc…ôr, ¬ęBaf…Ē Kanu ka afi k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ, mba ka ayi w…ôyeŇč, bawo nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē, f…ôp f…ôŇčyi w…ôyeŇč.¬Ľ  
\v 39 K…Ē acic…ôs a sariy…õ al…Ēma Ňčal…õk moloku, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, m…ôloku belbel!¬Ľ  
\v 40 K…Ē Ňčanes…õ s…Ē k…ôyif k…Ē moloku m…Ēl…Ēma. 
\s1 W…ôy…õk-y…õk w…ôka Kanu k…Ē Dawuda 
\r Mat 22.41-46; Mark 12.35-37 
\p  
\v 41 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē antam k…ôloku a Krist wan ka Dawuda gb…ôc…ôr…ôm …Ēf…Ē-…õ?  
\v 42 Bawo Dawuda nk…Ēn yati oloku buk ba Yabura Dawuda disr…õ: 
\q1 ‚ÄĻMariki Kanu …õnaloku Mariki mem: 
\q1 M…ôder m…ônd'em nn…Ē k…ôca kem k…ôt…Ēt, 
\q1  
\v 43 haŇč iclip k…ôboc ater…õn…õ am w…õc…ôk wam d…ônt…Ēf.‚Äļ\x - \xo 20:43 \xt Yabura 110.1\x* 
\m  
\v 44 K…Ē Dawuda ewe w…ôsom w…ôka Kanu ¬ęMariki m…Ēn¬Ľ, c…ôke c…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õntam k…ôy…Ēn…õ wan k…Ēn-…õ?¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu oloku a pak…õmb…ôrn…õ m…Ēy…Ē ma at…ôks…õ sariy…õ 
\r Mat 23.1-36; Mark 12.38-40 
\p  
\v 45 Nt…õ afum Ňčayi k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Yesu m…Ē, k'oloku ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč:  
\v 46 ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif: Ňäamb…Ēt…ôr k…ôcac…õn…õ suma s…ôp…ĒŇč, Ňčamb…Ēt…ôr pacyif Ňča k…ôyif k…ôlel mofo mm…õ amb…ôps…õn…õ m…Ē, Ňčamb…Ēt…ôr pacs…ĒŇč Ňča s…ôc…Ēm s…ôkiriŇč sa d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, pacs…ĒŇč Ňča d…ôk…ônd…õ d'ab…õ mofo medi yeri d…ôc…ôsata.  
\v 47 ŇäacbaŇčs…ôr ac…ôbok…ôra daka daŇčan, Ňčacb…Ēls…õ sali nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pagb…õk…ôr…õ Ňča m…Ē. Andek…Ēkiti Ňča kiti k…ôyeŇčki!¬Ľ 
\c 21  
\s1 K…ôpoc…õ ka w…ôran w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka nw…õ wos …õnafi m…Ē 
\r Mark 12.41-44 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Yesu eyekti f…Ēr, k'…õn…ôŇčk nt…õ aka daka Ňčancb…õr k…ôpoc…õ k…ôŇčan kaŇčk…ôra ka p…ôsam ka \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* m…Ē.  
\v 2 K'…õn…ôŇčk s…Ē w…ôc…ôbok…ôra w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka p…ôcb…õr f…ôr…õŇčk m…õr…ôŇč.  
\v 3 K'oloku: ¬ęKance icloku nu: W…ôc…ôbok…ôra w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka w…ôkaw…õ ompoc…õ p…ôtas ak…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 4 Bawo afum f…ôp, pecern…õ paŇčan p…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…ôpoc…õ k…ôŇčan, mba nk…Ēn, k…ôt…Ēy…Ē k…Ēn daka disr…õ omboc p…Ēk…Ē …Ēy…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm pedi m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu oluku a andel…ôs…ôr k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu 
\r Mat 24.1-2; Mark 13.1-2 
\p  
\v 5 Afum al…Ēma Ňčancloku teta \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k*: ¬ęK…ôntes…õ k'alomp…ôs…õ ki masar m…õpat m…Ēt…Ēt k…Ē ca y…Ēt…Ēt ya ki ny…õ aŇčs…ĒŇč Kanu k…ôpoc…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloku:  
\v 6 ¬ęD…Ēs…Ēk dendeder, mam…õ n…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õ m…Ē f…ôp andewuŇč mi. Tasar p…Ēf…ĒdedeŇčs…õ tasar p…Ēl…Ēma k…ôroŇč.¬Ľ 
\s1 P…ôl…õc k…Ē k…ôt…Ēr…ôs 
\r Mat 24.3-14; Mark 13.3-13 
\p  
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôt…ôks…õ, ake t…õm t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē tendeyi-…õ? T…õgb…õk…ôr…õ tere tendementer a mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…ôp-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 8 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ, ta n…ôsakn…õ patal…ôr nu! Bawo afum alar…ôm Ňčandeder ŇčacbaŇč…õn…õ k…ôb…ôc…õ tewe tem, Ňčacloku nu: ‚ÄĻIn'…Ēf…Ē, w…ôsom w…ôka Kanu,‚Äļ ‚ÄĻT…õm t…õmb…ôp!‚Äļ Mba ta n…ôdec…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč!  
\v 9 K…Ē n…ôndene pacloku teta k…ôwan, k'afum a d…Ēt…Ēf ŇčayeŇčk…ôr ab…õ aŇčan b…ôk…ôc-…õ, ta n…ônes…õ. P…ômar mam…Ēk…Ē monuŇčk…õn…õ meder k…ôr…õsna, mba baf…Ē nd…õk…ôl doru dand…õ dendelip.¬Ľ  
\v 10 K'oloku Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęAfum a t…Ēf Ňčandey…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē afum al…Ēma, d…õb…õ d…õy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē d…õb…õ.  
\v 11 Ant…Ēf Ňčendeyikc…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč mofo m…Ēl…Ēma, dor k…Ē docu dendeyi. Mes m…õw…õy-w…õy mendeyi, k…Ē \k m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…Ēp…ĒŇč mm…õ mendey…õf…õ nde Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē\k*.  
\v 12 Mba mam…Ēk…Ē mendeb…ôp, pasump…ôr nu, pat…Ēr…ôs nu, pas…ĒŇč nu k…ôk…Ēkiti d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif a padeb…õr nu d…ôbili. Andekek…ôr…õ nu nda ab…õ a t…Ēf k…Ē akiriŇč a s…ôdare s…ôp…ĒŇč al…Ēma k…ôk…Ēkiti nu teta tewe tem.  
\v 13 Tat…Ēk…Ē tendemar nu k…ôloku ka t…Ēk…Ē n…ônc…ôr…õ tetem m…Ē.  
\v 14 Ta n…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ p…ôlar…ôm t…õyacn…õ tonu.  
\v 15 Ina w…ôkaw…õ yati in'endek…Ēs…ĒŇč nu moloku k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ mes nk…õ ater anu nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēdetam k…ôgb…õk…ôl m…Ē.  
\v 16 Akom…õn…õ, aw…õnc aŇča, anapa, k…Ē ab…Ēt anu yati Ňčandek…Ēb…õr nu ater…õn…õ anu d…ôwaca, andes…ĒŇč…õ alar…ôm k…ôfi nu dac…Ē.  
\v 17 F…ôp f…ôndeter nu teta tewe tem.  
\v 18 Mba ali k…ôfon konu ka d…ôromp kin k…ôf…Ēdes…Ēl…õ.  
\v 19 K…Ē n…ômb…õr…õn…õ k…ôsump…ôr belbel-…õ, n…ôndeyacn…õ n…ôyi doru.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu …õnd…ôŇčk k…ôdel…ôs…ôr ka Yerusal…õm 
\r Mat 24.15-21; Mark 13.14-19 
\p  
\v 20 ¬ęK…Ē n…ônden…ôŇčk as…Ēdar Ňčak…õl Yerusal…õm-…õ, n…ôc…ôr…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē a k…ôl…ôs…ôr ka di k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.  
\v 21 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ak…Ē Ňčayi Yude m…Ē, Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôp…õrn…õ ka d…ôm…Ēr…Ē. Ak…Ē Ňčayi Yerusal…õm dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňčawur. Ak…Ē Ňčayi d…ôkulum m…Ē, ta Ňčab…õr…õ s…Ē dare de.  
\v 22 Bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d'andeboc kiti, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ mes mm…õ anacic m…Ē f…ôp meyi.  
\v 23 Pucuy pere p…Ē tendey…Ēn…õ ab…õk…ôs, k…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčande Ňčacm…õs…ôr d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē! Bawo p…ôyeŇčki p…Ēp…ĒŇč pendeyi d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēt…Ēf, k…Ē m…õt…õl…õ m…Ēp…ĒŇč ma Kanu nn…Ē afum akak…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 24 Sakma s…Ē andedif…ôt…õ Ňča, t…Ēf f…ôp yosump…ôr-sump…ôr Ňča yekek…ôr…õ Ňča p…ôb…Ēl…õ. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē afum acuru ŇčabaŇč Yerusal…õm, haŇč t…õm nt…õ as…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē teclip.¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôder ka Wan ka W…ôrkun 
\r Mat 24.29-31; Mark 13.24-27 
\p  
\v 25 ¬ęM…Ēy…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ mm…õ m…õy…õf…õ nde Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē mendeyi d…ôdec, d…ôŇčof k…Ē d…ôc…Ēs. D…ônt…Ēf, b…ôk…ôc yendel…õc…õ-l…õc…õ afum teta pukul…õ-kul…õ pa d…ôk…ôba k…Ē yam ya ki.  
\v 26 Afum Ňčandefin…õ k…ônes…õ ka k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ ka t…Ēk…Ē tendeder d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, bawo f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa k…Ēm f…ôndeyikc…õ.  
\v 27 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē anden…ôŇčk Wan ka W…ôrkun k…ôder k…ôp k…ôroŇč, d…ôf…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôlar…ôm, k…Ē d…ôn…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn.  
\v 28 K…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē mendecop k…ôder-…õ, n…ôlomp, n…ôyekti s…ôbomp, bawo k…ôs…ĒŇč konu k…ôway k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 C…ôke c…Ē k…ôt…Ēk k…ôkom k…ônat…ôks…õ-…õ? 
\r Mat 24.32-35; Mark 13.28-31 
\p  
\v 29 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča totubc…õn…õ tin: ¬ęN…ôn…ôŇčk k…ôt…Ēk k…ôkom\f + \fr 21:29 \ft  C…ôTabo ¬ęfiguier¬Ľ\f* k…Ē t…Ēk y…õl…ôp…ôs ny…õ.  
\v 30 N…ônck…Ēnan…ôŇčk yi y…õl…õŇčk, n…ôc…ôr…õ katin a k…ôt…ôn k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.  
\v 31 N…ôna s…Ē, k…Ē n…ônden…ôŇčk mes mam…Ēk…Ē mecder-…õ, n…ôc…ôr…õ a d…õb…õ da Kanu d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ.  
\v 32 Kance icloku nu: D…õt…õmp dand…õ d…Ēf…Ēcep…ôr ta mes mam…õ f…ôp meyi-…õ.  
\v 33 K…Ēm k…Ē ant…Ēf yendes…Ēl…õ mba moloku mem m…Ēf…Ēdes…Ēl…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Ta n…ôdir…ôrn…õ! 
\p  
\v 34 ¬ęN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ belbel! Ta n…ôsak b…ôk…ôc yonu y…õtas…ôrn…õ c…ôsata k…Ē k…ôcis, k…Ē k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ ka doru dand…õ, k…Ē p…ôyi ti tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēp…ĒŇč dad…Ēk…Ē dendeb…ôp…õn'am,  
\v 35 p…ôm…Ē nt…õ manta m…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ lop m…Ē. Bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē dendeb…ôp…õn…õ afum a doru f…ôp.  
\v 36 Ta n…ôdir…ôrn…õ, \k n…ôclok-lok…ôr Kanu\k* t…õm f…ôp, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôde n…ôs…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ômulp…õn…õ mes m…Ēk…Ē mendeder m…Ē f…ôp, n…ôdek…Ē n…ôc…ôm…õ, n…ôment…ôrn…õ Wan ka W…ôrkun, ta n…ôlap…ôrn…õ.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 37 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, Yesu p…ôct…ôks…õ afum d…ôndo \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k*, k'owur k…ôk…Ēcep…ôr…õn…õ pibi nde aŇčwe ¬ęT…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif¬Ľ m…Ē.  
\v 38 Afum f…ôp, k…Ē dec d…Ēs…Ēk-…õ, Ňčanck…Ē nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* k…ôk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē. 
\c 22  
\s1 Ab…õ k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôy…Ē ka Yesu p…ôl…õc 
\r Mat 26.1-5; Mark 14.1-2; IsaŇč 11.45-53 
\p  
\v 1 K…ôsata ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin nk…õ aŇčwe k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ medif m…Ē k…ônal…Ēt…ôrn…õ.  
\v 2 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôt…õn nt…õ ŇčaŇčy…Ē a Ňčadif Yesu m…Ē, mba Ňčacnes…õ afum. 
\s1 Yudas k…ôwos…õ k…Ēn k…ômar ab…õ a aSuyif a Ňčasump…ôr Yesu 
\r Mat 26.17-25; Mark 14.10-11 
\p  
\v 3 K…Ē Sentani s…ômb…õr…õ Yudas, nw…õ ancwe ¬ęW…ôka dare da Keriyot¬Ľ m…Ē, nw…õ ancl…Ēm ac…õps…õ a Yesu w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 4 K…Ē Yudas …ĒŇčk…Ē Ňčanen…õn…õ k…Ē ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ k…Ē as…Ēdar aŇč…õ Ňčancbum \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* m…Ē, t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar p…ôb…õr Yesu Ňča d…ôwaca m…Ē.  
\v 5 K…Ē p…ômb…Ēt Ňča, k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē p…ôsam.  
\v 6 K…Ē Yudas owos…õ, k'…õy…õf…õ oŇč k…ôt…õn t…Ēy…Ē nt…õ …ĒŇčy…Ē a p…ôb…õr Yesu Ňča d…ôwaca ta afum Ňčanc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôs…ĒŇč ka k…ôlomp…ôs yeri ya k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr 
\r Mat 26.17-25; Mark 14.12-21; IsaŇč 13.21-30 
\p  
\v 7 K…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôsata ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin d…õmb…ôp nd…õ p…ômar padif aŇčkesiya ŇčoloŇčn…õ Ňča K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ medif m…Ē.  
\v 8 K…Ē Yesu osom Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč, p…ôcloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôlomps…õ su yeri ya k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif\f + \fr 22:8 \fq K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif \ft C…ôKresi = Pak\f*, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôde s…ôdi yi m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 9 K…Ē Ňčayif Yesu: ¬ęDeke m…ôfaŇč a s…ôlomp…ôs yi-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 10 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē n…ôndena n…ôcb…õr…õ dare disr…õ-…õ, n…ôŇčk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma p…ôsar…õ apamp…õ Ňča domun. N…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč haŇč nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ēb…õr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 11 N…ôloku w…ôka k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē: ‚ÄĻW…ôt…ôks…õ osom su a s…ôder s…ôyif'…ôm: Deke d…ôk…ôl…Ē deyi nd…õ indedi yeri ya k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif k…Ē ac…õps…õ em dar…ôŇč-…õ?‚Äļ  
\v 12 Endek…Ēment…ôr nu k…ôl…Ē darenc, d…ôk…ôl…Ē d…Ēp…ĒŇč palomp…ôs di belbel. D…ôndo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēlomp…ôs yeri ya k…ôsata.  
\v 13 K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp ca f…ôp p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Yesu …õnaloku Ňča ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs yeri ya k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôyer ka k…ôcom ka k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr 
\r Mat 26.26-30; Mark 14.22-26 
\p  
\v 14 Nt…õ t…õm t…õmb…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu …õnd…õ d…õm…õsa k…ôdi yeri k…Ē Asom …Ēn.  
\v 15 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęP…ômbas im k…ôdi yeri ya k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif yay…õ k…Ē n…ôna, a idet…Ēr…Ē.  
\v 16 Bawo iclok'un, if…Ēs…Ēdi yi, haŇč t…õm nt…õ teta yi tendek…Ēlar…õ nde akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk t…Ēmb…ôl, k'eyif Kanu barka, k'oloku: ¬ęN…ôl…õk t…Ēmb…ôl tant…õ, n…ôyer…õn…õ pedisr…õ pa pi,  
\v 18 bawo icloku nu, if…Ēs…Ēmun w…õn haŇč d…õb…õ da Kanu deder.¬Ľ  
\v 19 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ day, k…Ē Yesu …õl…õk k…ôcom, nt…õ elip k…ôyif Kanu barka\f + \fr 22:19 \fq K…ôyif Kanu barka\ft  = ¬ęk…ôkor-koru Kanu¬Ľ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ¬ęk…ôyif Kanu n…ôwali teta k…ôcom¬Ľ \f* m…Ē, k'entepi ki, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…ôs Ňča p…ôcloku: ¬ęDis dem d…Ē dand…õ, nd…õ as…ĒŇč…õ tetonu m…Ē. N…ôde n…ôcy…Ē ti nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôcc…õm-c…õmn'em m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 20 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôdi yeri m…Ē, k'…õl…õk s…Ē t…Ēmb…ôl ta w…õn, p…ôcloku: ¬ęMecir mem mm…õ meyi d…ôt…Ēmb…ôl tant…õ m…Ē, m'andeloŇč…õ tetonu, mi mendecaŇč…ôs danapa dofu da Kanu k…Ē n…ôna.  
\v 21 Ti disr…õ, fum nw…õ endeb…õr im ater…õn…õ em d…ôwaca m…Ē, …õnd…õ nn…Ē am…õsa ŇčaŇč…õ k…Ē ina.  
\v 22 Wan ka W…ôrkun endefi, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic ti m…Ē, mba p…ôl…õc peyi fum w…ôkak…Ē endeb…õr k…Ē ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyift…õn…õ d…ônda, an'eyi su dac…Ē nw…õ endeb…õr k…Ē ater…õn…õ …Ēn d…ôwaca m…Ē? 
\s1 An'ecep…ôr nu f…ôp d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ-…õ? 
\p  
\v 24 K…Ē k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôy…õf…õ ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč dac…Ē, teta k…ôc…ôr…õ ka nw…õ …õmb…õk d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôcep…ôr Ňča dac…Ē f…ôp m…Ē.  
\v 25 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęAb…õ a t…Ēf Ňčantas…ôrn…õ afum aŇčan, aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ k…ôtam nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē. Ab…õ akak…Ē Ňčacwen…õ ¬ęAy…Ē mes m…Ēt…Ēt¬Ľ.  
\v 26 Baf…Ē tin tayi t…Ē k…Ē n…ôna! Mba m…õn…õ nw…õ encep…ôr nu f…ôp m…Ē, p…ôyi p…ôm…Ē nw…õ …õf…õt…õ nu dac…Ē f…ôp m…Ē. Nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ m…Ē, p…ôyi p…ôm…Ē w…ômar…ôs.  
\v 27 Bawo, nw…õ encep…ôr nu m…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ, nw…õ …õnd…õ d…õm…õsa m…Ē ba, ka nw…õ …õŇčk…õr…õ k…Ē yeri d…ônda m…Ē? Baf…Ē nw…õ …õnd…õ d…õm…õsa m…Ē …Ēf…Ē? K…Ē ina, iyi nu dac…Ē, p…ôm…Ē nw…õ …õŇčk…õr…õ nu yeri d…õm…õsa m…Ē.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 28 ¬ęN…ôn'…õnasim…ôs k…Ē ina t…õm nt…õ inayi p…ôcuca disr…õ m…Ē.  
\v 29 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ is…ĒŇč nu d…õb…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ papa kem …õnas…ĒŇč im di m…Ē:  
\v 30 Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôdi yeri, n…ômun am…õsa Ňčem k…ôroŇč nde akip Ňča d…õb…õ dem d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē. N…ônd…õ s…ôc…Ēm sa d…õb…õ k…ôroŇč, n…ôckiti c…ôsuŇčka w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ca Yisrayel. 
\s1 Yesu …õnd…ôŇčk a Piy…õr endebaŇč…õn…õ k…ôt…Ēc…ôr…õ k…Ē 
\r Mat 26.31-35; Mark 14.27-31; IsaŇč 13.36-38 
\p  
\v 31 K…Ē Yesu oloku Sim…ĒŇč Piy…õr: ¬ęSim…ĒŇč, Sim…ĒŇč! M…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ! Sentani s…ôntola k…ôd…õs-d…õs'un d…ôsifit…õ p…ôm…Ē k…ôcom.  
\v 32 Mba intolan'am, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õkaf…ôl'am\f + \fr 22:32 \fq Ta ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õkaf…ôl'am,\ft  k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ¬ęta k…ôlaŇč kam k…ôsol…õ¬Ľ\f* m…Ē. K…Ē m…ôndeder'im-…õ, m…ôyeŇčk…ôs b…ôk…ôc ya aw…õnc'…ôm aŇča.¬Ľ  
\v 33 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku k…Ē: ¬ęMariki, iwos…õ k…ôk…Ē d…ôbili, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ifi k…Ē m…ôna.¬Ľ  
\v 34 Mba k…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęPiy…õr, iclok'…ôm, m…ôndegb…õk…ôl m…Ēk…Ē k…ôc…ôr'em k…ômaas a kicipi k…ôccam.¬Ľ 
\s1 P…ôsam pa delek, al…Ēba, k…Ē dakma 
\p  
\v 35 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęNt…õ incsom nu ta iŇčs…ĒŇč nu p…ôsam, ta iŇčs…ĒŇč nu al…Ēba Ňč…õb…õr…õ yamos, ta iŇčs…ĒŇč nu c…Ēfta c…ôb…õrn…õ m…Ē, paka penayi yi dac…Ē mp…õ n…ônat…Ē-s…Ēt…Ē m…Ē ba?¬Ľ K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčaloku: ¬ęAla! Ali pin p…õnayi f…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 36 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęNd…õk…ôl mes m…õs…ôkp…õ! M…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē p…ôsam m…Ē, m…ôl…õk…õn…õ pi. M…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē al…Ēba Ňč…õb…õr…õ yamos m…Ē, m…ôl…õk…õn…õ Ňči, k…Ē m…ôna nw…õ m…ônt…Ēy…Ē dakma m…Ē, m…ôcam…ôs yamos yam, m…ôway din!  
\v 37 Bawo, iclok'un: M…õn…õ t…Ēk…Ē ancic m…Ē t…õlar…õ nn…Ē iyi m…Ē: ‚ÄĻAnal…Ēm k…Ē calbante dac…Ē.‚Äļ Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ temi m…Ē, t…Ēmb…Ēl…õ f…õ s…Ē k…ôlip.¬Ľ  
\v 38 K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôb…õ m…ôbaŇč sakma ns…õ m…õr…ôŇč.¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęP…ônt…ôŇčn…õ tant…õ.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Olif 
\r Mat 26.36-46; Mark 14.32-42 
\p  
\v 39 P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēncy…Ē ti m…Ē, Yesu endewur k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē ta T…Ēk ya Olif. K'ac…õps…õ …Ēn Ňčanc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč. 
\p  
\v 40 Nt…õ Ňčamb…ôp k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôtola Kanu ta n…ôsakn…õ n…ôb…õr…õ k…ôwak…ôs disr…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 41 K'…Ēmb…Ēl…õn…õ Ňča p…ôm…Ē k…ôl…ôm ka tasar katin, k'…õnc…ôp suwu, k'ontola Kanu,  
\v 42 p…ôcloku: ¬ęPapa k…Ē m…ôwos…õ-…õ, m…ôb…Ēl…õn'em t…Ēmb…ôl pa k…ôt…Ēr…ôs pamp…õ. Ti disr…õ, ta t…õfaŇč tem teyi, mba tam teyi.¬Ľ  
\v 43 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ m…Ēl…Ēma mowur…ôr k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ darenc, k…ôdeyeŇčk…ôs k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.  
\v 44 K'ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õl…õc…õ-l…õc…õ k…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr Kanu, k'ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õmp…õ k…Ē, k…Ē kawon…õ k…Ēn k…ôyi p…ôm…Ē nt…õ mocul ma mecir mendet…õmp…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.  
\v 45 K…Ē Yesu …õsak s…Ē k…ôtola Kanu k…ôŇčk…Ē …õnayi m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčadir…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc y…õr…õnc.  
\v 46 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôndir…õn…õ-…õ? N…ôy…õf…õ, \k n…ôtola Kanu\k* ta n…ôsakn…õ n…ôb…õr…õ k…ôwak…ôs disr…õ!¬Ľ 
\s1 K…ôsump…ôr ka Yesu 
\r Mat 26.47-56; Mark 14.43-50; IsaŇč 18.3-11 
\p  
\v 47 Yesu p…ôs…Ēr…Ēlok-loku, k…Ē k…ônay k'afum k…ônder, fum w…ôk…Ē ancwe Yudas, nw…õ …õnayi ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē m…Ē, p…ôyi Ňča kiriŇč. K'…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Yesu k…ôk…Ēcup k…Ē.  
\v 48 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęYudas, k…ôcup k…Ē m…ôndel…õk…õ Wan ka W…ôrkun m…ôb…õr k…Ē ater …Ēn d…ôwaca!¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 49 Nt…õ asol a Yesu Ňčan…ôŇčk tat…Ēk…Ē t…õnak…Ēcep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayif Yesu: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, s…ôntam k…ôsutn…õn…õ sakma sosu ba?¬Ľ  
\v 50 K…Ē fum w…ôkin ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč dac…Ē, …õnc…õp w…ôcar ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč al…ôŇč…ôs Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, k'eŇčgbinti Ňči.  
\v 51 K…Ē Yesu …õyac Ňča p…ôcloku: ¬ęN…ôce tat…Ēk…Ē!¬Ľ K'oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ al…ôŇč…ôs Ňča fum w…ôkak…Ē, k'…õntamn…õ. 
\p  
\v 52 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ k'…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, ab…õ a abum a k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf aŇč…õ Ňčanader k…ôsump…ôr k…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęN…ônder n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr sakma k…Ē t…Ēk yosutn…õn…õ, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ n…ônder k…ôsump…ôr kalbante m…Ē.  
\v 53 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk s…ôn'encyi nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k* k…Ē n…ôna, ali fum …õnasump…ôr f'em. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, t…õm tonu t…õb…ôp, k…Ē k…ôtam ka kubump.¬Ľ 
\s1 Piy…õr …õmbaŇčn…õ k…ôt…Ē-c…ôr…õ Yesu 
\r Mat 26.57-58,69-75; Mark 14.53-54,66-72; IsaŇč 18.12-18,25-27 
\p  
\v 54 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôsump…ôr Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē nde k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč. Mba Piy…õr p…ôcm…Ēm…ôn ti p…ôb…Ēl…õ.  
\v 55 K'amot n…õnc abaŇčka dac…Ē k'and…õ di k…ôs…ôk. K…Ē Piy…õr …õnd…õ Ňča dac…Ē.  
\v 56 Nt…õ w…ôcar w…ôyec…ôra w…ôl…Ēma …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē p…ônd…õ Ňča dac…Ē n…õnc kiriŇč m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęŇäa Ňčayina k…Ē fum w…ôkaw…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 57 K…Ē Piy…õr …õŇčgb…õk…ôl w…ôran nw…õ, p…ôcloku: ¬ęW…ôran, inc…ôr…õ f…õ fum w…ôkaw…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 58 P…ôwon f…õ k…Ē w…ôl…Ēma …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęM…ôna s…Ē akin ayi Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Piy…õr oloku w…ôrkun nw…õ: ¬ęAla! Baf…Ē akin ayi Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 59 K…Ē dec din dencep…ôr, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma …õŇčgb…ôc k…ôloku: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ oŇčwur…õn…õ k…ônayi k…Ē Yesu, bawo w…ôKalile …Ēf…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 60 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku: ¬ęM…ôna, ina inc…ôr…õ f…õ tant…õ m…ôŇčk…õr…õ k…ôloku m…Ē.¬Ľ Ňäayi k…ôlok-loku k…Ē kicipi k…ôncam.  
\v 61 K…Ē Mariki …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ k'…õŇčgb…ôtn…õ Piy…õr. K…Ē Piy…õr …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ toloku t…Ēk…Ē Mariki Yesu …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęM…ôndegb…õk…ôl k…ôt…Ēc…ôr'em k…ômaas a kicipi k…ôccam.¬Ľ  
\v 62 K…Ē Piy…õr owur nde dabaŇčka, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôbok belbel. 
\s1 K…ôl…Ēm…ôs k…Ē k…ôsut ka Yesu 
\r Mat 26.67-68; Mark 14.65 
\p  
\v 63 Arkun aŇč…õ Ňčancbum Yesu m…Ē Ňčafani k…Ē, Ňčacsut k…Ē.  
\v 64 Ňäackump k…Ē k…ôro, a Ňčacyif…ôt k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęAwa Sayib…õ, m…ôloku su an'osut …ôm-…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 65 K…Ē Ňčales-les k…Ē moloku m…Ēl…Ēm…ôs m…õlar…ôm. 
\s1 Yesu nde aboc kiti ap…ĒŇč f…Ēr kiriŇč 
\r Mat 26.59-66; Mark 14.55-64; IsaŇč 18.19-24 
\p  
\v 66 Nt…õ dec d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf, aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, k'at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčamb…ôp…ôs…õn…õ. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ Yesu nde aboc kiti aSuyif Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 67 K…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist-…õ, m…ôloku su ti.¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęK'iloku nu ti-…õ, n…ôf…ĒlaŇč ti,  
\v 68 k'iyif nu s…Ē moloku-…õ, n…ôf…Ēluks'em mi.  
\v 69 K…ôy…õf…õ nd…õk…ôl, Wan ka W…ôrkun p…ônd…õ Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes f…ôp m…Ē k…ôs…ôk.¬Ľ  
\v 70 K…Ē afum f…ôp ŇčambaŇč…õn…õ: ¬ęM…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč Wan ka Kanu ba?¬Ľ K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôn'oloku ti: Nk…Ēn iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 71 K…Ē Ňčayift…õn…õ: ¬ęSede s…ôre s…Ē p…ômar payif-…õ? S…ôna yati, s…ôn'enen…õ k…Ē ti d…ôkusu.¬Ľ 
\c 23  
\s1 Yesu f…Ēr ya Pilat kiriŇč 
\r Mat 27.1-2,11-14; Mark 15.1-5; IsaŇč 18.28-38 
\p  
\v 1 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ f…ôp faŇčan, k…Ē Ňčasol…õ Yesu k…ôkek…ôr…õ k…Ē nde f…Ēr ya Pilat kiriŇč.  
\v 2 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyems…õn…õ k…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôb…ôp p…ôcgbiŇč…ôr afum k…ôyeŇčk…ôr su s…ôbomp, Ňčafati k…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ ka doru f…ôp dut, p…ôcwen…õ s…Ē ¬ęW…ôy…õk-y…õk w…ôka Kanu, w…ôb…õ w…ôka at…Ēf¬Ľ.¬Ľ  
\v 3 K…Ē Pilat eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Yesu oluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôn'oloku ti.¬Ľ  
\v 4 K…Ē Pilat oloku w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu k…Ē k…ônay ka afum: ¬ęIn…ôŇčk f…õ t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm nt…õ p…ômar pasump…ôr…õ w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 5 Mba k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôc gb…õs, k…ôloku: ¬ęAfum Ňč…Ē eŇčgbiŇč…ôr, p…ôct…ôks…õ afum at…Ēf Ňča Yude disr…õ f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Kalile nde …õnacop m…Ē, haŇč nn…Ē.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu f…Ēr ya Herodu kiriŇč 
\p  
\v 6 Nt…õ Pilat ene teta Kalile m…Ē, k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęW…ôka Kalile m…ôy…Ēn…õ ba?¬Ľ  
\v 7 Nt…õ Pilat ene a w…ôka Kalile …Ēf…Ē m…Ē, k'oloku a fum w…ôkaw…õ, Herodu p…ômar p…ôkiti k…Ē. K'oloku a paken…õ k…Ē Herodu nw…õ …õnayi mata mam…Ēk…Ē Yerusal…õm m…Ē.  
\v 8 Nt…õ Herodu …õn…ôŇčk Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt k…Ē, bawo …õnct…õn k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ p…ônawon m…Ē, teta mes m…Ēk…Ē encne pacloku t…Ēn m…Ē, p…ôy…Ē amera k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē, p…ôy…Ē \k t…Ēy…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ nt…õ t…õy…õf…õ nde Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē\k* f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč.  
\v 9 K…Ē Herodu eyif…ôt Yesu mes m…õlar…ôm, mba Yesu …õnaluks…õ f…õ k…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ.  
\v 10 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčanayi di, ŇčacnaŇčkan…õ k…ôyems…õn…õ k…Ē.  
\v 11 Herodu k…Ē abum …Ēn Ňčafani k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…Ē k…Ē p…ôl…õc p…ôl…õc, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē duma d'ab…õ, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē a paken…õ Pilat.  
\v 12 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē yati d…Ē Pilat k…Ē Herodu Ňčanab…Ēt oŇč, Ňčanater…õn…õ c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. 
\s1 Ant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôdif Yesu 
\r Mat 27.15-26; Mark 15.6-15; IsaŇč 18.39-19.16 
\p  
\v 13 K…Ē Pilat ewe aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč, ab…õ a d…Ēt…Ēf, k…Ē afum.  
\v 14 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôŇčk…õr'em fum nw…õ a nk…Ēn eŇčgbiŇč…ôr afum k…ôyeŇčk s…ôbomp. Mba f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč iyif…ôt k…Ē, ali tes tin in…ôŇčk f…õ nt…õ …Ēy…Ē mes mam…õ n…ômbonc…õ k…Ē m…Ē, nt…õ p…ômar padif…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 15 Herodu s…Ē …õn…ôŇčk f…õ ali tin, bawo oluks…õ su k…Ē. Awa! Fum w…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ē f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ p…ômar padif…õ k…Ē m…Ē.  
\v 16 K…ôsak k…Ē k'inder k'andelip k…ôsut k…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 17 K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif nk…õ o nk…õ, Pilat …õncsak…õ afum y…õŇč…ôn w…ôyi d…ôbili w…ôkin.  
\v 18 K…Ē k…ônay k…ômbaŇč…õn…õ f…ôp k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęM…ôdif w…ôkaw…õ! M…ôsak…õ su Barabas y…õŇč…ôn!¬Ľ  
\v 19 Anab…õr Barabas d…ôbili teta k…ôdif fum, nt…õ Ňčanay…õf…õ k…ôyeŇčk…ôr ab…õ a d…Ēt…Ēf s…ôbomp m…Ē.  
\v 20 K…Ē Pilat nw…õ …õnafaŇč k…ôsak Yesu m…Ē, …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôyif ti k…ônay ka afum.  
\v 21 Mba Ňčanckul…õ-kul…õ: \k ¬ęM…ôcaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl\k*! M…ôcaŇč k…Ē!¬Ľ  
\v 22 K…Ē Pilat eyif Ňča s…Ē tamaas: ¬ęP…ôl…õc pere p'…Ēy…Ē-…õ? In…ôŇčk f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ p…ômar padif…õ k…Ē m…Ē. K…ôsak k…Ē k'inder k'alip k…ôsut k…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 23 K…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ sim k…ôbup…ôr…õ a pacaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl. K…Ē sim s…ôŇčan s…ôŇčkal…ôrn…õ.  
\v 24 K…Ē Pilat owos…õ k…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ŇčanafaŇč m…Ē.  
\v 25 K…Ē Pilat …õsak y…õŇč…ôn Barabas w…ôk…Ē Ňčanawer k…Ē m…Ē. Barabas nw…õ anab…õr d…ôbili teta k…ôdif…ôt…õn…õ, k…Ē k…ôdif ka fum m…Ē. K…Ē Pilat …õl…õk Yesu, k'…õmb…õr Ňča d…ôwaca Ňčay…Ē k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ŇčanafaŇč m…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôcaŇč ka Yesu 
\r Mat 27.32-44; Mark 15.21-32; IsaŇč 19.17-27 
\p  
\v 26 Nt…õ Ňčayi k…ôkek…ôr…õ Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Sim…ĒŇč, w…ôka dare da Sir…õn …õnayi p…ôy…õf…õ dal…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgbaŇčs…ôr k…Ē t…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl ny…õ anak…Ē k…ôcaŇč Yesu m…Ē a p…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč p…ôkek…ôr…õ yi.  
\v 27 K…Ē k…ônay ka afum alar…ôm k…Ē aran Ňčanc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč Ňčacsut-sutn…õ b…ôk…ôc Ňčacy…Ēn…õ k…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr.  
\v 28 K…Ē Yesu …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęAran a Yerusal…õm, ta n…ôbok…õ tetem! Mba n…ôbok…õ te tonu k…Ē ta awut anu!  
\v 29 Bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dendeder nd…õ andeloku: ‚ÄĻP…ômb…Ēt aran aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēb…õk…ôs m…Ē, p…ômb…Ēt cor nc…õ c…ônt…Ēkom m…Ē, k…Ē m…õs…õ mm…õ m…Ēnt…Ēm…õs…ôr m…Ē!‚Äļ  
\v 30 Afum Ňčandeloku m…Ēr…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôt…õmp…õn…õ su k…ôroŇč!‚Äļ k…Ē mofo meŇčeci, ‚ÄĻM…ôgb…ôp…ôrn…õ su!‚Äļ  
\v 31 Bawo k'ay…Ē ti k…ôt…Ēk k…ôcaŇčk-…õ, c…ôke c…Ē andey…Ē k…ôwosu-…õ? 
\p  
\v 32 K…Ē Ňčasol…õn…õ s…Ē k…ôkek…ôr…õ calbante m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ anak…Ēdif…õn…õ k…Ē Yesu m…Ē.  
\v 33 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma nk…õ aŇčwe ¬ęK…ômb…õmb…ôl…õ¬Ľ m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčancaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl d…ôndo, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ calbante akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, w…ôkin p…ôyi k…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, w…ôk…Ē p…ôyi k…Ē k…ôca k…ômeriya.  
\v 34 K…Ē Yesu oloku: ¬ęPapa m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča, bawo Ňčanc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ Ňčayi k…ôy…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē as…Ēdar akaŇč…õ Ňčayer…õn…õ yamos y…Ēn Ňčakot…õ ti yampuŇčpuŇč.  
\v 35 Afum Ňčac…ôm…õ, Ňčacm…Ēm…ôn. Ab…õ Ňčacfani Yesu, Ňčacloku: ¬ęBawo …õyac ak…Ē, p…ôyacn…õ oŇč ma nk…Ēns…ôrka, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a Krist …Ēy…Ēn…õ, W…ôsom nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē-…õ!¬Ľ  
\v 36 K…Ē as…Ēdar s…Ē Ňčanc…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôk…Ēfani Yesu, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē m…ônc…Ēnc…Ē.  
\v 37 Ňäacloku: ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif-…õ, m…ôyacn…õ oŇč ma, m…ônas…ôrka!¬Ľ  
\v 38 Anacic k…Ē domp tak…ôroŇč: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka aSuyif.¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 39 Kalbante kin akak…Ē anacaŇč m…Ē, p…ôcl…Ēm…ôs Yesu, p…ôcloku: ¬ęBaf…Ē m…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist W…ôy…õk-y…õk w…ôka Kanu ba? M…ôyacn…õ oŇč ma, k…Ē s…ôna!¬Ľ  
\v 40 Mba k…Ē kalbante kam…õr…ôŇč k…ôŇčk…Ē anacaŇč m…Ē, k…ôŇčgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr k…Ē, k…ôcloku: ¬ęC…ôp…Ē m…ôf…Ēnes…õ Kanu ba, m…ôna nw…õ andey…Ē p…ôm…Ē s…ôna m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 41 ¬ęTa s…ôna, kance k…Ē, tant…õ t…Ē p…ômar pas…ĒŇč su k…ôway ka m…õl…ôs…ôr mosu. Mba w…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ēf…õ t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…õl…õc.¬Ľ  
\v 42 K'oloku: ¬ęYesu m…ôde m…ôc…õm-c…õmn'em k…Ē m…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ akip Ňča d…õb…õ dam d…ônt…Ēf-…õ.¬Ľ  
\v 43 K…Ē Yesu oloku k…Ē: ¬ęKance k…Ē, iclok'…ôm: M…Ēk…Ē, s…ôn'…ĒŇčk…Ēyi Ariyana k…Ē m…ôna.¬Ľ 
\s1 Defi da Yesu 
\r Mat 27.45-56; Mark 15.33-41; IsaŇč 19.28-30 
\p  
\v 44 DaŇč d…õnab…ôp, dec dosur…õn…õ afum d…ôs…ôbomp, k…Ē kubump k…ôntor d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp, t…õnab…Ēl…õ k…ôt…õnc haŇč salifana.  
\v 45 Dec d…õnakal…õ, p…ônabiy…õ. K…Ē k…ôloto k…ôlel nk…õ k…ôŇčk…ôŇčk t…Ēks…Ē ta k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…Ē, k…ôŇčgb…õr…õ dac…Ē.  
\v 46 K…Ē Yesu oŇčkul…ôrn…õ dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč: ¬ęPapa, il…õk amera Ňčem, k'imb…õr …ôm d…ôwaca!¬Ľ Nt…õ elip k…ôloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'efi.  
\v 47 Nt…õ w…ôb…õ k'as…Ēdar w…ôRom …õn…ôŇčk mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…õnacep…ôr m…Ē, k'oŇčkor-koru Kanu p…ôcloku: ¬ęKance k…Ē, fum w…ôkaw…õ w…ôlompu yati …õnayi!¬Ľ  
\v 48 Nt…õ k…ônay ka afum aŇč…õ Ňčanader k…ôdet…ôŇčn…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, Ňčan…ôŇčk nt…õ t…õnacep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalukus Ňčacsut-sutn…õ b…ôk…ôc n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr.  
\v 49 AŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôr…õ Yesu m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē aran ak…Ē Ňčanac…ômb…ôr k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ Kalile m…Ē, Ňčanac…ôm…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õ, Ňčacm…Ēm…ôn t…Ēk…Ē mes mencep…ôr m…Ē. 
\s1 K…ôb…õr ka Yesu d…ôkufu 
\r Mat 27.57-61; Mark 15.42-47; IsaŇč 19.38-42 
\p  
\v 50 W…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Isifu. ∆źnay…Ēn…õ aboc kiti aSuyif dac…Ē, fum w…ôt…Ēt, p…ôlomp.  
\v 51 Nk…Ēn …õnawos…õ f…õ k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôsek ka moloku mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē ma ak…Ē. W…ôka dare da Arimate …õnay…Ēn…õ, at…Ēf Ňča Yude, p…ôckar d…õb…õ da Kanu.  
\v 52 K'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde Pilat eyi m…Ē, k'ontola k…Ē k…ôbel ka Yesu.  
\v 53 K'ontor…õ k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl\f + \fr 23:53 \fq D…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl\ft  it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęk…ôt…Ēk ka k…ôpand…ôn.¬Ľ\f* nde anacaŇč k…Ē m…Ē, k'…õn…õps…ôr k…Ē kasaŇčke ka k…ôloto k…ôtel…ôr, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôboc k…Ē nde d…ôkufu nk…õ anay…Ēk d…ôtasar m…Ē. Kufu k…ônayi nk…õ anat…Ēwup fum o fum ki disr…õ k…ôr…õsna m…Ē.  
\v 54 Yuma y…õnayi, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôlomp…ôsn…õn…õ simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē d…õcfaŇč k…ôcop.  
\v 55 Aran aŇč…õ Ňčanasol k…Ē Yesu k…ôy…õf…õ Kalile m…Ē, Ňčander k…Ē Isifu, k…Ē Ňčam…Ēm…ôn kufu disr…õ, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē anaboc Yesu m…Ē.  
\v 56 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalukus dare, k…ôk…Ēlomp…ôs moro k…Ē labund…õ da d…ôris. D…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ Mariki m…Ē k…Ē ŇčaŇčes…ôm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ôsom ti m…Ē. 
\c 24  
\s1 Yesu k…ôy…õf…õ k…Ēn afi dac…Ē 
\r Mat 28.1-10; Mark 16.1-8; IsaŇč 20.1-10 
\p  
\v 1 Tataka ta sandeŇč b…ôtb…ôt suy, k…Ē aran aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē s…Ē d…ôndo d…ôkufu, Ňčakek…ôr…õ moro mobotu amb…Ēnc mm…õ Ňčanalomp…ôs m…Ē.  
\v 2 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp pabiŇčk…ôli tasar t…Ēk…Ē anasunc…õ kufu m…Ē,  
\v 3 k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ, mba Ňčanab…ôp f…õ k…ôbel ka Mariki Yesu.  
\v 4 Nt…õ tes tat…Ēk…Ē tenciyan…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē arkun m…õr…ôŇč Ňčawur…ôr Ňča, Ňčab…õrn…õ yamos yomot…ôr-mot…ôr.  
\v 5 K…ônes…õ k…ôŇčan disr…õ, k…Ē aran Ňčanc…ôp c…ôro f…ôp faŇčan d…ônt…Ēf. Mba k…Ē afum aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčayif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônt…õn…õ w…ôt…Ēfi afi dac…Ē-…õ?  
\v 6 Eyi f…õ nn…Ē! ∆Üf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē! N…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ t…Ēk…Ē …õnaloku nu nt…õ …õnayi at…Ēf Ňča Kalile m…Ē.  
\v 7 Nt…õ oncloku: ‚ÄĻM…õn…õ pal…õk Wan ka W…ôrkun pab…õr k…Ē aciya d…ôwaca, \k ŇčacaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl\k*, p…ôy…õf…õ defi tataka t…Ēn ta maas.‚Äļ¬Ľ 
\p  
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ toloku ta Yesu tat…Ēk…Ē.  
\v 9 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ d…ôndo d…ôkufu k…ôk…Ēloku ti asom a Yesu aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin, k…ôb…ôp ka afum alp…ôs ak…Ē.  
\v 10 Mari w…ôka Makdala, Yohanna, Mari w…ôka Sak k…Ē aran al…Ēma, aŇč…õ Ňčanan…ôŇčk s…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, Ňčaloku s…Ē tin tayi asom a Yesu.  
\v 11 Mba moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…õnayi Ňča p…ôm…Ē nt…õ atoŇčkulu Ňčandelok-lok…ôr Ňča m…Ē, ŇčanalaŇč f…õ moloku ma aran akak…Ē.  
\v 12 K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ, k'…õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ē nde d…ôkufu. Nt…õ ontuln…õ k…ôm…Ēm…ôn m…Ē, …õn…ôŇčk f…õ daka o daka m…õn…õ mopol ma k…ôloto m…Ēk…Ē m…õnaf…ônt…ôr…õ d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē. K'…õy…õf…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nd…Ēr…Ēn, p…ôciyan…õ k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õn…ôŇčk m…Ē. 
\s1 Nde d…Ēp…Ē da Emayus 
\r Mark 16.12-13 
\p  
\v 13 D…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē, ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč Ňčack…Ē dare d…Ēl…Ēma nd…õ ancwe Emayus m…Ē, dare d…õnayi, nd…õ d…õnab…Ēl…õn…õ Yerusal…õm k…ôk…Ēt ka dec m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.  
\v 14 Afum akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčaclok…õn…õ mes m…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē f…ôp.  
\v 15 Ňäayi k…ôlok…õn…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē, Ňčacgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ, k…Ē Yesu …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Ňča, k…Ē Ňčasol.  
\v 16 Mba paka p…Ēl…Ēma p…õncyam…ôs Ňča k…ôn…õp…ôl k…Ē.  
\v 17 K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęAke moloku m…Ē n…ôyi tant…õ n…ôŇčk…Ē m…Ē?¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ, k…Ē dis d…õnd…õnc…õ Ňča.  
\v 18 K…Ē w…ôkin w…ôk…Ē ancwe K…ôleyopas m…Ē, oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôna sona gboŇč, m…ôna eyi m…Ēk…Ē Yerusal…õm nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēc…ôr…õ nt…õ tencep…ôr mata mam…õ m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 19 K'eyif Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęAke?¬Ľ K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ tencep…ôr teta Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôka Kanu w…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē. …õnament…ôr ti d…ôm…Ēy…Ē k…Ē d…ômoloku, f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč, k…Ē nn…Ē afum Ňčayi m…Ē.  
\v 20 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč asu, k…Ē ab…õ asu aka d…Ēt…Ēf Ňčal…õk k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr k…Ē afum d…ôwaca, \k k'ancaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl\k*.\f + \fr 24:20 \fq K'ancaŇč k…Ē\ft  = ¬ęampand…ôn k…Ē d…ôk…ôt…Ēk¬Ľ k…Ē ¬ęaŇčgb…õk k…Ē d…ôk…ôt…Ēk¬Ľ\f* 
\v 21 S…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ f…Ē nk…Ēn enader k…ôwur…ôs p…ôbaŇč Yisrayel, mba mam…õ oŇč f…ôp, tataka ta maas t…Ē tant…õ, nt…õ mes mam…õ mencep…ôr m…Ē.  
\v 22 Kance k…Ē: A aran al…Ēma Ňčayi su dac…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē p…ôciyan…õ su m…Ē. ŇčanuŇčk…õn…õna k…ôk…Ē nde d…ôkufu,  
\v 23 nt…õ Ňčant…Ēnan…ôŇčk k…ôbel ka Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčander Ňčaloku su a m…õl…õk…õ mowur…ôrna Ňča, k…Ē moloku a eyi doru.  
\v 24 K…Ē afum al…Ēma Ňčayina su dac…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē d…ôndo d…ôkufu, k…Ē akak…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp mes p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aran Ňčalokuna su m…Ē, mba nk…Ēn, Ňča Ňčan…ôŇčkna f…õ k…Ē.¬Ľ  
\v 25 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôna afum at…Ēs…Ēk s…ôbomp, b…ôk…ôc yonu yoŇčwon k…ôlaŇč moloku mm…õ ad…ôŇčk a Kanu Ňčanaloku m…Ē!  
\v 26 P…ônamar dis d…Ēl…Ēl Krist W…ôy…õk-y…õk w…ôka Kanu tant…õ a p…ôdeb…õr…õ debeki d…Ēn d…Ēn disr…õ?¬Ľ  
\v 27 K…ôy…õf…õ ka buk ba Musa k…ôb…ôp ka yecic…ôs yecempi ya ad…ôŇčk a Kanu alp…ôs aŇč…õ f…ôp, k…Ē Yesu …Ēl…Ēm…ôr Ňča t…Ēk…Ē Yecic…ôs Yosoku f…ôp yoloku tet…Ēn m…Ē. 
\p  
\v 28 Nt…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ tadare t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanck…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Yesu …Ēy…Ē p…ôm…Ē nt…õ …õŇčfaŇč k…ôcep…ôr p…ôk…Ē p…ôb…Ēl…õ m…Ē.  
\v 29 Mba k…Ē Ňčam…Ēn…õ k…Ē k…ôcep…ôr, Ňčacloku: ¬ęM…ôyi nn…Ē k…Ē s…ôna, dec d…õfaŇč k…ôkal…õ, k…ôbiy…õ k…Ē p…ônd…õ. K…Ē Yesu …õmb…õr…õ k…ôk…Ēyi di k…Ē Ňča.¬Ľ  
\v 30 Ňäand…õ d…õm…õsa k…ôk…Ēdi yeri, k…Ē Yesu …õl…õk k…ôcom, k'eyif Kanu barka, k'entepi ki k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča.  
\v 31 K…Ē f…Ēr yaŇčan yemep…õ, k…Ē Ňčan…õp…ôl k…Ē, mba k'…Ēs…Ēl…õ s…Ē f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč.  
\v 32 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôlok…õn…õ: ¬ęP…ôyina f…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ n…õnc deŇčyi su d…ôcor, nt…õ endenas…Ēk…ôs…õ su moloku mecic nde d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē?¬Ľ  
\v 33 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňčalukus Yerusal…õm, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp ac…õps…õ dar…ôŇč a Yesu aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin ŇčacloŇčkan…õ k…Ē asol aŇčan,  
\v 34 Ňčacloku: ¬ęKance k…Ē: W…ôb…õ …Ēf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôwur…ôr Sim…ĒŇč!¬Ľ  
\v 35 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Ňčal…Ēm s…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanan…õp…ôl k…Ē k…ôtepi k…Ēn k…ôcom p…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē. 
\s1 Yesu k…ôment…ôrn…õ k…Ēn ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč 
\r Mat 28.16-20; Mark 16.14-18; IsaŇč 20.19-23; Asom 1.6-8 
\p  
\v 36 Ňäayi k…ôloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Yesu nk…Ēns…ôrka owur…ôr Ňča, k'oloku: ¬ęP…ôforu peyi nu!¬Ľ  
\v 37 K…Ē ayek-yek Ňčontor…ôr Ňča, k…Ē Ňčanes…õ, k…Ē p…ôyi Ňča p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ŇčaŇčn…ôŇčk tub…õri m…Ē.  
\v 38 Mba k…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē p…ôyin…õ nu yamayama tant…õ-…õ, ta ake t…Ē n…ôŇčgb…õk…ôln…õn…õ d…ôb…ôk…ôc-…õ?  
\v 39 N…ôm…Ēm…ôn ma w…õc…ôk wem k…Ē waca wem-a, ina …Ēf…Ē yati! N…ôgbuŇč…õn'em, n…ôm…Ēm…ôn! Tub…õri t…Ēy…Ē f…õ s…õm, t…Ēy…Ē f…õ b…õnt. Mba ina, iy…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ  
\v 40 Yesu eyi k…ôloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē, k'ement…ôr Ňča waca w…Ēn k…Ē w…õc…ôk.  
\v 41 Mba nt…õ p…ônanaŇčkan…õ k…ôb…Ēt Ňča haŇč ta Ňčantam k…ôlaŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayi p…ôciyan…õ disr…õ. K…Ē Yesu eyif Ňča: ¬ęN…ôy…Ē paka p…Ēl…Ēma pedi ba?¬Ľ  
\v 42 K…Ē ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč Ňčawur…õ alop Ňč…õn…õk…ôt Ňčin k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē.  
\v 43 K…Ē Yesu …õl…õk alop ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k'…Ēs…Ēm Ňči f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč. 
\p  
\v 44 Nt…õ elip k…ôs…Ēm alop nŇč…õ m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęMes mam…õ m'inclok'un nt…õ inayi k…Ē n…ôna m…Ē. M…õn…õ mes m…Ēk…Ē ancic tetem Tawureta Musa, yecic…ôs yecempi ya ad…ôŇčk a Kanu k…Ē Yabura Dawuda m…Ē f…ôp meyi.¬Ľ  
\v 45 K…Ē Yesu …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôs…Ēk s…ôbomp nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôr…õ Yecic ya Kanu f…ôp m…Ē.  
\v 46 K…Ē Yesu oloku Ňča: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē ancic d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku, a dis dendel…Ēl Krist, k…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, p…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē tataka t…Ēn ta maas.  
\v 47 M…õn…õ pacam k…ôs…ôkp…ôr mera pac…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč tewe t…Ēn, k…ôy…õf…õ ka Yerusal…õm, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ paŇčaŇčn…õn…õ afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp kiciya k…ôŇčan m…Ē.  
\v 48 N…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ sede sa mes mam…õ.  
\v 49 K…Ē ina, k…ôk…õr…õ nu k'inder daka nd…õ Papa kem …õnas…ĒŇč temer k…ôs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē. N…ôyi nn…Ē dare dand…õ haŇč Kanu k…ôlas nu f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa darenc.¬Ľ 
\s1 Yesu k…ôp…õ k…Ēn darenc 
\r Mark 16.19-20; Asom 1.9-11 
\p  
\v 50 K…Ē Yesu osol…õ Ňča k'eŇčkek…ôr…õ dare k…ôs…ôk ntende Betani, nt…õ Ňčamb…ôp di m…Ē, k'…õmp…õn…õ waca darenc, k'ontolan…õ Ňča.  
\v 51 Eyi k…ôtolan…õ Ňča, k'…õsak Ňča, k'amp…õn…õ k…Ē d…ôk…Ēm.  
\v 52 K…Ē Ňčanc…ôp…õ k…Ē mobu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē p…ôleli, k…Ē Ňčalukus Yerusal…õm, p…ôbotu disr…õ.  
\v 53 T…õm o t…õm Ňčanck…Ē oŇč nde \k k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu\k*, Ňčackor-koru Kanu.